es%20aimed%20at%20professional%20customers%20rather%20than%20gamers%20and%20hobbyists.%20The%20Quest%20Pro%20is%20more%20than%20a%20traditional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-virtual-reality%5C%22%3EMeta%20VR%3C%2Fa%3E%20headset%3B%20it%20also%20has%20augmented%20reality%20capabilities%20that%20integrate%20virtual%20elements%20into%20the%20real%20world.%20That%20makes%20this%20a%20so-called%20mixed-reality%20headset.%20Here's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20new%20Meta%20Quest%20Pro.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Meta%20Quest%20Pro%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Meta%20Quest%20Pro%20is%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-exec-reportedly-tells-employees-wont-make-follow-up-pro-2023-3%5C%22%3EMeta%20VR%20headset%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20intended%20to%20be%20an%20upgrade%20to%20the%20Meta%20Quest%202.%20While%20the%20Quest%202%20is%20exclusively%20a%20VR%20headset%20and%20intended%20primarily%20for%20gamers%20and%20VR%20hobbyists%2C%20the%20Quest%20Pro%20lives%20up%20to%20its%20name%20by%20being%20aimed%20at%20professional%20users%20who%20may%20have%20a%20need%20to%20perform%20activities%20in%20the%20metaverse.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20Quest%20Pro%20operates%20very%20much%20like%20the%20older%20Quest%202%2C%20and%20more%20casual%20users%20may%20use%20it%20for%20gaming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20headset%20is%20powered%20by%20the%20Qualcomm%20Snapdragon%20XR2%2B%20chipset%20and%20has%2012GB%20RAM%20and%20256GB%20of%20onboard%20storage.%20Each%20eye%20delivers%20a%20resolution%20of%201800x1920%20pixels%20--%20about%20the%20same%20as%20the%20Quest%202.%20It%20also%20has%20three%20front-facing%20and%20two%20side-facing%20cameras.%20Like%20the%20Quest%202%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20pair%20of%20hand%20controllers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20difference%20between%20the%20Quest%20Pro%20and%20the%20older%20Quest%202%20is%20that%20while%20the%20Quest%202%20is%20designed%20entirely%20for%20virtual%20reality%2C%20the%20Quest%20Pro%20has%20mixed%20reality%20capabilities%20that%20can%20blend%20virtual%20elements%20into%20a%20view%20of%20the%20real%20world%20transmitted%20through%20the%20headset's%20cameras.%20It%20has%20some%20other%2C%20less%20significant%20differences%20as%20well.%20It%20is%20equipped%20with%20twice%20the%20memory%20(12GB%20vs.%208GB)%2C%20for%20example%2C%20and%20a%20more%20elegant%20IPD%20adjustment%20for%20optimizing%20vision%20and%20focus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20is%20special%20about%20Meta%20Quest%20Pro%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20be%20familiar%20with%20the%20Quest%202's%20black-and-white%20passthrough%20mode%2C%20which%20switches%20off%20virtual%20reality%20to%20let%20you%20see%20the%20physical%20world%20around%20you.%20The%20Quest%202's%20passthrough%20mode%20is%20mainly%20designed%20to%20let%20you%20briefly%20interact%20with%20the%20real%20world%20without%20removing%20the%20headset.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20Quest%20Pro%20has%20a%20full-color%2C%20high-resolution%20passthrough%20that%20serves%20as%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20headset's%20mixed%20reality%20mode.%20With%20the%20right%20software%2C%20you%20can%20run%20augmented%20reality%20simulations%20in%20the%20real%20world%2C%20for%20example%2C%20or%20use%20your%20computer's%20mouse%20and%20keyboard%20within%20a%20mixed%20reality%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20much%20does%20the%20Meta%20Quest%20Pro%20cost%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-slashing-vr-headset-prices-up-to-500-underwhelming-sales-2023-3%5C%22%3EMeta%20Quest%20Pro%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20currently%20%24999.99%2C%20a%20substantial%20price%20reduction%20compared%20to%20when%20the%20Quest%20Pro%20debuted%20in%20October%202022%20at%20%241%2C500.%20There%20are%20a%20handful%20of%20accessories%20available%20as%20well%2C%20like%20full%20light%20blockers%20that%20shield%20light%20coming%20in%20from%20the%20periphery%20of%20the%20headset%2C%20a%20carrying%20case%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20price%20is%20substantially%20more%20than%20the%20%24300%20Quest%202%2C%20but%20most%20casual%20gamers%20and%20hobbyists%20should%20probably%20pass%20on%20this%20headset%20and%20opt%20for%20the%20less%20expensive%20Quest%202%20or%20the%20forthcoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-cto-denies-rushing-quest-3-announcement-apple-vision-pro-2023-7%5C%22%3EQuest%203%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIs%20the%20Meta%20Quest%202%20or%20Quest%20Pro%20better%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20easy%20answer%20to%20the%20question%20of%20which%20headset%20is%20better.%20Technologically%2C%20the%20new%20Quest%20Pro%20is%20significantly%20better%2C%20with%20a%20faster%20processor%20--%20the%20Qualcomm%20Snapdragon%20XR2%2B%20is%20about%2050%25%20faster%20than%20the%20chipset%20found%20in%20the%20Quest%202%20--%20and%20additional%20memory.%20However%2C%20it%20only%20features%20256GB%20of%20storage%20for%20games%20and%20apps%2C%20while%20the%20Quest%202%20has%20more%20storage%20options.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20the%20same%20resolution%20as%20the%20Quest%202%2C%20but%20the%20display%20is%20slightly%20better%20overall%2C%20with%20a%20wider%20color%20gamut%20that%20can%20add%20up%20to%20better%20VR%20visuals.%20The%20headset%20itself%20is%20less%20bulky%20and%20more%20lightweight.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20continuous%20IPD%20control%20from%2055-75mm%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20people%20with%20varying%20interpupillary%20distances%20to%20get%20a%20comfortable%20experience.%20The%20Quest%202%20has%20fewer%20options%20for%20getting%20a%20comfortable%20fit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20real%20difference%20between%20the%20Meta%20Quest%202%20and%20the%20Quest%20Pro%20comes%20down%20to%20the%20Quest%20Pro's%20mixed%20reality%20capabilities.%20And%20with%20the%20right%20software%2C%20it%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20integrate%20virtual%20elements%20into%20the%20passthrough%20view%20of%20the%20physical%20world.%20This%20augmented%20reality%20capability%20might%20be%20valuable%20to%20professionals%20who%20need%20to%20work%20and%20collaborate%20this%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tradeoff%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20the%20Quest%20Pro%20pricing%20starts%20at%20%241%2C000%2C%20which%20is%20more%20than%20three%20times%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20Quest%202.%20If%20you%20don't%20need%20the%20mixed%20reality%20features%2C%20you're%20almost%20certainly%20better%20off%20with%20the%20Quest%202%20or%20the%20forthcoming%20Quest%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-quest-pro%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694420341000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6421a68e0237f900185312ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-quest-pro%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Meta%20Quest%20Pro%20price%2C%20though%20reduced%2C%20is%20still%20higher%20than%20standard%20VR%20headsets%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20its%20augmented%20reality%20capabilities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Dave%20Johnson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-quest-pro%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20India-Bharat%20Name%20Change%20Row%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Jab%20At%20Government%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Frahul-gandhi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20government%20on%20Sunday%20over%20speculation%20it%20plans%20to%20change%20the%20country's%20name%20to%20Bharat.%20At%20an%20event%20in%20France%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20if%20%26quot%3B...%20this%20change%20(to)%20a%20more%20pop