t%20is%20historically%20of%20far%20more%20importance%20in%20understanding%20the%20conflict%20between%20capitalism%20and%20socialism.%20On%20September%2011%2C%201973%2C%20a%20democratically%20elected%20socialist%2FMarxist%20government%20led%20by%20President%20Salvador%20Allende%20in%20Chile%20was%20overthrown%20in%20a%20military%20coup%20which%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fthe-americas%2F2023%2F08%2F31%2Fchile-is-still-haunted-by-the-coup-in-september-1973%5C%22%3ECIA%20admitted%20later%20that%20it%20had%20engineered%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllende%E2%80%99s%20coming%20to%20power%20was%20the%20first%20historical%20example%20of%20a%20socialist%2FMarxist%20movement%20gaining%20success%20in%20country%20through%20democratic%20means%20in%20an%20election%20battle%20with%20the%20right-wing%20parties.%20This%20was%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20with%20the%20Bolshevik%20Revolution%20of%201917%2C%20Chinese%20Revolution%20in%201949%20and%20Cuban%20Revolution%20in%201959.%20Kerala%20in%20India%20in%201957%20is%20generally%20cited%20as%20the%20first%20example%20of%20communists%20coming%20to%20power%20through%20the%20electoral%20process%3B%20but%20this%20victory%2C%20though%20very%20important%2C%20was%20confined%20to%20a%20state%20in%20a%20big%20country%20and%20did%20not%20have%20the%20same%20international%20significance%20as%20the%20Chilean%20success%20under%20Allende%E2%80%99s%20leadership.%20It%20was%20precisely%20this%20democratic%20Chileans%20path%20to%20socialism%20which%20scared%20the%20anti-socialist%20global%20establishment%20led%20by%20the%20US%2C%20and%20that%20too%20geographically%20so%20close%20to%20the%20US.%20The%20US%20was%20already%20trying%20to%20crush%20Cuba%E2%80%99s%20turn%20to%20socialism%20through%20economic%20blockades%20and%20military%20intrusions%20and%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22America%E2%80%99s%20First%20Date%20with%209%2F11%20Was%20Not%20on%20US%20Soil%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Famericas-first-date-with-9-11-was-not-on-us-soil%5C%22%3EAmerica%E2%80%99s%20First%20Date%20with%209%2F11%20Was%20Not%20on%20US%20Soil%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChile%E2%80%99s%20turn%20to%20socialism%20was%20even%20more%20threatening%20to%20the%20US%20establishment%20than%20Cuba%20because%20of%20five%20reasons%3A%20one%2C%20it%20was%20an%20economically%20successful%20economy%20with%20very%20good%20resource%20base%20especially%20in%20copper%2C%20two%2C%20another%20socialist%20country%20in%20Latin%20America%20along%20with%20Cuba%20was%20seen%20as%20encouraging%20anti-American%20bloc%20in%20the%20US%20sphere%20of%20influence%2C%20third%2C%20the%20democratic%20Chilean%20path%20to%20socialism%20was%20seen%20by%20the%20US%20as%20a%20possible%20example%20to%20other%20countries%20in%20Latin%20America%20to%20follow%20the%20socialist%20path%20in%20contrast%20with%20doubts%20in%20those%20countries%20about%20following%20the%20Cuba%20style%20guerrilla%20path%20of%20armed%20capture%20of%20state%20power%2C%20fourth%2C%20very%20big%20multinational%20corporations%20in%20the%20US%20had%20long%20established%20business%20interests%20in%20Chile%20especially%20in%20copper%2C%20and%20fifth%2C%20Chile%20in%20addition%20to%20Cuba%20was%20seen%20as%20strengthening%20the%20Soviet%20sphere%20of%20influence%20in%20Latin%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20due%20to%20these%20reasons%20that%20the%20US%20started%20campaigns%20and%20strategies%20to%20unseat%20Allende%20from%20power.%20One%20of%20the%20first%20significant%20economic%20sabotage%20campaigns%20organised%20by%20the%20CIA%20was%20to%20finance%20the%20anti-socialist%20opposition%20to%20organise%20a%20nationwide%20strike%20by%20truck-drivers%20and%20shop%20keepers.%20Geographically%2C%20Chilean%20territory%20is%20characterised%20by%20length%20and%20very%20narrow%20in%20breadth.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20strike%20by%20the%20truck%20drivers%20crippled%20the%20transport%20system%20in%20the%20country.%20US%20blocked%20loans%20to%20Chile.%20The%20Richard%20Nixon-led%20administration%20in%20the%20US%20openly%20supported%20CIA%20led%20sabotage%20of%20Allende-led%20Chile%20and%20directed%20the%20CIA%20to%20make%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20economy%20scream.%20These%20sabotage%20campaigns%20gave%20push%20to%20shortages%20and%20high%20inflation.%20Allende%20still%20retained%20his%20popularity%20but%20also%20sought%20military%20support%20to%20his%20regime%20by%20bringing%20some%20military%20commanders%20into%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20of%20nationalisation%20of%20copper%20mines%20started%20by%20Allende%E2%80%99s%20government%20especially%20alarmed%20the%20US%20corporations%20and%20their%20allies%20in%20the%20US%20military%20and%20Chilean%20military.%20The%20nationalisation%20of%20copper%20mines%20was%20internally%20so%20popular%20in%20Chile%20that%20even%20the%20opposition%20supported%20it.%20The%20Allende%20government%20proceeded%20to%20issue%20a%20decree%20for%20state%20takeover%20of%20150%20large%20firms.%20Some%20left%20adventurist%20supporters%20of%20the%20government%20went%20on%20a%20spree%20of%20illegal%20seizure%20of%20many%20businesses%2C%20farms%20and%20even%20houses.%20This%20left%20adventurism%20caused%20unease%20with%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20middle%20class%20which%20had%20previously%20supported%20the%20Allende%20government%E2%80%99s%20measures%20of%20wage%20increases%20and%20expansion%20of%20public%20sector%20jobs.%20The%20country%20was%20getting%20increasingly%20polarised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERumours%20started%20circulating%20that%20military%20might%20stage%20a%20coup.%20Allende%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20militant%2C%20believed%20in%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20trusted%20the%20Chilean%20constitution%20that%20military%20would%20remain%20neutral%20in%20political%20contestation.%20Many%20of%20his%20supporters%20held%20huge%20rallies%20in%20his%20support%20with%20a%20demand%20for%20weapons%20to%20defend%20his%20government.%20This%20led%20to%20unjustified%20and%20deliberate%20propaganda%20that%20his%20supporters%20were%20acquiring%20weapons%20for%20a%20military%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20military%20led%20by%20General%20August%20Pinochet%20staged%20the%20coup.%20The%20military%20entered%20the%20presidential%20place.%20Allende%20did%20not%20surrender%20and%20died%20fighting.%20It%20is%20still%20uncertain%20whether%20he%20shot%20himself%20or%20was%20killed%20by%20the%20army.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20managed%20to%20broadcast%20a%20seven-minute%20historically%20significant%20message%20to%20the%20nation%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20not%20resign.%20I%20will%20repay%20the%20loyalty%20of%20the%20people%20with%20my%20life%E2%80%A6%20Always%20remember%20that%20much%20sooner%20that%20later%20the%20great%20avenues%20along%20which%20free%20men%20pass%20to%20build%20a%20better%20society%20will%20once%20again%20be%20open.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FIZVWOWA2Hpk%3Fsi%3DbOablZFCu4FjVhws%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifteen%20years%20of%20military%20dictatorship%20(1973-1988)%20of%20Pinochet%20followed.%20This%20was%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20periods%20for%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20any%20country.%20Chile%20entered%20a%20period%20of%20darkness.%20Trade%20unionists%2C%20academics%2C%20journalists%2C%20lawyers%20and%20students%20were%20arrested%2C%20tortured%20and%20disappeared.%20The%20military%20junta%20murdered%202%2C130%20people%20and%20tortured%20at%20least%2030%2C000%2C%20some%20very%20brutally%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2004%2Fnov%2F15%2Fchile.jonathanfranklin%5C%22%3Einvestigations%20by%20democratic%20governments%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20came%20to%20power%20after%201988.%20The%20narratives%20I%20heard%20in%20Oxford%20from%20some%20victims%20of%20Pinochet%E2%80%99s%20terror%20regime%2C%20which%20was%20also%20very%20corrupt%20like%20all%20dictatorships%2C%20have%20been%20horrifying.%20Pinochet%20was%20eventually%20arrested%20in%20London%20in%201998%20by%20an%20order%20passed%20by%20a%20great%20Spanish%20Judge%20Baltasar%20Garzon%20under%20an%20international%20law%20that%20anyone%20responsible%20for%20torture%20and%20disappearance%20of%20political%20prisoners%20in%20a%20country%20can%20be%20arrested%20even%20outside%20that%20country.%20This%20was%20a%20landmark%20case%20in%20strengthening%20the%20idea%20of%20universal%20jurisdiction%20for%20crimes%20against%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Day%20Chile%20and%20the%20Rest%20of%20Latin%20America%20Remember%20as%20Their%209%2F11%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-day-chileans-and-the-rest-of-latin-america-remember-their-911%5C%22%3EThe%20Day%20Chile%20and%20the%20Rest%20of%20Latin%20America%20Remember%20as%20Their%209%2F11%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPinochet%20died%20a%20disgraced%20man%20in%202011%20while%20Allende%20has%20entered%20Chilean%20and%20global%20history%20as%20an%20icon%20of%20progress%20and%20justice.%20The%20current%20president%20of%20Chile%2C%20Gabriel%20Boric%2C%20paid%20homage%20on%20his%20day%20of%20inauguration%20to%20Allende%20at%20his%20statue%20in%20front%20of%20La%20Moneda%2C%20the%20presidential%20palace%20in%20the%20capital%20Santiago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20remain%20a%20very%20black%20spot%20in%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20international%20political%20order%20that%20it%20engineered%20this%20most%20dreadful%20military%20coup%20of%20a%20democratically%20elected%20leader.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20black%20spot%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Chicago%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20which%20led%20by%20Milton%20Freedman%20advised%20the%20dictator%20Pinochet%20to%20launch%20the%20neoliberal%20programme%20of%20privatisation%20and%20dismantling%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20providing%20public%20utilities.%20For%20the%20socialists%20in%20Chile%20and%20outside%2C%20Allende%20remains%20a%20source%20of%20inspiration%20while%20recognising%20that%20the%20new%20era%20of%20socialist%20vision%20must%20incorporate%20the%20ecological%20perspective%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20threat%20of%20global%20climate%20change%20being%20hastened%20under%20capitalism.%20The%20eco-socialist%20vision%20must%20eschew%20the%20old%20socialist%20fascination%20with%20fast%20industrialisation%20and%20economic%20growth.%20Building%20a%20broader%20alliance%20of%20forces%20to%20forge%20a%20consensus%20for%20building%20a%20fairer%2C%20equitable%20and%20sustainable%20future%20of%20humanity%20would%20be%20the%20most%20appropriate%20way%20of%20paying%20homage%20to%20Allende%20and%20the%20thousands%20of%20socialist%20martyrs%20of%20Chile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPritam%20Singh%20is%20Professor%20Emeritus%20at%20Oxford%20Brookes%20Business%20School%20and%20the%20author%20of%20Economy%2C%20Culture%20and%20Human%20Rights.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694419847000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11133907%2F8284617884_3171c96d6a_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fremembering-salvador-allendes-socialist-chile-50-years-on%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20will%20remain%20a%20very%20black%20spot%20in%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20international%20political%20order%20that%20it%20engineered%20a%20most%20dreadful%20military%20coup%20of%20a%20democratically%20elected%20leader.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fremembering-salvador-allendes-socialist-chile-50-years-on%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20G20%20Spotlights%20Indias%20Ascendance%20In%20Global%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20firmly%20positioned%20itself%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20new%20global%20order%20and%20decision-making%20with%20astute%20diplomacy%20and%20strategy%2C%20which%20culminated%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Declaration%20during%20its%20G20%20presidency.%20Despite%20a%20nine-month%20impasse%20with%20consensus%20seemingly%20elusive%2C%20200%20hours%20of%20tireless%20negotiations%20and%20four%20drafts%20finally%20led%20to%20a%20unanimous%20agreement%20among%20G20%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20negotiations%2C%20India%20emphasized%20unity%20over%20division.%20This%20G20%20presidency%20marked%20a%20historic%20moment%20for%20India%2C%20elevating%20its%20role%20in%20the%20emerging%20global%20order.%20Today%2C%20the%20world%20views%20India%20as%20a%20trustworthy%2C%20robust%20power%20and%20an%20advocate%20for%20the%20underserved%20and%20marginalised%20nations.%20Earlier%20in%20the%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20showcased%20his%20vision%20by%20hosting%20the%20'Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South'%20virtual%20summit.%20This%20entailed%20consultations%20with%20125%20countries%2C%20often%20sidelined%20in%20such%20dialogues.%20Beyond%20the%20wealthier%20members%2C%20nations%20from%20the%20Global%20South%20predominated%20India's%20G20%20guest%20list.%20That%20is%20a%20position%20that%20distinguishes%20India%20from%20other%20emerging%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22hle8f54g%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fhle8f54g_pm-modi-g20-declaration-650_625x300_09_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Democracy%20vs%20China's%20Autocracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Covid%20pandemic%20and%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20highlighted%20the%20global%20economies'%20over-reliance%20on%20China's%20supply%20chain.%20The%20need%20for%20not%20just%20affordable%20labour%20but%20also%20reliable%2C%20resilient%20partners%20became%20apparent.%20Repeated%20lockdowns%20in%20China%20disrupted%20global%20supply%20chains.%20Geopolitical%20tensions%2C%20coupled%20with%20China's%20hegemonic%20goals%20and%20intrusive%20business%20practices%2C%20have%20eroded%20trust.%20The%20world%20now%20faces%20a%20dichotomy%20-%20India's%20democratic%20approach%20versus%20China's%20opaque%20autocracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20were%20sceptical%20about%20this%20year's%20summit%20due%20to%20the%20contrasting%20stance%20of%20the%20Russia-China%20alliance%20and%20the%20G7%20on%20subjects%20like%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20and%20China's%20regional%20expansionism.%20Critics%20doubted%20the%20possibility%20of%20any%20significant%20joint%20communique.%20However%2C%20India%20surpassed%20expectations%20and%20by%20some%20distance.%20Amidst%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20India%20asserted%20its%20independence%20by%20importing%20Russian%20oil%2C%20defying%20the%20western%20bloc's%20wishes.%20Against%20western%20scepticism%2C%20the%20G20%20members%20passed%20a%20resolution%20on%20Ukraine%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20India%20further%20showcased%20its%20importance%20in%20the%20global%20supply%20chain%20with%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Corridor%20at%20the%20G20.%20This%20initiative%2C%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20trade%2C%20enhancing%20energy%20transport%2C%20and%20fostering%20digital%20connectivity%2C%20challenges%20China's%20economic%20aspirations%20in%20the%20region.%20Other%20than%20green%20energy%20manufacturing%20value%20chain%2C%20'Electric%20Vehicle'%20(EV)%20manufacturing%20represents%20one%20of%20the%20corridor's%20key%20future%20growth%20sectors%20as%20India%20is%20expected%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20third-largest%20automotive%20market%20by%202026%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%202021%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%20paper.%20These%20are%20just%20of%20many%20opportunities%20waiting%20to%20be%20explored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20Firsts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20prowess%20in%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructure%20(DPI)%20was%20also%20evident.%20India%20proposed%20the%20Global%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructure%20Repository%20(GDPIR).%20The%20'India%20Stack'%2C%20an%20ensemble%20of%20open-source%20digital%20solutions%2C%20resonated%20with%20G20%20members.%20To%20bring%20out%20the%20goodness%20of%20millets%20and%20to%20introduce%20its%20benefits%20to%20the%20world%2C%20India%20pushed%20for%20the%20launch%20of%20an%20international%20research%20initiative%20on%20millets%20and%20other%20ancient%20grains.%20The%20Global%20Biofuel%20Alliance%2C%20a%20grouping%20of%20more%20than%2030%20countries%20and%20international%20institutions%2C%20is%20another%20much-awaited%20outcome%20of%20India's%20presidency.%20It%20will%20facilitate%20sustainable%20biofuels%20in%20emerging%20economies.%20Another%20first%20for%20G20%20is%20India's%20proposal%20to%20hold%20a%20virtual%20meet%20later%20in%20November%20to%20review%20the%20progress%20of%20all%20the%20suggestions%20made%20in%20the%20leaders'%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndispensable%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntroducing%20the%20African%20Union%20to%20the%20G20%20marks%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20global%20dynamics.%20This%20move%20amplifies%20India's%20sway%20in%20Africa%2C%20a%20continent%20where%20major%20powers%20have%20been%20vying%20for%20some%20influence.%20India's%20intention%20is%20to%20collaborate%20with%20Africa%20on%20climate%20change%2C%20trade%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20infrastructure.%20India's%20soft%20power%2C%20including%20its%20art%2C%20heritage%2C%20and%20tourism%2C%20was%20prominently%20showcased%20during%20the%20year-long%20delegate%20meetings%20across%20various%20states.%20The%20meticulous%20planning%20and%20execution%20of%20the%20summit%20left%20global%20leaders%20in%20admiration.%20India%20has%20set%20a%20challenging%20benchmark%2C%20and%20countries%20like%20Brazil%20and%20South%20Africa%20will%20have%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20to%20match%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20democracies%20need%20to%20recalibrate%20their%20strategies%2C%20India%20is%20increasingly%20becoming%20indispensable.%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20this%20ascent.%20A%20pragmatist%20at%20heart%2C%20he%20prioritises%20national%20interests%20through%20realistic%20alliances.%20His%20international%20outreach%2C%20often%20criticised%20domestically%2C%20has%20proven%20to%20have%20strategic%20depth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20New%20Global%20Order%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20in%20its%20article%2C%20'India's%20G-20%20win%20shows%20US%20learning%20how%20to%20counter%20China's%20rise'%2C%20has%20written%20how%20the%20joint%20communique%20gave%20PM%20Modi%20a%20win%20that%20bolsters%20India's%20status%20as%20a%20rising%20power%20and%20blunts%20China's%20global%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20section%20of%20western%20media%20has%20shown%20bias%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20covering%20India%20and%20its%20growth%20story.%20They%20had%20written%20off%20India's%20year-long%20presidency%20as%20just%20a%20routine%20rotational%20exercise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20critics%20may%20point%20to%20numerous%20challenges%20ahead%2C%20this%20G20%20presidency%20has%20infused%20fresh%20energy%20and%20purpose%20into%20the%20forum.%20The%20inclusion%20of%20the%20African%20Union%20indicates%20promising%20developments%20and%20pivotal%20decisions%20on%20the%20horizon.%20Amidst%20a%20faltering%20West%20and%20an%20assertive%20China%2C%20India%20is%20poised%20to%20navigate%20the%20new%20global%20order%20based%20on%20its%20formidable%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nation's%20journey%20as%20a%20dominant%20global%20player%20for%20centuries%20to%20come%20has%20well%20and%20truly%20begun.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694419620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fqhqohjho_g20-declaration_625x300_10_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fg20-summit-brings-india-to-the-centre-stage-4379020%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20firmly%20positioned%20itself%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20new%20global%20order%20and%20decision-making%20with%20astute%20diplomacy%20and%20strategy%2C%20which%20culminated%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Declaration%20during%20its%20G20%20presidency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fg20-summit-brings-india-to-the-centre-stage-4379020%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fg20-summit-brings-india-to-the-centre-stage-4379020%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fg20-summit-brings-india-to-the-centre-stage-4379020%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asia%20Cup%20Live%3A%20Clear%20Sky%20In%20Colombo%2C%20Match%20Expected%20To%20Start%20At%203%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20vs%20Pakistan%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20Super%204%2C%20Live%20Updates%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20the%20latest%20update%20from%20the%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%2C%20there%20is%20clear%20sky%20in%20Colombo%20and%20the%20match%20is%20expected%20to%20begin%20at%203%20PM.%20After%20rain%20played%20a%20spoilsport%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20Super%204%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20resume%20on%20Monday%20in%20Colombo.%20India%20will%20resume%20at%20the%20score%20of%20147%20for%202%20in%2024.1%20overs%20with%20KL%20Rahul%20(17*)%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20(8*)%20at%20the%20crease.%20Earlier%2C%20Pakistan%20skipper%20Babar%20Azam%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20invited%20India%20to%20bat%20first.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(56)%20and%20Shubman%20Gill%20(58)%20stitched%20121%2