22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwatch-chaos-and-stampede-like-situation-at-ar-rahmans-chennai-concert-4378881%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Plans%20To%20Restrict%20Paracetamol%20Sale%20To%20Reduce%20Suicides%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUK%20government%20is%20planning%20to%20limit%20the%20availability%20of%20over-the-counter%20drugs%20containing%20paracetamol%20to%20reduce%20deaths%20by%20suicide.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20is%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Suicide%20Prevention%20Strategy%20unveiled%20recently.%20The%20document%20highlights%20how%20reductions%20in%20deaths%20by%20suicide%20have%20stalled%20since%202018.%20The%20new%20policy%20also%20talks%20about%20a%20national%20alert%20system%20to%20highlight%20new%20methods%20of%20suicide%20to%20schools%20and%20colleges%20across%20the%20country%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnational-alert-system-could-highlight-new-methods-of-suicide-to-schools-and-universities-12958594%5C%22%3Ethe%20outlet%3C%2Fa%3E%20further%20said.%20The%20last%20such%20strategy%20was%20published%20more%20than%2010%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20says%20medical%20experts%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20review%20whether%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20paracetamol%20people%20can%20buy%20in%20shops%20could%20help%20bring%20down%20suicide%20rates%20in%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2023%2F09%2F11%2Fparacetamol-sales-restricted-further-reduce-suicides%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20currently%20people%20can%20buy%20a%20maximum%20of%20two%20packets%20of%20medication%20containing%20paracetamol%2C%20which%20is%20typically%2016%20tablets%20of%20500mg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20government%20has%20asked%20the%20Medicines%20and%20Healthcare%20products%20Regulatory%20Agency%20(MHRA)%20to%20consider%20a%20further%20clampdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinisters%20in%20the%20UK%20have%20pledged%20to%20reduce%20suicide%20rates%20in%20England%20within%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fjournals%2Fthe-british-journal-of-psychiatry%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fparacetamol-selfpoisoning-characteristics-prevention-and-harm-reduction%2FCD0DD73FD2CB5D85A17418B749348808%5C%22%3E2018%20study%20published%20by%20Cambridge%20University%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20paracetamol%20is%20the%20most%20common%20drug%20used%20for%20self-poisoning%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20is%20associated%20with%20fatal%20liver%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20was%20based%20on%20analysis%20of%20the%20data%20of%2080%20patients%20in%20hospitals%20using%20a%20structured%20interview%20schedule%2C%20measures%20of%20depression%20and%20suicidal%20intent%2C%20information%20collected%20through%20the%20Oxford%20Monitoring%20System%20for%20Attempted%20Suicide%2C%20along%20with%20the%20results%20of%20liver%20function%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Health%20Service%20(NHS)%20said%20more%20than%205%2C000%20people%20die%20by%20suicide%20each%20year%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20receives%20200%2C000%20calls%20to%20crisis%20lines%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20ple