a%2Famp_articleshow%2F103571965.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fthailands-new-pm-draws-flak-in-parliament-for-aimless-economic-agenda%2Famp_articleshow%2F103571965.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Civil%20Society%20Calls%20Out%20G20%20Declaration%E2%80%99s%20Omission%20of%20Civic%20Space%20Erosion%2C%20Democracy%20Decline%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08133538%2F2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20G20%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Declaration%2C%20following%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Summit%2C%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20from%20civil%20society%20organisations%20for%20its%20inadequacy%20in%20addressing%20critical%20global%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Declaration%20falls%20short%20in%20offering%20a%20clear%20roadmap%20to%20tackle%20the%20pressing%20concerns%20of%20economic%20inequality%2C%20climate%20crisis%2C%20hunger%2C%20and%20energy%20issues%2C%20Peoples%E2%80%99%2020%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday%2C%20September%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Summit%20itself%20was%20marred%20by%20controversy%2C%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbeautification%20drive%E2%80%9D%20displacing%20slum%20residents.%20Meanwhile%2C%20reports%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20against%20the%20Christian%20minority%20were%20reported%20in%20Northeast%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Declaration%2C%20a%20result%20of%20intense%20negotiations%20among%20G20%20member%20nations%2C%20also%20lacks%20a%20comprehensive%20reassessment%20of%20neoliberal%20market-driven%20economies%20and%20GDP-centric%20growth%20paradigms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20Declaration%E2%80%99s%20omission%20of%20critical%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20erosion%20of%20civic%20space%20and%20the%20global%20decline%20in%20democracy.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20alarming%20trend%20is%20especially%20pertinent%20in%20several%20G20%20countries%2C%20including%20China%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Russia%2C%20T%C3%BCrkiye%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20India%2C%20as%20highlighted%20by%20CIVICUS%E2%80%99s%20Civic%20Space%20Monitor%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ffive-keys-takeaways-from-the-g20-summit-in-delhi%5C%22%3EFive%20Keys%20Takeaways%20From%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20text%20of%20the%20full%20statement%20is%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EG20%20Falls%20Short%20in%20Addressing%20Global%20Challenges%2C%20Promises%20Abound%20but%20Impact%20Lacks%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECivil%20society%20organizations%20(CSOs)%20are%20raising%20their%20voices%20in%20dissent%20as%20they%20criticize%20the%20G20%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Declaration%20for%20its%20inability%20to%20confront%20the%20most%20critical%20global%20issues.%20Despite%20its%20grandiose%20language%2C%20the%20Declaration%20falls%20short%20in%20offering%20concrete%20commitments%20and%20a%20clear%20roadmap%20to%20tackle%20the%20pressing%20concerns%20of%20rising%20economic%20inequality%2C%20climate%20crisis%2C%20hunger%2C%20and%20the%20energy%20crisis.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20G20%20New%20Delhi%20Summit%20unfolded%20amid%20controversy%2C%20marked%20by%20a%20contentious%20%E2%80%9Cbeautification%20drive%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20event.%20This%20drive%20resulted%20in%20the%20displacement%20of%20numerous%20slum%20residents%20as%20their%20homes%20were%20bulldozed.%20Additionally%2C%20there%20was%20a%20crackdown%20on%20civil%20society%20gatherings%20critical%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20and%20troubling%20incidents%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20against%20the%20Christian%20minority%20in%20Northeast%20India%20were%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20G20%20Summit%20took%20place%20amidst%20one%20of%20the%20most%20polarized%20periods%20in%20its%20history%2C%20harkening%20back%20to%20the%20turbulence%20of%202008.%20The%20Declaration%2C%20adopted%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20Summit%2C%20represents%20the%20outcome%20of%20extensive%20negotiations%20among%20member%20nations%20grappling%20with%20divergent%20interests%2C%20including%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20extend%20our%20congratulations%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20for%20skillfully%20facilitating%20the%20negotiation%20process%20that%20culminated%20in%20the%20consensus%20document%2C%20a%20product%20of%20compromise%20among%20the%2020%20member%20states%20grappling%20with%20conflicting%20priorities.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EComprising%20over%2014%2C000%20words%2C%20the%20Declaration%20delves%20into%20a%20wide%20spectrum%20of%20global%20economic%2C%20social%2C%20and%20environmental%20issues.%20In%20comparison%20to%20the%202022%20Bali%20Declaration%2C%20it%20provides%20a%20more%20substantial%20treatment%20of%20topics%20such%20as%20the%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs)%2C%20gender%20equality%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%20and%20digital%20technology%2C%20including%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENevertheless%2C%20beneath%20its%20eloquent%20rhetoric%2C%20the%20Declaration%20falls%20short%20in%20providing%20substantial%20analysis%20and%20tangible%20solutions%20for%20the%20pressing%20global%20crises.%20These%20crises%2C%20including%20escalating%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20political%20and%20ecological%20inequalities%20and%20climate%20and%20biodiversity%C2%A0%20threats%2C%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences%20affecting%20not%20only%20G20%20nations%20but%20also%20non-G20%20countries%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20and%20countries%20in%20conflict%2C%20which%20are%20highly%20susceptible%20to%20external%20economic%20and%20ecological%20shocks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Declaration%20of%20the%20PEOPLES%E2%80%99%2020%20Assembly%20held%20on%20August%2023-24%2C%202023%2C%20we%20fervently%20called%20upon%20G20%20leaders%20to%20display%20resolute%20collective%20determination%20in%20reshaping%20the%20existing%20political%20and%20economic%20framework.%20This%20framework%20has%20contributed%20to%20the%20global%20crisis%20by%20prioritizing%20narrow%20national%20and%20elite%20interests%2C%20exploitative%20extractive%20industry%2C%20fossil%20fuel%20and%20carbon-based%20growth%20models%2C%20global%20value%20chains%20that%20disrespect%20human%20and%20labour%20rights%2C%20and%20military%20security%20considerations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20G20%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Declaration%20fails%20to%20conduct%20a%20thorough%20reassessment%20of%20neoliberal%20market-driven%20economies%20and%20the%20GDP-centric%20growth%20paradigm.%20It%20offers%20little%20indication%20of%20genuine%20efforts%20to%20explore%20alternative%20paradigms%20rooted%20in%20ecological%20sustainability%2C%20inclusive%20human%20development%2C%20human%20security%2C%20positive%20peace%2C%20gender%20equality%2C%20and%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMuch%20to%20their%20dismay%2C%20we%20perceive%20a%20perpetuation%20of%20the%20status%20quo%20and%20a%20business-as-usual%20approach%20in%20the%20G20%E2%80%99s%20actions%2C%20ignoring%20the%20deepening%20global%20crisis.%20While%20the%20G20%20leaders%20managed%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20Declaration%2C%20the%20unprecedented%20fragmentation%20and%20division%20within%20the%20G20%20cast%20significant%20doubt%20on%20its%20normative%20and%20political%20legitimacy%20and%20effectiveness.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20we%20appreciate%20the%20Declaration%E2%80%99s%20inclusion%20of%20an%20extensive%20list%20of%20commitments%2C%20we%20cannot%20help%20but%20harbor%20doubts%20about%20its%20practical%20effectiveness.%20These%20doubts%20stem%20from%20the%20absence%20of%20concrete%2C%20time-bound%20action%20plans%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20an%20independent%20accountability%20and%20monitoring%20mechanism%20to%20assess%20their%20implementation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20has%20been%20an%20undue%20emphasis%20on%20the%20role%20of%20the%20private%20sector%20in%20economic%20development.%20We%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20corporate%20influence%20on%20government%20policies%20and%20multilateral%20organizations%20such%20as%20the%20UN.%20We%20notice%20the%20absence%20to%20a%20reference%20on%20ongoing%20efforts%20in%20several%20G20%20countries%20and%20regions%20(EU%20and%20AU)%20for%20due%20diligence%20laws%20for%20global%20value%20chains%20and%20the%20ongoing%20negotiations%20for%20a%20binding%20treaty%20on%20business%20and%20human%20rights.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENotably%2C%20there%20has%20been%20insufficient%20progress%20on%20critical%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20waiving%20of%20patent%20rights%2C%20which%20obstructs%20access%20to%20vital%20COVID-19%20and%20other%20life-saving%20medications.%20The%20Declaration%20also%20falls%20short%20in%20addressing%20global%20taxation%20and%20a%20UN-based%20tax%20body%2C%20and%20reform%20of%20the%20international%20financial%20architecture%2C%20guided%20by%20principles%20of%20global%20equality%20and%20justice.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20deeply%20disappointing%20to%20witness%20a%20lack%20of%20commitment%20to%20debt%20cancellation%20for%20the%2060%20countries%20that%20are%20most%20severely%20burdened%20by%20their%20debt%20obligations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20that%20the%20Declaration%20has%20largely%20disregarded%20policy%20recommendations%20presented%20by%20Civil%20Society%20Organizations%20(CSOs)%2C%20despite%20the%20dedicated%20efforts%20of%20engagement%20groups%20and%20independent%20CSOs.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20process%20has%20denied%20access%20to%20human%20rights-based%20civil%20society%20and%20trade%20union%20movements%2C%20which%20is%20equally%20troubling.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20express%20profound%20concern%20over%20the%20Declaration%E2%80%99s%20omission%20of%20critical%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20erosion%20of%20civic%20space%20and%20the%20global%20decline%20in%20democracy.%20This%20alarming%20trend%20is%20especially%20pertinent%20in%20several%20G20%20countries%2C%20including%20China%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Russia%2C%20T%C3%BCrkiye%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20India%2C%20as%20highlighted%20by%20CIVICUS%E2%80%99s%20Civic%20Space%20Monitor.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFurthermore%2C%20it%20was%20disappointing%20to%20note%20that%20the%20Declaration%20made%20no%20reference%20to%20vital%20concepts%20such%20as%20democracy%2C%20civil%20society%2C%20and%20youth%2C%20despite%20the%20host%20country%2C%20India%2C%20proudly%20proclaiming%20itself%20as%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2030%20Agenda%20for%20Sustainable%20Development%20and%20the%20SDGs%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%202023%20G20%20Summit%20was%20a%20timely%20opportunity%2C%20situated%20midway%20to%202030%2C%20for%20taking%20stock%20and%20assessing%20global%20progress%20on%20the%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs).%20We%20welcome%20the%20G20%20leaders%E2%80%99%20acknowledgment%20that%20%E2%80%9Cglobal%20progress%20on%20SDGs%20is%20off-track%2C%20with%20only%2012%20percent%20of%20the%20targets%20on%20track.%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20also%20recognize%20the%20G20%20leaders%E2%80%99%20commitment%20to%20leveraging%20the%20G20%E2%80%99s%20convening%20power%20and%20collective%20determination%20to%20fully%20implement%20the%202030%20Agenda%20and%20expedite%20progress%20towards%20the%20SDGs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20while%20much%20was%20discussed%20regarding%20the%20SDGs%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20concrete%20commitment%20to%20the%20500%20billion%20SDG%20Stimulus%20Fund.%20While%20the%20G20%20commits%20to%20supporting%20the%20full%20and%20effective%20implementation%20of%20the%20SDGs%2C%20it%20fails%20to%20propose%20strategies%20that%20can%20effectively%20realize%20these%20targets%20for%20vulnerable%20populations%20that%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20principle%20of%20%E2%80%9Cleave%20no%20one%20behind%E2%80%9D%20was%20not%20effectively%20implemented%2C%20as%20the%20Declaration%20lacked%20specific%20policies%20catering%20to%20the%20rights%20and%20needs%20of%20vulnerable%20and%20marginalized%20groups%2C%20including%20migrants%2C%20indigenous%20peoples%2C%20social%20and%20ethnic%20minorities%20like%20Dalits%2C%20persons%20with%20disabilities%2C%20and%20small-scale%20farmers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20urgently%20call%20upon%20all%20G20%20countries%2C%20particularly%20the%20United%20States%2C%20to%20engage%20more%20actively%20in%20the%20Voluntary%20National%20Review%20(VNR)%20process%20as%20a%20demonstration%20of%20their%20commitment%20to%20aligning%20their%20policies%20with%20the%202030%20Agenda%20for%20Sustainable%20Development%20and%20and%20reporting%20on%20their%20progress%20and%20challenges.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20we%20acknowledge%20the%20G20%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20quality%20and%20cyber%20education%2C%20we%20emphasize%20the%20paramount%20importance%20of%20universal%20basic%20education%20for%20all%2C%20alongside%20the%20significant%20challenges%20posed%20by%20the%20digital%20divide%20both%20within%20and%20among%20countries.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20wholeheartedly%20applaud%20the%20decision%20to%20grant%20permanent%20membership%20to%20the%20African%20Union%20(AU)%20within%20the%20G20%2C%20signifying%20a%20pivotal%20step%20towards%20greater%20inclusivity%20and%20representation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20the%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs)%20aim%20for%20universalizing%2012%20years%20of%20schooling%2C%20the%20G20%20discusses%20foundational%20learning%20and%20does%20not%20commit%20to%20the%20SDG%20targets%2C%20marking%20a%20step%20backward.%20The%20G20%20also%20places%20significant%20emphasis%20on%20technical%20and%20vocational%20education%20and%20digital%20education.%20However%2C%20without%20access%20to%20secondary%20education%2C%20these%20initiatives%20become%20dead%20ends%20and%20do%20not%20adequately%20foster%20youth%20development.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Declaration%20discusses%20facilitating%20migration%20for%20skilled%20workers%2C%20mapping%20skills%20gaps%2C%20and%20providing%20skills%20training%2C%20among%20other%20topics.%20However%2C%20it%20notably%20excludes%20the%20large%20majority%20of%20unskilled%20workers%20from%20the%20global%20south%20who%20migrate%20to%20developed%20countries%2C%20such%20as%20construction%20workers%2C%20domestic%20workers%2C%20and%20plantation%20workers.%20It%20is%20crucial%20that%20facilitation%20and%20protection%20measures%20also%20encompass%20these%20workers%2C%20as%20they%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20by%20sending%20valuable%20remittances%20to%20their%20home%20countries%20and%20serving%20as%20the%20mainstay%20for%20their%20impoverished%20families.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGender%20Equality%20and%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Empowerment%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20declaration%20instrumentalizes%20gender%20equality%20for%20economic%20growth%20instead%20of%20recognizing%20it%20as%20a%20fundamental%20human%20right.%20It%20fails%20to%20acknowledge%20intersectionality%20and%20the%20diversity%20among%20women.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20establishment%20of%20a%20new%20Working%20Group%20on%20the%20Empowerment%20of%20Women%20is%20a%20positive%20development.%20We%20hope%20it%20will%20significantly%20contribute%20to%20expediting%20progress%20towards%20the%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs)%20by%20adopting%20a%20gender-equal%2C%20transformative%2C%20and%20inclusive%20approach%20across%20all%20dimensions%20of%20the%202030%20Agenda.%20We%20also%20hope%20that%20this%20effort%20will%20complement%20the%20work%20of%20UN%20Women%2C%20Women%2020%2C%20and%20collaborate%20with%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Major%20Group%20and%20the%20Women%20and%20Gender%20Constituency%2C%20rather%20than%20creating%20another%20parallel%20process%20that%20consumes%20additional%20time%20and%20resources.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20warmly%20welcome%20the%20commitment%20to%20respect%20religious%20diversity%20and%20tolerance%20(paragraph%2078)%2C%20which%20highlights%20the%20significance%20of%20both%20freedom%20of%20religion%20or%20belief%20and%20the%20rights%20to%20peaceful%20assembly%20and%20freedom%20of%20association.%20Once%20more%2C%20we%20emphasize%20the%20crucial%20need%20for%20an%20explicit%20reference%20to%20human%20rights%20and%20labor%20rights%20conventions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20and%20Nuclear%20Weapons%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20emphasis%20on%20international%20security%20was%20notable%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20glaring%20absence%20of%20attention%20to%20the%20escalating%20military%20expenditures%2C%20arms%20proliferation%2C%20and%20the%20military-industrial%20complex%20among%20G20%20member%20states.%20We%20strongly%20urge%20G20%20countries%20to%20redirect%20currently%20exploding%20military%20spending%20towards%20climate%20loss%20and%20damage%20funds%20and%20the%20SDG%20stimulus%20fund.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20appreciate%20the%20reaffirmation%20of%20the%20inadmissibility%20of%20the%20use%20or%20threat%20of%20use%20of%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20as%20previously%20expressed%20in%20the%20Bali%202022%20Declaration.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20establish%20effective%20implementation%20mechanisms%2C%20such%20as%20a%20No%20First%20Use%20policy%20or%20a%20multilateral%20mutual%20non-use%20and%20non-threat%20commitment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERegrettably%2C%20the%20Declaration%20does%20not%20include%20any%20mention%20of%20the%20ratification%20of%20the%20Treaty%20for%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Nuclear%20Weapons%20(TPNW).%20We%20call%20upon%20all%20six%20nuclear-armed%20G20%20nations%2C%20namely%20China%2C%20France%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20to%20demonstrate%20their%20responsibility%20for%20global%20human%20security%20by%20taking%20meaningful%20action%20on%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollow-up%20and%20Next%20G20%20Summit%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20recognize%20the%20G20%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprovide%20full%20support%20to%20the%20UN%202023%20SDGs%20Summit%20and%20the%20UN%202024%20Summit%20of%20the%20Future.%E2%80%9D%20As%20G20%20countries%20are%20also%20UN%20members%2C%20they%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20their%20leadership%20by%20fulfilling%20their%20obligations%20and%20commitments.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20Brazil%20set%20to%20host%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%202024%20and%20South%20Africa%20in%202025%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20G20%20takes%20immediate%2C%20radical%20action%20on%20the%20climate%20crisis.%20Time%20is%20of%20the%20essence.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECSOs%20strongly%20urge%20G20%20leaders%2C%20especially%20those%20of%20Brazil%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20these%20global%20crises%20and%20challenges%2C%20working%20proactively%20to%20prevent%20their%20recurrence%20in%20partnership%20with%20civil%20society.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAbout%20PEOPLES%3B%2020%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPEOPLES%E2%80%99%2020%20is%20a%20worldwide%20network%20and%20initiative%20composed%20of%20civil%20society%20actors%20and%20organizations%20that%20willingly%20participate%20in%20the%20G20%20summit%20and%20associated%20processes.%20This%20initiative%20was%20formally%20inaugurated%20on%20March%201%2C%202023%2C%20following%20a%20series%20of%20consultation%20meetings%20involving%20CSOs%20in%20India%20and%20from%20around%20the%20world%20who%20have%20been%20actively%20engaged%20with%20the%20G20%20since%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPEOPLES%E2%80%99%2020%20convened%20its%20own%20Assembly%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20August%2023-24%2C%202023%2C%20during%20which%20it%20adopted%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Declaration%20and%20the%20Policy%20Pack%20on%20the%20G20%20Summit.%20This%20package%20encapsulates%20the%20policy%20recommendations%20put%20forth%20by%20CSOs%20and%20citizens%20hailing%20from%20both%20G20%20and%20non-G20%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694418642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08133538%2F2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcivil-society-calls-out-g20-declarations-omission-of-civic-space-erosion-democracy-decline%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20G20%20Declaration%20falls%20short%20in%20offering%20a%20clear%20roadmap%20to%20tackle%20the%20pressing%20concerns%20of%20economic%20inequality%2C%20climate%20crisis%2C%20hunger%2C%20and%20energy%20issues%2C%20Peoples'%2020%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20Bandh%20Today%3A%20Reasons%2C%20Challenges%2C%20Government's%20Action%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20State%20Private%20Vehicles%20Owner%20Association%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-bandh-private-taxis-autos-to-be-off-road-samid-transporters-strike-in-bengaluru-4378457%5C%22%3Ehas%20called%20for%20a%20Bandh%20in%20Bengaluru%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20opposing%20the%20Shakti%20scheme%20--%20one%20of%20the%20five%20pre-election%20guarantees%20of%20the%20ruling%20Congress%2C%20which%20provides%20free%20travel%20to%20women%20on%20government%20buses.%20The%20private%20transport%20operators%20say%20that%20the%20scheme%20eats%20into%20their%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federation%20comprises%20a%20total%20of%2032%20private%20transport%20associations%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20private%20transport%20services%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20available%20during%20the%20strike.%C2%A0The%20Bengaluru%20Airport%20Authority%20has%20also%20advised%20passengers%20to%20make%20necessary%20arrangements%20to%20reach%20the%20airport%20on%20time%20in%20view%20of%20bandh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDuration%20of%20the%20strike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20private%20bus%2C%20taxi%2C%20and%20auto%20unions%20have%20called%20for%20a%20shut-down%20from%20Sunday%20midnight%20to%20Monday%20midnight.%20The%20Bengaluru%20traffic%20police%20has%20issued%20a%20traffic%20advisory%20for%20the%20public%20to%20plan%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20are%20private%20transporters%20protesting%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federation%20has%20called%20for%20bandh%20seeking%20a%20ban%20on%20bike%20taxis%2C%20and%20urging%20the%20government%20to%20extend%20the%20Shakti%20scheme%20to%20private%20buses%20as%20well%2C%20among%20other%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20private%20transporters%20have%20claimed%20that%20they%20have%20been%20negatively%20impacted%20by%20the%20Shakti%20scheme%20and%20that%20the%20state%20government%20has%20not%20fulfilled%20their%20demands%20despite%20repeated%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransport%20Minister's%20response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Transport%20Minister%20Ramalinga%20Reddy%20has%20said%20that%20the%20private%20transport%20union%20is%20demanding%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20as%20compensation.%20%26quot%3BSome%20issues%20are%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20and%20Supreme%20Court...Things%20which%20I%20can%20solve%2C%20I%20have%20taken%20actions%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20news%20agency%20ANI%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20state%20government's%20backup%20plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20Transport%20Department%20has%20made%20alternate%20arrangements%20to%20tackle%20the%20Bandh.%20Transport%20Minister%20Ramalinga%20Reddy%20on%20Sunday%20said%20the%20state%20transport%20department%20is%20preparing%20to%20operate%20numerous%20buses%20on%20the%20bandh%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20assured%20that%20Bangalore%20Metropolitan%20Transport%20Corporation%20(BMTC)%20buses%20have%20been%20arranged%20to%20avoid%20any%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20arranged%20BMTC%20(Bangalore%20Metropolitan%20Transport%20Corporation)%20buses%20for%20school-going%20children%2C%20office-going%20people%20and%20for%20those%20who're%20going%20to%20hospitals.%20BMTC%20has%20arranged%20around%20500%20extra%20buses.%20Nothing%20will%20happen.%20They%20(private%20transport)%20are%20going%20for%20a%20strike%2C%20let%20them%2C%20they%20have%20the%20right%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transport%20minister%20has%20reportedly%20instructed%20officials%20to%20run%20government%20buses%20on%20the%20routes%20to%20schools%20and%20colleges%20in%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20directed%20that%20more%20buses%20should%20be%20arranged%20near%20hospitals%20so%20that%20patients%20do%20not%20face%20any%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolice%20tighten%20security%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20Police%20Commissioner%20B%20Dayananda%20said%20that%20adequate%20security%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20across%20the%20city%20as%20a%20precautionary%20measure%20to%20tackle%20any%20untoward%20incident%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20our%20officials%20including%20senior%20officers%20are%20on%20patrolling%2C%20and%20we%20have%20also%20used%20a%20sufficient%20number%20of%20tracking%20forces%20at%20all%20the%20strategic%20locations.%20We%20have%20also%20spoken%20to%20the%20associations%20who%20are%20participating%20in%20the%20strike.%20They%20would%20be%20assembling%20at%20Freedom%20Park%2C%20where%20the%20protest%20will%20be%20held%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever%20wants%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20road%20can%20stay%20off%2C%20but%20they%20cannot%20force%20anybody%20to%20stay%20off%20the%20road.%20We%20have%20given%20instructions%20and%20if%20an