0src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11122010%2FEfZNZmZUcActHdO.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20National%20Socialist%20Council%20of%20Nagaland%20%E2%80%93%20Isak-Muivah%20(NSCN-IM)%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20on%20Saturday%20(September%209)%2C%20said%20that%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20seven-decade-old%20Naga%20political%20conflict%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fnagaland%2Fno-solution-possible-under-indian-constitution-naga-rebel-group-nscn-im-days-after-resumption-of-talks-2680705%5C%22%3Enot%20possible%20under%20the%20Indian%20constitution%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20without%20a%20separate%20flag%20and%20constitution%20for%20the%20Nagas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20has%20come%20days%20after%20the%20Union%20government%20resumed%20talks%20with%20the%20insurgent%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENSCN-IM%20said%20this%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccoherent%20voice%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20consultative%20meeting%20at%20Mayangkhang%20at%20Senapati%20(in%20Manipur)%20on%20September%208.%20The%20meeting%20was%20held%20to%20apprise%20the%20leaders%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98executive%20steering%20committee%E2%80%99%20about%20developments%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Naga%20political%20issue%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fnagaland%2Fno-solution-possible-under-indian-constitution-naga-rebel-group-nscn-im-days-after-resumption-of-talks-2680705%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20meeting%20concluded%20with%20the%20resolve%20to%20stand%20by%20the%20core%20issues%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Framework%20Agreement%E2%80%99%20signed%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20August%202015%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20NSCN-IM%E2%80%99s%20first%20statement%20after%20the%20Union%20resumed%20talks%20with%20the%20outfit%20on%20August%2025%20in%20Delhi%20in%20which%20its%20general%20secretary%20Thuingaleng%20Muivah%20took%20part.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Naga%20talks%20have%20been%20formally%20resumed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20neighbours%20in%20the%20Manipur%20hills%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-naga-kuki-peace-talks-muivah-nscn-im%5C%22%3Ethe%20Kukis%2C%20have%20begun%20demanding%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseparate%20administration%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fstalemate-in-naga-peace-talks-due-to-centres-lack-of-commitment-nscn-i-m%5C%22%3EStalemate%20in%20Naga%20Peace%20Talks%20Due%20to%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20Lack%20of%20Commitment%3A%20NSCN%20(I-M)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%2014%20this%20year%2C%20celebrated%20as%20Independence%20Day%20by%20the%20NSCN-IM%2C%20Muivah%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-naga-kuki-peace-talks-muivah-nscn-im%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20flag%20and%20constitution%20are%20naturally%20inseparable%20from%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20a%20people.%20It%20is%20universally%20an%20accepted%20truth%20that%20the%20flag%20and%20constitution%20are%20constituent%20parts%20of%20sovereignty.%20There%20is%20no%20ambiguity%20about%20it.%20The%20Indian%20leaders%20understand%20it%20too.%20They%20must%20take%20the%20stand%20to%20speak%20the%20truth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENaga%20groups%20including%20the%20NSCN-IM%20claim%20that%20the%20Nagas%20were%20never%20part%20of%20India%20and%20declared%20%E2%80%9Cindependence%E2%80%9D%20on%20August%2014%2C%201947.%20The%20NSCN-IM%20had%20led%20the%20insurgent%