%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20reactions%20started%20pouring%20in%20with%20users%20praising%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20Indian%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWow.%20We%20cannot%20achieve%20growth%20and%20progress%20without%20peace.%20Hope%20this%20%23UkraineRussianWar%20gets%20over%20soon%20and%20world%20is%20back%20to%20normal%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20one%20user.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20Mr.%20Amitabh%20Cant%20do!%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbsolutely%20epic%2C%20Mr.%20Kant!%20Diplomacy%20as%20powerful%20as%20an%20AK-87%20-%20wielding%20words%20for%20world%20peace...%20Kudos%20to%20the%20entire%20team%20for%20their%20tireless%20efforts%20in%20bringing%20nations%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20third%20user%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-delhi-declaration-what-is-delhi-declaration-all-you-need-to-know-about-consensus-document-4375275%5C%22%3EWhat%20Is%20Delhi%20Declaration%3F%20All%20You%20Need%20To%20Know%20About%20Consensus%20Document%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20Mr%20Kant%20told%20NDTV's%20Vishnu%20Som%20that%20the%20negotiations%20went%20on%20till%20the%20last%20minute.%20He%20explained%20that%20the%20team%20drew%20%26quot%3Bred%20lines%26quot%3B%20of%20each%20country%20and%20then%20worked%20on%20the%20final%20draft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20expected%20that%20we'll%20arrive%20at%20a%20consensus.%20On%20the%20first%20draft%2C%20we%20got%20a%20number%20of%20reactions.%20People%20were%20very%20pessimistic%20about%20consensus%20on%20Russia-Ukraine%20crisis%20because%20all%20multilateral%20and%20bilateral%20forums%20had%20failed%20at%20arriving%20a%20consensus%20during%20the%20last%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20G20's%20adoption%20of%20New%20Delhi%20declaration%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20huge%20win%20for%20India%20against%20the%20backdrop%20o