0against%20the%20internet%20sector%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZhang's%20departure%20ends%20a%20storied%20eight-year%20tenure%2C%20during%20which%20Alibaba%20became%20China's%20largest%20company%20and%20ventured%20into%20new%20arenas%20such%20as%20physical%20retail%2C%20which%20grew%20into%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20fastest%20growing%20businesses.%20An%20Alibaba%20representative%20confirmed%20Zhang's%20departure.%20The%20former%20CEO%20will%20now%20steer%20a%20%241%20billion%20technology%20investment%20fund%20on%20Alibaba's%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cloud%20business%20leadership%20change%20announcement%20may%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20Sachs%20analysts%20including%20Ronald%20Keung%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BInvestors%20will%20be%20focused%20on%20any%20further%20clarity%2Fupdates%20from%20the%20new%20management%20team%20on%20Alibaba%20Group's%20latest%20organizational%20strategies%20and%20capital%20market%20plans%20of%20its%20respective%20subsidiaries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20exit%20coincides%20with%20signs%20the%20company's%20overhaul%20is%20proceeding%20less%20smoothly%20than%20expected.%20Alibaba%20is%20putting%20a%20Hong%20Kong%20initial%20public%20offering%20of%20its%20Freshippo%20grocery%20chain%20on%20hold%20for%20now%20because%20it%20couldn't%20get%20the%20valuation%20sought%2C%20Bloomberg%20News%20reported.%20The%20cloud%20division%20Zhang%20oversaw%20is%20separately%20seeking%20to%20raise%20as%20much%20as%2020%20billion%20yuan%20(%242.7%20billion)%2C%20including%20from%20Chinese%20state%20enterprises%2C%20ahead%20of%20its%20own%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20analysts%20had%20expected%20Zhang%20to%20stay%20and%20steer%20the%20%2411%20billion%20cloud%20business%2C%20which%20provides%20internet%20services%20to%20companies%20globally%20and%20spearheads%20research%20into%20areas%20such%20as%20artificial%20intelligence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20successors%20are%20business%20heavyweights%20credited%20with%20overseeing%20the%20technology%20and%20strategy%20that%20underpinned%20China's%20erstwhile%20most%20valuable%20corporation%2C%20co-founded%20by%20Ma%2C%20Tsai%20and%20Wu%20in%201999%20at%20the%20dawn%20of%20China's%20internet%20industry.%20But%20around%202020%2C%20Alibaba%20found%20itself%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Xi%20Jinping's%20tech%20crackdown%20on%20the%20nation's%20most%20powerful%20private%20firms%2C%20which%20obliterated%20growth%20across%20swaths%20of%20the%20industry%20and%20nixed%20once-aggressive%20expansion%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20regulatory%20uncertainty%2C%20Alibaba%2C%20a%20proxy%20for%20Chinese%20consumption%2C%20has%20struggled%20with%20geopolitics%20and%20a%20weakening%20domestic%20economy.%20It's%20also%20facing%20stiff%20competition%20from%20other%20e-commerce%20platforms%20such%20as%20PDD%20Holdings%20Inc.%20as%20well%20as%20short%20videos%20like%20those%20from%20ByteDance%20Ltd.%2C%20which%20increasingly%20are%20pushing%20into%20online%20commerce%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence%20Says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unexpected%20departure%20of%20Alibaba's%20cloud-unit%20CEO%20and%20chairman%20Daniel%20Zhang%20within%20two%20months%20of%20his%20appointment%20raises%20the%20likelihood%20that%20the%20business's%20new%20partners%20will%20exert%20greater%20influence%20on%20strategic%20cloud%20decisions%20in%20future.%20Bloomberg%20reported%20on%20Sept.%204%20that%20Alibaba%20was%20in%20talks%20to%20raise%20funds%20for%20the%20cloud%20unit%20from%20state-owned%20entities%20in%20China.%20Zhang%20will%20remain%20part%20of%20Alibaba's%20ecosystem%20by%20running%20the%20firm's%20newly%20established%20%241%20billion%20technology%20investment%20fund.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20leadership's%20task%20is%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20follow%20through%20on%20a%20landmark%20restructuring%20aimed%20at%20galvanizing%20Alibaba's%20separate%20businesses.%20With%20the%20overhaul%2C%20Alibaba%20has%20said%20it%20wants%20to%20operate%20as%20a%20true%20investment%20holding%20company%2C%20where%20individual%20units%20can%20seek%20funding%20and%20list%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYale%20alumnus%20Tsai%2C%20a%20deal-maker%20well-liked%20among%20investors%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20handling%20markets%20and%20Alibaba's%20most%20prominent%20backers.%20A%20former%20lacrosse%20athlete%20arguably%20best-known%20in%20America%20as%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20Brooklyn%20Nets%2C%20Tsai%20understands%20the%20business%20intimately%3A%20he%20was%20right%20beside%20Ma%20at%20Alibaba's%20inception%20in%20a%20Hangzhou%20lakeside%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWu%2C%20who%20was%20similarly%20with%20Ma%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20is%20a%20lesser-known%20quantity.%20The%20former%20computer%20science%20major%20is%20credited%20with%20helping%20develop%20the%20company's%20ad%20platform%20and%20the%20PayPal-like%20Alipay%2C%20now%20part%20of%20the%20Ma-backed%20Ant%20Group%20Co.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20establish%20a%20venture%20capital%20firm%20that%20manages%20about%20a%2010%20billion%20yuan%20(%241.4%20billion)%20portfolio%20encompassing%20autonomous%20driving%20and%20software.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Zhang's%20departure%2C%20Wu%20will%20serve%20as%20acting%20chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20cloud%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694413380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-10%2F4lg7if1_jack-ma-bloomberg_625x300_20_October_21.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Falibabas-ex-ceo-resigns-as-jack-mas-lieutenants-take-up-positions-4378791%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alibaba%20Group%20Holding%20Ltd.'s%20former%20chief%20Daniel%20Zhang%2