695%2Cimgsize-34132.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fprateik-babbar-hints-at-jaane-tu-ya-jaane-na-co-star-imran-khans-comeback-says-something-is-cooking%2Farticleshow%2F103568754.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103568754.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPrateik%20Babbar%2C%20Imran%20Khan's%20co-star%20from%20the%20movie%20Jaane%20Tu...%20Ya%20Jaane%2C%20in%20an%20interaction%20with%20Instant%20Bollywood%2C%20opened%20up%20on%20his%20comeback.%20Prateik%20said%20that%20he%20has%20spoken%20to%20Imran%20over%20the%20phone%20and%20it%20was%20good%20to%20hear%20his%20voice.%20He%20further%20added%20that%20everyone%20misses%20him%2C%20and%20even%20though%20he%20had%20given%20up%20hopes%20of%20seeing%20Imran%20act%20again%2C%20he%20now%20thinks%20something%20is%20cooking%20on%20that%20front.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fprateik-babbar-hints-at-jaane-tu-ya-jaane-na-co-star-imran-khans-comeback-says-something-is-cooking%2Farticleshow%2F103568754.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIndia%20Was%20Able%20To%20Find%20A%20Formula%26quot%3B%3A%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20On%20G20%20Delhi%20Declaration%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20on%20Sunday%20hailed%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Declaration%20of%20the%20G20%20members%2C%20saying%20it%20%26quot%3Bundoubtedly%26quot%3B%20represents%20%26quot%3Ba%20diplomatic%20triumph%20for%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20ANI%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Delhi%20Declaration%20is%20undoubtedly%20a%20diplomatic%20triumph%20for%20India.%20It's%20a%20good%20achievement%20because%20right%20until%20the%20G20%20summit%20was%20being%20convened%2C%20the%20widespread%20expectation%20was%20there%20would%20be%20no%20agreement%20and%2C%20that%2C%20therefore%2C%20a%20joint%20communique%20might%20not%20be%20possible%2C%20and%2C%20that%20we%20might%20have%20to%20end%20up%20with%20a%20chairman's%20summary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20on%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20a%20consensus%20had%20been%20built%20on%20the%20New%20Delhi%20G20%20Leaders'%20Summit%20Declaration%20before%20formally%20announcing%20its%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20who%20chaired%20G20%20sessions%20through%20the%20day%2C%20congratulated%20the%20Sherpas%20and%20ministers%20for%20working%20towards%20arriving%20at%20a%20common%20ground%20and%20eventually%20building%20a%20consensus%20among%20all%20G20%20members%20and%20other%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETharoor%20further%20praised%20India%20for%20bringing%20all%20member%20states%20to%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Declaration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20reason%20(for%20lack%20of%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20statement)%20was%20the%20big%20gulf%20between%20those%20who%20wanted%20a%20condemnation%20of%20the%20Russian%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20those%2C%20like%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%20who%20wanted%20no%20mention%20whatsoever%20of%20that%20subject.%20India%20was%20able%20to%20find%20a%20formula%20to%20bridge%20that%20gap%20and%20that%20is%20a%20significant%20diplomatic%20achievement%20because%20when%20there%20is%20a%20Summit%20without%20a%20joint%20communique%2C%20it%20is%20always%20seen%20as%20a%20setback%20for%20the%20chairman%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%20under%20India's%20presidency%2C%20Tharoor%20said%20the%20government%20actually%20made%20it%20a%20'people's%20G20'%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20also%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bruling%20party%26quot%3B%20(BJP)%20to%20turn%20the%20mega%20huddle%20of%20world%20leaders%20into%20an%20%26quot%3Basset%26quot%3B%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20that%20were%20remarkable%20about%20the%20government's%20conduct%20of%20the%20presidency%20was%20that%20they%20did%20something%20that%20no%20previous%20G20%20presidency%20has%20done.%20They%20actually%20made%20it%20a%20nationwide%20event%2C%20200%20meetings%20in%2058%20cities%20with%20huge%20amount%20of%20action%2C%20they%20converted%20the%20G20%20into%20a%20sort%20of%20people%20G20.%20With%20public%20events%2C%20the%20university%20connect%20programmes%2C%20civil%20societies%2C%20all%20these%20things%20were%20done%20under%20our%20presidency.%20That%20is%20in%20some%20ways%20both%20a%20credit%20to%20India%20for%20taking%20a%20message%20of%20G20%20to%20the%20entire%20people.%20But%20it%20was%20also%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20instrumentalize%20the%20G20%20as%20something%20that%20would%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20an%20asset%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20while%20announcing%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%20on%20Sunday%2C%20proposed%20to%20hold%20a%20virtual%20G20%20session%20in%20November%20to%20review%20the%20suggestions%20and%20proposals%20made%20at%20the%20premier%20forum%20for%20international%20economic%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20that%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20every%20right%20to%20do%20that%2C%20they%20are%20the%20ruling%20party.%20Many%20countries%20have%20hosted%20the%20G20%20event%2C%20but%20never%20a%20ruling%20party%20has%20celebrated%20its%20leadership%20in%20such%20a%20way%2C%20the%20whole%20Vishwaguru%20concept%2C%20the%20posters%20of%20Mr%20Modi%20every%2050%20meters%20in%20Delhi.%20All%20of%20these%20are%20advertising%20the%20G20%20as%20if%20it%20was%20the%20personal%20achievement%20of%20Mr%20Modi%