.%20After%20being%20bitten%20several%20times%20on%20the%20chest%20and%20arm%2C%20he%C2%A0went%20into%20cardiac%20arrest.%20Despite%20several%20attempts%20by%20paramedics%20and%20other%20attendees%20to%20revive%20him%2C%20he%20died%20at%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''There%20was%20a%20rapid%20call%20for%20an%20ambulance%20and%20bystanders%20performed%20CPR%20immediately%20as%20the%20man%20collapsed.%20Despite%20heroic%20measures%20by%20both%20the%20bystanders%20and%20the%20Queensland%20Ambulance%20Service%2C%20he%20was%20unfortunately%20unable%20to%20be%20revived%20and%20has%20passed%20away%2C''%20Claire%20Bertenshaw%2C%20the%20Queensland%20Ambulance%20Service's%20acting%20deputy%20commissioner%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20the%20second%20man%2C%20also%20in%20his%2060s%2C%20was%20transported%20to%20Mackay%20Base%20Hospital%20and%20is%20in%20a%20stable%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20other%20fellow%20is%20well%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20last%20night.%20I%20can't%20say%20with%20any%20certainty%20whether%20he%20was%20bitten%20or%20not.%20My%20thoughts%20are%20with%20the%20family%20and%20friends%20of%20the%20patient%20who%20tragically%20lost%20their%20life%20last%20night''%2C%20Ms%20Bertenshaw%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20incident%2C%20tributes%20flooded%20social%20media%20with%20many%20calling%20him%20a%20''good%20friend%20and%20neighbour''%20and%20a%20''hero''%20for%20his%20brave%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%C2%A0not%20known%20what%20type%20of%20snake%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20Dr%20Bertenshaw%20said%20the%20man's%20symptoms%20pointed%20to%20a%20highly%20venomous%20eastern%20brown%20snake.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fnewsweek-com-deadly-snake-intruder-found-airport-1768336%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENewsweek%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0their%20venom%20contains%20a%20powerful%20neurotoxin%2C%20which%20progressively%20paralyzes%20the%20victim's%20nerves%20in%20their%20heart%2C%20lungs%2C%20and%20diaphragm%2C%20eventually%20causing%20suffocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESnake%20bites%20in%20Australia%20are%20relatively%20common%20with%20about%203000%20occurring%20annually%20but%20fatal%20bites%20are%20rare.%20As%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Fnational%2Fqueensland%2Fnews%2Fman-69-killed-while-trying-to-remove-coiled-snake-from-another-mans-leg-in-north-queensland%2Fnews-story%2Fbed8a7bb2d8e5daafd94ac0e8b801ed3%5C%22%3ENews.com.au%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0Queensland%20is%20home%20to%20about%2078%20species%20of%20venomous%20snakes%2C%20although%20only%2012%20are%20considered%20%E2%80%9Cpotentially%20dangerous%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Queensland%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694407680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2F6uia39cg_snake-generic-unsplash_625x300_15_September_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-man-dies-after-being-bitten-by-deadly-snake-he-was-trying-to-save-his-friend-4378535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20several%20attempts%20by%20paramedics%20and%20other%20attendees%20to%20revive%20him%2C%20he%20died%20at%20the%20scene.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-man-dies-after-being-bitten-by-deadly-snake-he-was-trying-to-save-his-friend-4378535%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-man-dies-after-being-bitten-by-deadly-snake-he-was-trying-to-save-his-friend-4378535%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-man-dies-after-being-bitten-by-deadly-snake-he-was-trying-to-save-his-friend-4378535%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Delhi%20Leaders'%20Declaration%20Calls%20for%20Inclusive%2C%20Equitable%20Education%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20outcome%20for%20the%20education%20sector%20from%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20the%20participating%20countries%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Leaders'%20Declaration%20outlined%20an%20ambitious%20education%20plan%20that%20aims%20to%20bring%20about%20significant%20changes.%20They%20called%20for%20inclusive%2C%20equitable%2C%20high-quality%20education%20and%20skills%20training%20for%20all%2C%20including%20those%20in%20vulnerable%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20declaration%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20committed%20to%20inclusive%2C%20equitable%2C%20high-quality%20education%20and%20skills%20training%20for%20all%2C%20including%20those%20in%20vulnerable%20situations.%20We%20recognize%20the%20importance%20of%20investing%20in%20supporting%20human%20capital%20development.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20G20%20countries%20in%20the%20declaration%20have%20also%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20fundamental%20learning%2C%20expressed%20their%20commitment%20to%20narrowing%20digital%20disparities%2C%20and%20pledged%20their%20support%20to%20help%20educational%20institutions%20and%20educators%20adapt%20to%20emerging%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20emphasised%20access%20to%20high-quality%20technical%20and%20vocational%20education%20and%20training%2C%20promoting%20scientific%20cooperation%2C%20and%20facilitating%20lifelong%20learning%2C%20especially%20for%20marginalized%20communities.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20declaration%20emphasises%20equity%2C%20adaptability%2C%20and%20collaboration%20on%20a%20global%20scale%20to%20ensure%20that%20education%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20avenue%20of%20opportunity%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHighlights%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERecognise%20the%20importance%20of%20foundational%20learning%20(literacy%2C%20numeracy%2C%20and%20socioemotional%20skills)%20as%20the%20pr