Fstock-market-live-updates-nse-bse-sensex-nifty-rishabh-instruments-sjvn-share-market-today-123091100066_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Simultaneous%20Elections%3A%20Why%20Now%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16163914%2F2048px-BMC_Election_2012_-_Ink_mark_after_voting_6886404209.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20constitution%20of%20a%20committee%20of%20seven%20chaired%20by%20former%20president%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20to%20make%20recommendations%20on%20simultaneous%20elections%20at%20each%20of%20the%20three%20levels%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20taken%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20concretising%20an%20idea%20which%20had%20featured%20in%20the%202014%20election%20manifesto%20of%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20an%20ex-president%20is%20chairing%20a%20panel%20on%20an%20intensely%20political%20and%20already%20decided%20issue.%20The%20pliable%20president%20has%20been%20a%20feature%20ever%20since%20Fakhruddin%20Ali%20Ahmad%2C%20and%20endorsing%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20stand%20is%20constitutionally%20and%20politically%20problematic.%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%201991%20and%20has%20donated%20his%20ancestral%20home%20in%20Paraunkh%20to%20the%20RSS%2C%20became%20president%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20behest.%20We%20have%20to%20wait%20to%20know%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20other%20seven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20secured%20the%20recommendation%20of%20a%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20simultaneous%20polls%20in%20December%202015.%20However%2C%20the%20committee%20had%20thought%20of%20streamlining%20elections%20into%20two%20phases%20%E2%80%93%20one%20concurrent%20with%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20other%20in%20the%20mid-term%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20at%20two%20levels%2C%20not%20three.%20It%20considered%20such%20a%20reform%20%E2%80%98important%20for%20India%E2%80%99%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20development%20agenda%20to%20compete%20with%20other%20nations.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20has%20responded%20positively.%20Now%2C%20the%20new%20panel%20is%20tasked%20with%20the%20legitimisation%20of%20simultaneous%20elections%20at%20the%20three%20levels%20of%20the%20Union%2C%20states%20and%20local%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20separation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndira%20Gandhi%20broke%20the%20simultaneity%20of%20elections%20after%201971%20to%20neutralise%20the%20satraps%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20decline%20of%20the%20party%20followed%20in%201989-1996.%20But%20the%20%E2%80%98one-party-dominant%20system%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98the%20Congress%20system%E2%80%99%20that%20functioned%20alternately%20in%20governance%20and%20the%20Opposition%2C%20despite%20the%20existence%20of%20several%20ideologically%20diverse%20dynamic%20parties%2C%20fractured.%20It%20caused%20instability%20in%201977-80%2C%201989-90%2C%20and%201996-99%2C%20until%20a%20federalised%20coalition%20system%20emerged%20as%20a%20bipolar%2Fbinodal%20configuration%20around%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20between%201999%20and%202014.%20The%202014%20and%202019%20absolute%20majority%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20a%20two-thirds%20majority%20for%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20crushed%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20Opposition%20strength%20contracted%20to%20a%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Simultaneous%20Polls%20Not%20the%20Panacea%20for%20the%20Ills%20Plaguing%20Indian%20Democracy%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsimultaneous-polls-democracy-india%5C%22%3ESimultaneous%20Polls%20Not%20the%20Panacea%20for%20the%20Ills%20Plaguing%20Indian%20Democracy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%201967%20elections%2C%20unstable%20coalition%20governments%20in%20the%20states%20didn%E2%80%99t%20last%20their%20term%2C%20and%20midterm%20elections%20were%20frequent%20until%201971%2C%20when%20the%20Fourth%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20dissolved%20to%20hold%20a%20mid-term%20poll%20and%20the%20rupture%20in%20simultaneous%20elections%20was%20complete.%20In%201972%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20dissolved%20and%20reelected%2018%20Legislative%20Assemblies.%20The%20extension%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20for%20a%20year%20(1975-76)%2C%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20state%20assemblies%20by%20the%20Morarji%20government%20in%201978%2C%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%20returning%20the%20compliment%20in%201980%2C%20only%20intensified%20it.%20The%20following%20years%20witnessed%20an%20increasing%20scattering%20of%20the%20election%20process%20as%20the%20fracturing%20of%20the%20party%20system%20intensified%20since%201989%3B%20state%2Fregional%20parties%20proliferated%2C%20consolidating%20in%20their%20strongholds%20and%20upping%20their%20stakes%20in%20New%20Delhi%20as%20they%20coalesced%20with%20national%20formations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20in%20India%20have%20thus%20become%20year-round%20%E2%80%98event%20management%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20continual%20exercise%20that%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%2C%20especially%20counting%20local%20body%20elections.%20No%20wonder%20the%20170th%C2%A0report%20(1999)%20of%20the%20Law%20Commission%20of%20India%20suggested%20comprehensive%20political%2C%20institutional%20and%20electoral%20reforms%20along%20with%20measures%20to%20%E2%80%98achieve%20the%20desired%20goal%20of%20one%20election%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20to%20all%20the%20Legislative%20Assemblies%20simultaneously.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20proposal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20NITI%20Aayog%20paper%20in%202017%20argued%20for%20%E2%80%98one%20nation%20one%20election%E2%80%99.%20It%20reasoned%20that%20since%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20system%20the%20legislative%20bodies%20do%20not%20have%20a%20fixed%20tenure%2C%20the%20two%20sets%20of%20elections%20could%20be%20synchronised%20in%20two%20phases%20between%20the%202019%2017th%20general%20election%20and%20the%20midterm%20of%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%202021%2C%20by%20adjusting%20the%20tenure%20of%20legislative%20assemblies.%20In%20case%20of%20a%20midterm%20dissolution%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20could%20be%20a%20provision%20for%20the%20President%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20country%2C%20on%20the%20aid%20and%20advice%20of%20his%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20to%20be%20appointed%20by%20him%20till%20the%20time%20the%20next%20House%20is%20constituted%E2%80%9D.%20With%20the%20local%20bodies%E2%80%99%20elections%20added%20this%20time%20in%20the%20suggested%20process%2C%20major%20constitutional%20issues%20are%20at%20stake%20in%20the%20initiative%2C%20whatever%20the%20proposed%20panel%20of%20loyalists%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Law%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20170th%20Report%2C%20quoted%20to%20justify%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20proposals%2C%20lays%20greater%20emphasis%20on%20the%20reform%20of%20the%20party%20system%20in%20the%20perspective%20of%20the%20proliferation%20and%20weakening%20of%20the%20parties%20and%20deinstitutionalisation%20of%20the%20party%20system.%20Anomalies%20in%20party%20funding%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20electoral%20and%20political%20processes%20are%20highlighted%20and%20streamlining%20is%20suggested.%20If%20undertaken%2C%20these%20would%20strengthen%20the%20party%20system%20and%20remove%20causes%20of%20instability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExperiences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%2C%20what%20prompted%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20to%20push%20for%20simultaneous%20election%20at%20full%20throttle%3F%20International%20and%20Indian%20experiences%20could%20provide%20possible%20answers%2C%20for%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20rationale%20economics%20of%20elections%2C%20time%20management%2C%20better%20coordination%20and%20governance%20is%20not%20credible.%20Let%20us%20begin%20with%20the%20international%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvailable%20evidence%2C%20particularly%20from%20the%20UK%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Argentina%2C%20Canada%2C%20Germany%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20suggest%20that%20simultaneous%20elections%20yield%20more%20aligned%20results%20between%20national%20and%20regional%20elections.%20Simultaneous%20elections%20also%20appear%20to%20contribute%20over%20time%20to%20the%20nationalisation%20of%20party%20systems%20and%20bring%20greater%20cohesion%20in%20them.%20But%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20in%202000%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%20differences%20persisted%20at%20the%20two%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Simultaneous%20Elections%20to%20Parliament%20and%20Assemblies%20is%20Not%20Good%20for%20Democracy%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fparliament-state-assembly-simultaneous-elections-democracy%5C%22%3ESimultaneous%20Elections%20to%20Parliament%20and%20Assemblies%20is%20Not%20Good%20for%20Democracy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20scholar%20and%20journalist%20Pran%20Chopra%20suggested%20in%201999%20that%20%E2%80%98simultaneous%20votes%20of%20no-confidence%20in%20the%20incumbent%20and%20confidence%20in%20the%20alternative%E2%80%99%20would%20be%20%E2%80%98much%20safer%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98would%20eliminate%20the%20need%20for%20a%20mid-term%20poll.%E2%80%99%20Obviously%2C%20if%20the%20political%20reforms%20and%20institutionalisation%20of%20the%20party%20system%20is%20initiated%20by%20this%20government%20with%20the%20active%20support%20and%20participation%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20the%20number%20of%20elections%20would%20certainly%20be%20reduced.%20In%20the%20interim%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20complex%20road-roller%20system%20proposed%2C%20elections%20to%20the%20Legislative%20Assemblies%20each%20year%2C%20as%20also%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%20year%20it%20falls%2C%20could%20be%20clubbed%2C%20making%20the%20process%20annual.%20Slowly%2C%20but%20surely%2C%20simultaneity%20would%20emerge%20with%20stability%20in%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAjay%20K.%20Mehra%20was%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Senior%20Fellow%2C%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%202019-21%20and%20Principal%2C%20Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Evening%20College%2C%20Delhi%20University%20(2018).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694405887000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16163914%2F2048px-BMC_Election_2012_-_Ink_mark_after_voting_6886404209.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsimultaneous-elections-why-now%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Available%20evidence%2C%20particularly%20from%20the%20UK%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Argentina%2C%20Canada%2C%20Germany%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20suggest%20that%20simultaneous%20elections%20yield%20more%20aligned%20results%20between%20national%20and%20regional%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsimultaneous-elections-why-now%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22He%20moved%20from%20Reno%20to%20rural%20Portugal%2C%20bought%20a%20house%20for%20%24300%2C000%2C%20and%20makes%20travel%20videos%20for%20a%20living%3A%20How%20one%20American%20guy%20pieced%20together%20his%20dream%20life%20at%2032%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221297%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20Dave%20Alastair's%20house%20in%20Portugal.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f6d5a87819260019111acd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22972%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20Dave%20Alastair's%20house%20in%20Portugal.%3Cp%3EDave%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDave%20Alastair%20moved%20from%20Reno%2C%20Nevada%2C%20to%20a%20rural%20province