3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20here%20to%20visit%2C%20just%20to%20see%20the%20country%2C%20and%20then%20once%20I%20saw%20it%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20a%20good%20fit%2C%26quot%3B%20Alastair%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHouse-hunting%20in%20Portugal%20wasn't%20that%20difficult%20either%2C%20since%20he%20already%20knew%20what%20he%20had%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20location%20that%20was%20a%20little%20more%20rural%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20something%20that%20was%20big%20enough%20for%20me%20to%20be%20able%20to%20play%20music%20and%20have%20a%20studio%20inside%20for%20my%20YouTube%20stuff%20and%20for%20an%20office%20in%20general%2C%26quot%3B%20Alastair%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHe%20found%20the%20perfect%20quaint%20three-bedroom%20home%20in%20the%20countryside%20after%20looking%20at%20real-estate%20listings%20online.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221297%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20Dave%20Alastair's%20house%20in%20Portugal.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f6d5a87819260019111acd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22972%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20Dave%20Alastair's%20house%20in%20Portugal.%3Cp%3EDave%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20come%20here%20to%20visit%20for%20months%20and%20scouted%20areas%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Alastair%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20been%20here%20a%20total%20of%20about%20three%20months%20before%20I%20purchased%20the%20house.%20I%20had%20been%20in%20the%20south%20and%20in%20Algoz%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20scouring%20online%20platforms%2C%20Alastair%20chanced%20upon%20a%20local%20real%20estate%20agency%20with%20a%20few%20homes%20for%20sale%20in%20the%20area%20he%20was%20looking%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20a%20bunch%20of%20listings%20within%20about%20a%2015%20or%2030-mile%20radius%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20I%20basically%20found%20this%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Alastair%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAlastair%20ended%20up%20buying%20the%20property%20in%20April%202022%20for%20280%2C000%20euros%2C%20or%20%24300%2C000.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227766%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eee95e26dda200194d8ad6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225824%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20room%20has%20a%20pitched%20ceiling.%3Cp%3EDave%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20moved%20into%20his%20new%20home%20in%20July%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bones%20of%20this%20house%20are%20probably%20in%20the%20range%20of%20about%20150%20years%20old%20or%20200%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20Alastair%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20building%20was%20converted%20into%20a%20home%20in%202007%20by%20a%20woman%20from%20Lisbon%2C%20but%20it%20was%20originally%20part%20of%20a%20wine%20vineyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20wine%20warehouse%2C%20basically%20off%20to%20the%20side%20there's%20a%20lagar%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20a%20wine%20mashing%20station%20where%20you%20would%20mash%20the%20wine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BMy%20neighbors%20within%20a%20mile%20have%20tons%20of%20wine%20vineyards%2C%20so%20I'm%20guessing%20this%20was%20all%20wine%20country%20back%20then.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20was%20not%20able%20to%20independently%20verify%20the%20history%20of%20the%20building%2C%20but%20the%20Lisboa%20region%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flondonwinecompetition.com%2Fen%2Fresources%2Fregions-3375%2Fportugal-3388%2Flisboa-80.htm%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLisboa%2520is%2520a%2520winemaking%2520region%2Cfamous%2520are%2520Alenquer%2520and%2520Bucelas.%5C%22%3Eknown%20for%20its%20wine%20production%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20single-story%20home%20has%20a%20bright%20and%20airy%20layout.%20The%20rustic%20interior%20design%20features%20exposed%20bricks%2C%20wooden%20beams%2C%20and%20patterned%20tiles.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228064%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20surf%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eee92726dda200194d8a8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20front%20room%2C%20which%20has%20a%20sauna.%3Cp%3EDave%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20measures%20just%20under%203%2C000%20square%20feet.%20Alastair%20designed%20his%20home%20with%20help%20from%20his%20partner%20Sara.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20front%20room%20is%20where%20Alastair%20stores%20his%20surfing%20and%20biking%20equipment.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20little%20sauna%20where%20he%20relaxes%20after%20a%20long%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20open-concept%20living%20and%20dining%20area%2C%20there's%20a%20loft%20that%20Alastair%20uses%20as%20his%20office.%20Apart%20from%20his%20kitchen%20and%20bedroom%2C%20there's%20a%20guest%20room%20and%20a%20garage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%2C%20he%20grows%20vegetables%20and%20herbs%20in%20the%20garden%2C%20including%20tomatoes%2C%20peppers%2C%20and%20kale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20soil%20is%20very%20fertile%20in%20Portugal%2C%20and%20many%20things%20grow%20here.%20My%20goal%20is%20to%20continue%20to%20scale%20the%20garden%20to%20be%20able%20to%20live%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20off%20of%20this%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20big%20goal%20of%20mine%20in%20finding%20a%20rural%20property%20in%20Portugal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20things%20Alastair%20did%20once%20he%20moved%20in%20was%20install%20glass%20doors%20to%20open%20up%20the%20space%20and%20bring%20light%20into%20the%20house.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222301%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sofas%20in%20the%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eee95326dda200194d8ac2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221726%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20alternate%20view%20of%20the%20living%20room%2C%3Cp%3EDave%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20also%20meant%20that%20he%20was%20able%20to%20see%20out%20to%20the%20pool%20area%20from%20the%20living%20and%20dining%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20building%20was%20old%2C%20another%20major%20task%20that%20Alastair%20had%20was%20to%20protect%20the%20roof%20from%20termites%20and%20water%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20there%20were%20bugs%20in%20the%20roof.%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20there%20was%20any%20water%20damage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20primed%20the%20ceiling%20with%20an%20antifungal%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20everything%20was%20treated%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20that%20it%20was%20also%20kind%20of%20an%20anti-moisture%20primer%20paint%20that%20would%20make%20sure%20that%20everything%20was%20sealed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortugal%20has%20a%20relatively%20humid%20climate%2C%20and%20people%20should%20look%20out%20for%20mold%20when%20buying%20a%20home%20here%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipma.pt%2Fen%2Fagrometeorologia%2Fhumidade%2F%5C%22%3Eaverage%20daily%20humidity%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20go%20up%20to%20over%2080%25.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweather-and-climate.com%2Faverage-monthly-Humidity-perc%2Creno-us%2CUnited-States-of-America%5C%22%3Eaverage%20monthly%20humidity%20in%20Reno%3C%2Fa%3E%20ranges%20between%2036%25%20to%2068%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theportugalnews.com%2Fnews%2F2022-11-26%2Fwhat-causes-mould%2F72393%5C%22%3Eways%20to%20control%20mold%20indoors%3C%2Fa%3E%20include%20venting%20bathrooms%20to%20the%20outside%2C%20as%20well%20as%20adding%20insulation%20to%20walls%20to%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20of%20condensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20house%2C%20it's%20just%20very%20lucky%20the%20way%20that%20it%20was%20built%20and%20as%20old%20as%20it%20is%20that%20it%20controls%20the%20humidity%20as%20well%20as%20it%20does%2C%26quot%3B%20Alastair%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEven%20though%20Alastair%20has%20lived%20in%20the%20house%20for%20over%20a%20year%2C%20he%20still%20has%20some%20renovations%20planned%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20has%20white%20cabinets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eee96296b7920019ca3005%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EDave%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20installing%20solar%20panels%20on%20the%20roof%20and%20then%20switching%20over%20to%20a%20solar%20water%20heating%20system.%20He%20also%20plans%20on%20installing%20a%20battery%20so%20that%20the%20property%20can%20be%20fully%20independent%20from%20the%20power%20grid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPortugal%20is%20such%20a%20sunny%20part%20of%20Europe%2C%20and%20they%20say%20we%20get%20over%20300%20days%20of%20sunshine%20a%20year%20on%20average%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it%20would%20be%20an%20incredible%20opportunity%20to%20get%20the%20power%20from%20the%20sun%20to%20power%20the%20entire%20house%2C%20and%20be%20completely%20self-sustainable%20as%20far%20as%20the%20energy%20goes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20doesn't%20require%20any%20air%20conditioning%20or%20heating%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20thick%20stone%20walls%20that%20help%20regulate%20the%20interior%20temperatures%2C%20Alastair%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20walls%20are%20really%20thick%20%E2%80%94%20I%20would%20say%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20feet%20thick.%20So%20it%20insulates%20pretty%20well%20for%20how%20big%20the%20stone%20house%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBuying%20property%20in%20Portugal%20as%20a%20foreigner%20can%20be%20challenging%20because%20of%20the%20legalities%20of%20the%20process%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228064%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20bedrooms%20in%20the%20house.%20It%20has%20a%20bed%2C%20a%20bedside%20cabinet%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20decorative%20mirror.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eee94926dda200194d8aaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20primary%20bedroom.%3Cp%3EDave%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20having%20a%20really%20good%20lawyer%20by%20your%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Alastair%20said.%20%26quot%3BHere%20in%20Portugal%2C%20they%20don't%20have%20brokerages%20like%20they%20do%20in%20the%20United%20States%20that%20check%20all%20of%20the%20legalities%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20your%20real-estate%20agent%20is%20following%20all%20of%20the%20real%20estate%20laws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20best%20thing%20to%20do%20is%20hire%20a%20lawyer%20to%20check%20the%20property%20and%20the%20paperwork%20for%20you.%20This%20includes%20checking%20for%20any%20liens%20on%20the%20property%20and%20ensuring%20that%20the%20property%20lines%20are%20correctly%20marked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20in%20my%20case%2C%20I%20had%20a%20pool%2C%20and%20it's%20very%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20pool%20is%20legal%20and%20has%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20city%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20seek%20residence%20in%20Portugal%2C%20foreigners%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-moving-to-portugal-golden-visa-d7-overcrowding-housing-costs-2023-5%5C%22%3Eapply%20for%20a%20D7%20visa%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20buy%20property%20in%20the%20country%2C%20foreigners%20also%20need%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-diy-abandoned-farm-portugal-off-grid-youtube-creator-family-2023-8%5C%22%3Eapply%20for%20a%20taxpayer%20identification%20number%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20a%20NIF%20number%2C%20before%20they%20can%20enter%20a%20contract.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAlastair%20says%20that%20while%20his%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20lower%20than%20it%20was%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it's%20only%20because%20he%20lives%20in%20an%20older%20house%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Portugal.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222298%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20dining%20area%20has%20a%20wooden%20bench.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eee94396b7920019ca2ff0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221723%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dining%20area.%3Cp%3EDave%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20about%20owning%20an%20older%20house%20in%20Portugal%20is%20my%20house%20taxes%20are%20significantly%20lower%20here%20because%20it's%20from%20the%20time%20that%20the%20house%20was%20registered%20with%20the%20local%20municipality%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20my%20house%20taxes%20are%20only%20a%20couple%20hundred%20euros%20a%20year%2C%20versus%20a%20house%20that%20would%20be%20newer%2C%20which%20would%20be%20a%20couple%20of%20thousand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20he%20estimates%20he%20was%20paying%20almost%20%241%2C700%20a%20month%20to%20live%20in%20a%20studio%20apartment%20in%20Reno%2C%20Nevada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20now%20if%20you%20live%20in%20Lisbon%2C%20I'd%20say%20things%20would%20be%20pretty%20on%20par.%20The%20rental%20levels%20and%20cost%20of%20living%20now%20in%20Lisbon%20don't%20really%20make%20that%20huge%20of%20a%20difference%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20biggest%20difference%20by%20far%20in%20terms%20of%20cost%20between%20both%20countries%20is%20his%20healthcare%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20healthcare%20is%20the%20biggest%20difference%2C%20in%20Portugal%20I%20pay%20around%2080%20euros%20for%20a%20premium%20insurance%20versus%20in%20the%20United%20States%20for%20not%20the%20best%20one%2C%20I%20was%20paying%20around%20%24500%20monthly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHe%20has%20been%20documenting%20his%20experience%20moving%20to%20and%20living%20in%20Portugal%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228064%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20guest%20bedroom%20comes%20with%20a%20vanity.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eee94f96b7920019ca2ff9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20guest%20bedroom.%3Cp%3EDave%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlastair%20started%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40DaveinPortugal%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20was%20still%20in%20the%20US.%20Back%20then%2C%20it%20was%20a%20place%20for%20him%20to%20share%20about%20his%20travels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20he%20updated%20his%20channel%20with%20the%20news%20about%20his%20move%20to%20Europe%2C%20he%20noticed%20that%20there%20was%20interest%20in%20the%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20he%20started%20filming%20more%20videos%20about%20his%20life%20there%20and%20about%20Portuguese%20culture%20to%20give%20others%20a%20real%20idea%20of%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20live%20in%20the%20European%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20times%20when%20you%20haven't%20been%20to%20a%20place%2C%20you%20get%20these%20romantic%20notions%20of%20what%20you%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20like%2C%20and%20I%20think%20especially%20southern%20Europe%20can%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20difficult%20for%20Americans%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20the%20slow%20pace%20of%20life%2C%20the%20bureaucracy%20that's%20here%20can%20be%20different%20from%20the%20expectations%20they%20previously%20had%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20important%20that%20they%20come%20in%20with%20a%20realistic%20attitude%20and%20expectations%20of%20what%20they're%20really%20going%20to%20be%20experiencing%20when%20they%20come%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20most%20important%20thing%20Alastair%20learned%20about%20moving%20to%20a%20new%20country%20is%20to%20have%20an%20open%20mind.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20loft.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eee92426dda200194d8a88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20loft.%3Cp%3EDave%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20crucial%20to%20integrate%20into%20the%20new%20culture%20to%20feel%20what's%20happening%20in%20the%20country%20and%20to%20develop%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20if%20you%20come%20to%20a%20country%20and%20you%20want%20it%20to%20be%20the%20America%20that%20you%20came%20from%2C%20where%20you're%20just%20trying%20to%20meet%20immigrants%20from%20the%20United%20States%20and%20living%20in%20a%20bubble%2C%20then%20I%20think%20that%20you'll%20be%20disappointed%20and%20unhappy%20with%20the%20lifestyle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%20parts%20about%20living%20in%20Portugal%20is%20that%20he's%20learned%20to%20slow%20down%20and%20enjoy%20life%20and%20the%20company%20of%20the%20people%20around%20him%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221696%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20pushing%20a%20wheelbarrow%20in%20the%20garden.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eee94026dda200194d8aa4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221272%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDave%20in%20his%20garden.%3Cp%3EDave%20in%20Portugal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C