hristian%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20tolerating%20a%20Socialist%20government%20in%20the%20Western%20hemisphere.%20It%20tried%20to%20stall%20the%20Chilean%20Congress%20from%20ratifying%20Allende%20as%20president.%20When%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Facademic.brooklyn.cuny.edu%2Fhistory%2Fjohnson%2F65chile.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactively%20aided%3C%2Fa%3E%20elements%20within%20the%20armed%20forces%20to%20assassinate%20the%20army%20commander-in-chief%20Rene%20Schneider%2C%20a%20staunch%20constitutionalist%2C%20in%20October%201970.%20The%20murder%20rallied%20the%20Chilean%20people%20behind%20Allende%20and%20Congress%20ratified%20him%20as%20president.%20%C2%A0A%20miffed%20U.S.%20ambassador%20in%20Santiago%20informed%20Henry%20Kissinger%2C%20the%20national%20security%20adviser%20to%20President%20Richard%20Nixon%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20Allende%20comes%20to%20power%20we%20shall%20do%20all%20within%20our%20power%20to%20condemn%20Chile%20and%20the%20Chileans%20to%20utmost%20deprivation%20and%20poverty.%E2%80%9D%20That%20was%20Nixon%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20as%20well.%20If%20a%20military%20ouster%20was%20not%20immediately%20possible%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fnsarchive.gwu.edu%2FNSAEBB%2FNSAEBB8%2Fnsaebb8i.htm%5C%22%3Emake%20the%20economy%20scream%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20told%20the%20CIA%20chief%20of%20the%20time%2C%20Richard%20Helms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20was%20hedging%20its%20bets%20on%20an%20economic%20collapse%20but%20the%20Chilean%20economy%20grew%20in%201971%20and%2C%20with%20it%2C%20earnings%20and%20prosperity%20for%20the%20working%20and%20middle%20classes.%20Inflation%20went%20down%20and%20the%20new%20government%20undertook%20a%20whirlwind%20programme%20of%20economic%20and%20social%20reforms.%20Copper%20mines%20and%20banks%20were%20nationalised.%20Thousands%20of%20homes%20were%20built%20and%20state%20spending%20increased%20sharply%20in%20public%20health%2C%20education%20and%20pensions.%20In%20the%20brief%20period%20that%20the%20government%20was%20allowed%20to%20function%2C%20it%20took%20giant%20strides%20in%20tackling%20malnutrition%2C%20illiteracy%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%20in%20expanding%20popular%20culture%20and%20effecting%20land%20reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20boom%20began%20fading%20by%201972%20as%20copper%20prices%20fell.%20The%20multinational%20companies%20that%20produced%20most%20of%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20consumer%20goods%20held%20back%20on%20production%20to%20defeat%20price%20controls%20while%20Washington%20made%20sure%20that%20the%20government%20was%20unable%20to%20secure%20foreign%20investment.%20The%20Soviet%20Union%20largely%20ignored%20Allende%E2%80%99s%20requests%20for%20funds.%20Inflation%20rose%20sharply%20and%20a%20CIA-funded%20strike%20by%20truck%20owners%20dealt%C2%A0a%20crippling%20blow%20to%20the%20floundering%20economy.%20Small%20businessmen%20and%20middle%20class%20professionals%20started%20their%20own%20strikes%2C%20hoping%20to%20bring%20the%20government%20down.%20The%20nation%E2%80%99s%20largest%20daily%2C%3Cem%3E%20El%20Mercurio%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20launched%20a%20no-holds%20barred%20campaign%20against%20Allende%20with%20covert%20U.S.%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2F325163770_3c732c4be3_o.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2F325163770_3c732c4be3_o.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Undated%20photograph%20of%20Salvador%20Allende%20and%20Fidel%20Castro.%20Credit%3A%20Jorge%20Barahona%2FFlickr%20CC%202.0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22717%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2F325163770_3c732c4be3_o.jpg%20717w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2F325163770_3c732c4be3_o-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-10334%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22478%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUndated%20photograph%20of%20Salvador%20Allende%20and%20Fidel%20Castro.%20Credit%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flickr.com%2Fphotos%2Fjbarahona%2F325163770%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJorge%20Barahona%2FFlickr%20CC%202.0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0US%20and%20the%20Chilean%20opposition%20were%20confident%20of%20securing%20a%20two-thirds%20majority%20in%20the%20March%201973%20parliamentary%20elections%20that%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20president.%20Instead%2C%20the%20Popular%20Unity%20coalition%20vote%20share%20went%20up%20by%207%25.%20Washington%20and%20the%20Chilean%20elite%20realised%20that%20Allende%20could%20not%20be%20defeated%20by%20electoral%20means%3B%20the%20stage%20was%20set%20for%20a%C2%A0military%20coup.%20The%20opposition%20used%20its%20majority%20in%20the%20Congress%20to%20stall%20the%20working%20of%20the%20government.%20There%20were%20large%20street%20demonstrations%20organised%20by%20upper%20class%20women%20%E2%80%94%E2%80%9Cthe%20jolly%20ladies%20of%20the%20bourgeoisie%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20Gabriel%20Garcia%20Marquez%20described%20them%20%E2%80%94%20private%20university%20students%20and%20far-Right%20groups.%20Food%20and%20medicine%20disappeared%20from%20the%20shelves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tank%20regiment%20tried%20to%20storm%20the%20presidential%20palace%20in%20August%20but%20was%20repelled%20by%20the%20palace%20guards.%20Augusto%20Pinochet%20was%20appointed%20Army%20chief%2C%20the%20President%20being%20under%20the%20illusion%20that%20he%20was%20on%20his%20side.%20Working%20together%20with%20US%20intelligence%20and%20military%20officials%2C%20the%20Chilean%20armed%20forces%20began%20a%20systematic%20purge%20of%20all%20officers%20who%20were%20against%20a%20military%20takeover.%20On%20the%20morning%20of%20September%2011%2C%20the%20Navy%20mutinied%20in%20the%20port%20city%20of%20Valparaiso.%20Within%20an%20hour%2C%20the%20uprising%20spread%20to%20Santiago%2C%20with%20the%20military%20closing%20down%20most%20radio%20and%20television%20stations%20and%20declaring%20themselves%C2%A0in%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20was%20isolated%20and%20unaware%20of%20his%20total%20loss%20of%20control.%20He%20thought%20Pinochet%20had%20been%20taken%20prisoner%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20he%20was%20directing%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20palace.%20Allende%20was%20offered%20an%20aircraft%20to%20take%20him%20out%20of%20the%20country%20but%20he%20refused%2C%20which%20was%20just%20as%20well%20because%20recorded%20radio%20intercepts%20reveal%20Pinochet%20giving%20the%20order%20that%20the%20aircraft%20would%20have%20to%20be%20brought%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20palace%20was%20bombed%20at%2011%20a.m.%20Allende%20still%20had%20time%20for%20one%20last%20speech.%20Facing%20imminent%20death%2C%20he%20said%20in%20a%20crackling%20radio%20broadcast%20that%20when%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20calm%20metal%20of%20my%20voice%20will%20no%20longer%20reach%20you%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20would%20like%20to%20be%20remembered%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20man%20of%20dignity%20who%20was%20loyal%20to%20his%20country%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Csooner%20rather%20than%20later%2C%20the%20great%20avenues%20will%20open%20again%20and%20free%20men%20will%20walk%20through%20them%20to%20construct%20a%20better%20society%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllende%20and%20a%20small%20group%20resisted%20the%20military%20till%20almost%20the%20very%20end%2C%20the%20President%20finally%20killing%20himself%20in%20his%20office%20with%20the%20AK-47%20that%20Fidel%20Castro%20had%20gifted%20him%20at%20the%20start%20of%20his%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20coup%20heralded%20a%20wave%20of%20arbitrary%20killings%2C%20detentions%20and%20torture%20of%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Chileans.%20Military%20death%20squads%2C%20known%20as%20caravans%20of%20death%2C%20scoured%20the%20country%20for%20anyone%20associated%20with%20the%20Allende%20regime.%20Thousands%20ended%20up%20in%20unmarked%20mass%20graves%2C%20many%20in%20the%20inhospitable%20Atacama%20desert%2C%20where%20family%20members%20still%20search%20for%20their%20remains.%20Concentration%20camps%20and%20torture%20centres%20were%20set%20up%20in%20military%20installations%2C%20football%20stadiums%20like%20the%20one%20which%20hosted%20the%20recent%20Copa%20America%20and%20even%20on%20the%20Navy%20ship%20%3Cem%3ELa%20Esmeralda%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%2C%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20goodwill%20ambassador%20on%20the%20high%20seas%2C%20dropped%20anchor%20at%20Kochi%20(2008)%20and%20Mumbai%20(2012).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20to%20die%20from%20a%20heart%20attack%20brought%20on%20by%20torture%20was%20the%20father%20of%20the%20current%20Chilean%20President%2C%20Michele%20Bachelet%2C%20an%20Air%20Force%20General%2C%20at%20a%20military%20academy%20headed%20by%20his%20closest%20friend%20whose%20daughter%2C%20Evelyn%2C%20was%20the%20presidential%20candidate%20for%20the%20Right%20at%20the%20last%20elections.%20The%20two%20girls%20were%20childhood%20friends%20at%20the%20same%20military%20base%20and%20their%20fathers%20shared%20a%20passion%20for%20classical%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPinochet%E2%80%99s%20military%20dictatorship%20served%20as%20the%20staging%20ground%20for%20a%20neo-liberal%20reordering%20of%20the%20Chilean%20economy%20just%20at%20the%20time%20Reagan%20and%20Thatcher%20were%20evangelising%20the%20doctrine%20as%20an%20antidote%20to%20failed%20Communism.%20The%20result%20has%20been%20a%20deeply%20unequal%20society%20where%20poverty%20has%20been%20pushed%20to%20the%20margins%20and%20concealed%20from%20the%20outsiders%20by%20the%20glitter%20of%20its%20city%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20decades%20might%20seem%20like%20a%20long%20time%20to%20drag%20things%20out%20of%20the%20past%2C%20but%20people%20across%C2%A0Latin%20America%20commemorate%20the%20date%20as%20living%20history%2C%20not%20the%20least%20because%20the%20Chilean%20template%20is%20still%20being%20used%20to%20destabilise%20every%20progressive%20government%20in%20the%20region%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20that%20of%20Venezuela%2C%20Ecuador%2C%20Bolivia%2C%20Argentina%20or%20Brazil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20their%209%2F11%2C%20their%20moment%20of%20terror%20unfolding%20from%20the%20skies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694403929000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2F3943300954_1c19b03cef_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-day-chileans-and-the-rest-of-latin-america-remember-their-911%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pinochet%E2%80%99s%20military%20dictatorship%20served%20as%20the%20staging%20ground%20for%20a%20neo-liberal%20reordering%20of%20the%20Chilean%20economy%20just%20at%20the%20time%20Reagan%20and%20Thatcher%20were%20evangelising%20the%20doctrine%20as%20an%20antidote%20to%20failed%20Communism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22America%E2%80%99s%20First%20Date%20with%209%2F11%20Was%20Not%20on%20US%20Soil%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F10163513%2Fchile-9-11.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20September%2011%2C%202018%20and%20was%20republished%20on%20September%2011%2C%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20in%20New%20York%20on%20September%2011%2C%202001.%20On%20my%20way%20to%20work%20from%20Queens%20to%20midtown%20Manhattan%20that%20morning%2C%20I%20was%20changing%20trains%20at%20the%20Queensborough%20Plaza%20metro%20station%20as%20I%20did%20each%20day.%20On%20the%20station%20platform%2C%20I%20saw%20some%20people%20peering%20into%20the%20distance%20and%20heard%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98smoke%E2%80%99%20mentioned%20several%20times.%20On%20the%20train%20I%20heard%20no%20more%20of%20that%2C%20and%20did%20not%20think%20about%20it%20again%20till%20I%20reached%20my%20office%20a%20few%20minutes%20before%209%20am.%20My%20secretary%20met%20me%20at%20the%20door%20to%20tell%20me%20about%20a%20horrible%20accident.%20Apparently%20a%20plane%20had%20suddenly%20lost%20altitude%20and%20crashed%20into%20the%20World%20Trade%20Centre.%20She%20told%20me%20the%20news%20was%20all%20over%20TV.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20rang%20up%20home%20to%20tell%20my%20wife%20about%20the%20freak%20%E2%80%98accident%E2%80%99.%20She%20said%20she%20would%20check.%20A%20couple%20of%20minutes%20later%2C%20she%20called%20back%20breathlessly.%20Another%20plane%20had%20rammed%20into%20one%20of%20the%20towers%20even%20as%20she%20was%20switching%20on%20the%20TV.%20Thick%20smoke%20was%20billowing%20out%20of%20the%20towers%20and%20the%20fire%20seemed%20to%20be%20spreading%20rapidly.%20She%20sounded%20stunned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F06161849%2F1008x567.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221008%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F06161849%2F1008x567.jpg%201008w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F06161849%2F1008x567-300x169.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-287165%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22567%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20Brooklyn%20bridge%20in%20the%20foreground%2C%20a%20plane%20explodes%20after%20hitting%20the%20second%20tower%20of%20the%20World%20Trade%20Centre%20as%20the%20other%20tower%20burns%2C%20in%20New%20York%2C%20September%2011%2C%202001.%20Credit%3A%20Reuters%2FSara%20K.%20Schwittek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithin%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20the%20news%20was%20everywhere.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EA%20little%20later%2C%20there%20was%20report%20of%20the%20attack%20at%20the%20Pentagon.%20It%20was%20chaos.%20The%20New%20York%20metro%20shut%20down%2C%20something%20it%20very%20rarely%20did.%20I%20worried%20for%20my%20daughter%20who%20was%20a%20ninth-grader%20at%20a%20school%20in%20far-away%20Bronx%20and%20who%20commuted%20by%20the%20school%20bus.%20Was%20she%20going%20to%20be%20safe%3F%20I%20called%20the%20school%20and%20could%20reach%20someone%20after%20several%20attempts.%20A%20calming%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Evoice%20told%20me%20that%20every%20child%20would%20be%20taken%20care%20of%2C%20the%20school%20would%20make%20sure%20that%20she%20reached%20home%20safe%2C%20and%20would%20I%20please%20not%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ecall%20the%20school%20again%20because%20they%20were%20being%20swamped%20with%20telephone%20enquiries.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20I%20felt%20relieved.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%209%2F11%20attack%20brought%20mayhem%20but%2C%20remarkably%2C%20New%20York%20managed%20to%20rally%20in%20the%20crisis%20quickly%20enough.%20The%20metro%20resumed%20working%20in%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20although%20on%20a%20truncated%20route%3B%20my%20daughter%20was%20dropped%20off%20at%20home%20by%20the%20school%20bus%20like%20everyday%20else%2C%20though%20somewhat%20late%3B%20New%20Yorkers%20remained%20civil%20to%20one%20another%20and%20there%20were%20countless%20cases%20of%20people%20going%20out%20of%20their%20way%20to%20help%20others%2C%20often%20at%20great%20personal%20cost%20to%20themselves%3B%20and%20xenophobia%20was%20hardly%20in%20evidence%20anywhere%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20days%20immediately%20following%20the%20tragedy.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20that%20was%20destined%20to%20change%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20however.%20While%20%E2%80%9C(t)he%20world%20merely%20saw%20a%20particularly%20dramatic%20terror%20attack%20with%20a%20vast%20number%20of%20victims%20and%20(perhaps)%20a%20momentary%20public%20humiliation%20of%20the%20USA%E2%80%9D%2C%20President%20George%20W.%20Bush%20announced%20that%20September%2011%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ehad%20changed%20%3Ci%3Eeverything%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cin%20doing%20so%2C%20actually%20%3Ci%3Edid%20%3C%2Fi%3Echange%20everything%2C%20by%20in%20effect%20declaring%20(the%20USA)%20the%20single-handed%20protector%20of%20a%20world%20order%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20White%20House%20declared%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20global%20struggle%20to%20the%20death%20between%20the%20causes%20of%20God%20and%20Satan%20were%20now%20taking%20place%20one%20again%E2%80%9D%3B%20soon%20enough%2C%20%E2%80%9Creal%20life%20(began%20to)%20imitate(d)%20Hollywood%20spectaculars%E2%80%9D.%20Afghanistan%20and%20Iraq%20were%20invaded%20in%20quick%20succession%3B%20the%20Middle%20East%20plunged%20in%20its%20worst-ever%20crisis%20from%20which%20it%20has%20not%20managed%20to%20recover%20in%20nearly%20two%20decades%20yet%3B%20Bush%2C%20incredibly%2C%20had%20himself%20photographed%20against%20a%20giant%20%E2%80%9CMission%20Accomplished%E2%80%9D%20banner%20and%20retired%20in%20triumph%20to%20his%20Texas%20ranch%2C%20leaving%20much%20of%20the%20world%20in%20flames%20and%20proud%20of%20his%20legacy%20that%20consisted%20of%20such%20monstrosities%20as%20the%20USA%20PATRIOT%20Act%20%E2%80%93%20the%20hilarious%20American%20acronym%20for%20%3Ci%3EUniting%20and%20Strengthening%20America%20by%20Providing%20Appropriate%20Tools%20Required%20to%20Intercept%20and%20Obstruct%20Terrorism%20%3C%2Fi%3EAct%2C%202001%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20crippling%20impact%20on%20international%20trade%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Eis%20yet%20to%20fully%20run%20its%20course.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20had%20changed%20irrevocably.%20But%20had%20it%20really%3F%20Was%20US%20liberalism%20of%20the%201990s%20the%20real%20thing%2C%20or%20was%20it%20only%20a%20brief%20interregnum%3F%20Did%20Vietnam%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%93%20the%20tiny%20country%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20world%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20military%20power%20had%20peppered%20with%20more%20bombs%20than%20all%20the%20combatants%20of%20World%20War%20Two%20together%20had%20dropped%20upon%20one%20another%20over%206%20years%20%E2%80%93%20define%20the%20US%20or%20was%20it%20an%20aberration%3F%20What%20does%20American%20policy%20on%20Latin%20America%20tell%20us%3F%20What%20happened%20in%20Chile%20on%2011%20September%2C%201973%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EChile%2C%201970-1973%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F06134400%2Fsalvador_allende_fidel_castro.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22789%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F06134400%2Fsalvador_allende_fidel_castro.jpg%20789w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F06134400%2Fsalvador_allende_fidel_castro-300x167.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-287083%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESalvador%20Allende%20with%20Fidel%20Castro.%20Credit%3A%20Wikipedia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20before%20Salvador%20Allende%2C%20leader%20of%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20Socialist%20Party%2C%20took%20over%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20Marxist%20president%20in%20November%2C%201970%2C%20alarm%20bells%20had%20started%20ringing%20in%20Washington.%20Indeed%2C%20successive%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3EAmerican%20administrations%2C%20Republican%20as%20well%20as%20Democratic%2C%20had%20been%20heavily%20invested%20in%20the%20anti-Allende%20campaign%20in%20four%20successive%20presidential%20elections%20in%201952%2C%201958%2C%201964%20and%201970%2C%20as%20the%201975%20report%20of%20the%20Frank%20Church%20Committee%20of%20the%20US%20Congress%20was%20to%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ereveal%20later.%20The%20CIA%20had%20in%20fact%20spent%20more%20money%20%3Ci%3Eper%20capita%20%3C%2Fi%3Ein%20the%201964%20Chilean%20elections%20than%20did%20the%20Democratic%20and%20Republican%20campaigns%20together%20in%20that%20year%E2%80%99s%20US%20presidential%20hustings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlone%20among%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Emajor%20South%20American%20countries%2C%20Chile%20had%20a%20long%2C%20unbroken%20tradition%20of%20political%20democracy%20going%20back%20to%201927.%20Besides%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20social%20and%20cultural%20life%20had%20strong%20progressive%20elements%20that%20often%20raised%20the%20hackles%20of%20conservatives%20in%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20neighbours.%20Since%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20the%20US%20had%20been%20relentlessly%20expanding%20its%20sphere%20of%20influence%20in%20Latin%20America%2C%20and%20nearly%20every%20dictatorship%20in%20the%20region%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20in%20Bolivia%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Paraguay%2C%20Uruguay%20or%20Argentina%20%E2%80%93%20owed%20its%20allegiance%20to%20the%20bosses%20in%20the%20US%20who%20propped%20up%20their%20brutal%20regimes%20by%20generous%20financial%20and%20military%20support.%20In%20turn%2C%20these%20countries%20had%20allowed%20American%20business%20and%20US%20finance%20capital%20unlimited%20access%20to%20their%20markets%20and%20natural%20resources.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChile%2C%20with%20its%20vibrant%20socialist%20and%20workers%E2%80%99%20movements%2C%20was%20a%20thorn%20in%20the%20US%E2%80%99%20flesh%2C%20and%20it%20was%20with%20rising%20dismay%20that%20President%20Richard%20Nixon%20looked%20on%20as%20the%20September%2C%201970%20elections%20played%20out%20in%20Chile.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAllende%E2%80%99s%20margin%20of%20victory%20being%20slim%2C%20his%20election%20as%20president%20required%20Congressional%20ratification.%20Well%20before%20that%20could%20happen%2C%20Nixon%20had%20agreed%20with%20his%20National%20Security%20Advisor%2C%20Henry%20Kissinger%2C%20that%20the%20US%20could%20not%20%E2%80%9Clet%20Chile%20go%20down%20the%20drain%E2%80%9D.%20Allende%E2%80%99s%20strong%20socialist%20credentials%20struck%20fear%20in%20conservative%20hearts%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20Communist%20Party%2C%20too%2C%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20coalition%20that%20Allende%20headed%20made%20matters%20even%20worse.%20An%20interagency%20group%20called%20%E2%80%98The%2040%20Committee%E2%80%99%2C%20chaired%20by%20Kissinger%2C%20was%20quickly%20formed%20with%20the%20mandate%20to%20coordinate%20and%20oversee%20covert%20sabotage%20operations%20in%20Santiago%20that%20would%20frustrate%20Allende%E2%80%99s%20bid%2C%20if%20necessary%20by%20engineering%20a%20military%20coup.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%2C%20under%20intense%20international%20pressure%2C%20the%20Bill%20Clinton%20administration%20was%20obliged%20in%201999-2000%20to%20declassify%20and%20release%20some%20documents%20relating%20to%20the%20US%20intelligence%20operations%20in%20Chile%2C%20many%20chilling%20details%20came%20to%20light%20of%20a%20sinister%20project%20of%20subversion%20and%20terror.%20The%20CIA%20funded%20and%20coordinated%20a%20plot%20to%20kidnap%20General%20Schneider%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Chilean%20army%20who%20had%20refused%20to%20conspire%20against%20the%20elected%20president.%20Schneider%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20botched%20operation%2C%20and%20the%20CIA%20is%20on%20record%20with%20having%20helped%20the%20kidnappers%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20humanitarian%20reasons%E2%80%9D%20to%20flee%20to%20the%20US.%20Having%20failed%20to%20stop%20Allende%E2%80%99s%20inauguration%2C%20Nixon%20urged%20Kissinger%20to%20make%20the%20Chilean%20economy%20%E2%80%98scream%E2%80%99%2C%20so%20that%20Allende%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20did%20not%20spread%20like%20a%20contagious%20disease%20to%20the%20US%E2%80%99%20vassal%20states.%20Nixon%20also%20approved%20generous%20grants%20to%20several%20anti-Allende%20political%20formations%20and%20business%20enterprises.%20Thus%2C%20large%20sums%20of%20money%20were%20pumped%20into%20the%20staunchly%20right-wing%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3EEl%20Mercurio%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3EChile%E2%80%99s%20largest%20media%20conglomerate%2C%20which%20stepped%20up%20on%20its%20campaign%20of%20misinformation%20and%20propaganda%20against%20the%20new%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAllende%20set%20about%20his%20task%20of%20laying%20the%20foundation%20of%20an%20egalitarian%20society%20in%20right%20earnest.%20Land%20reforms%20were%20set%20in%20motion%20with%20large%20%3Ci%3Elatifundias%20%3C%2Fi%3Ebeing%20disbanded%3B%20copper%20mining%20%E2%80%93Chile%E2%80%99s%20largest%20industry%20and%20its%20biggest%20exporter%20%E2%80%93%20was%20nationalised%20(including%20the%20US%20copper%20giant%2C%20%3Ci%3EAnaconda%3C%2Fi%3E)%3B%20social%20security%20cover%20was%20extended%20to%20nearly%20the%20entire%20population%20in%20stages%3B%20the%20health-care%20sector%20was%20significantly%20strengthened%20with%20mothers%20and%20new-borns%20being%20accorded%20priority%3B%20vast%20swathes%20of%20the%20population%20lying%20beyond%20the%20reach%20of%20formal%20education%20were%20covered%20by%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eextensive%20literacy%20drives%3B%20real%20wages%20of%20workers%20rose%20and%20minimum%20wages%20were%20legislated%3B%20the%20income%20tax%20system%20was%20rationalised%3B%20milk%20and%20midday%20meals%20were%20introduced%20in%20all%20schools.%20Unemployment%20and%20inflation%20rates%20fell%20significantly%20while%20GDP%20and%20industrial%20production%20expanded%20in%20substantial%20measure.%20The%20government%20also%20began%20supporting%20new%20cultural%20initiatives%20and%20subsidised%20the%20printing%20and%20distribution%20of%20the%20treasures%20of%20Chilean%20and%20world%20literature%20for%20mass%20consumption.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20made%20a%20strong%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20US%E2%80%99%20eyes%2C%20defiant%20%E2%80%93%20political%20statement%20by%20establishing%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20Cuba.%20In%201971%2C%20Fidel%20Castro%20came%20on%20a%20rare%20state%20visit%20to%20Chile%20and%20toured%20the%20country%20extensively%2C%20to%20rousing%20reception%20everywhere%2C%20and%20was%20deeply%20impressed%20by%20Allende%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20build%20a%20socialist%20society%20by%20entirely%20peaceful%20means.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20this%20brought%20a%20restive%20US%20administration%20to%20the%20end%20of%20its%20tether.%20Kissinger%2C%20soon%20to%20win%20the%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%2C%20was%20now%20obliged%20to%20fall%20back%20upon%20his%20%E2%80%98Track%202%E2%80%99%20option%20%E2%80%93%20that%20of%20frank%20disruption.%20He%20famously%20said%20that%20if%20the%20Chileans%20did%20not%20know%20what%20was%20good%20for%20their%20country%2C%20the%20US%20%E2%80%93%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20had%20not%20merely%20to%20show%20it%20to%20them%2C%20but%20%3Ci%3Edo%20%3C%2Fi%3Eit%20for%20them%20too.%20A%20senior%20CIA%20operative%20put%20it%20succinctly%3A%20%E2%80%9C%20We%20cannot%20ignite%20the%20world%20if%20Chile%20itself%20is%20a%20placid%20lake.%20The%20fuel%20for%20the%20fire%20must%20come%20from%20within%20Chile.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20station%20(the%20CIA%E2%80%99s%20Santiago%20station)%20should%20employ%20every%20stratagem%E2%80%A6.%20to%20create%20this%20internal%20resistance%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20the%20fuse%20was%20lit%20in%201972.%20Disaffected%20groups%20in%20the%20army%20were%20funded%20and%20strongly%20encouraged%20to%20revolt%3B%20production%20in%20many%20industrial%20units%20was%20systematically%20cut%20back%2C%20even%20sabotaged%2C%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eby%20buying%20off%20groups%20of%20supervisors%20and%20technocrats%20who%20in%20any%20case%20hated%20Allende%E2%80%99s%20pro-poor%20initiatives%3B%20artificial%20shortages%20were%20created%20across%20many%20essential%20industrial%20and%20consumer%20items%20by%20bribing%20dealers%20and%20wholesalers%3B%20a%20marathon%20truckers%E2%80%99%20strike%20was%20orchestrated%20across%20Chile%20to%20further%20exacerbate%20these%20shortages%3B%20the%20judiciary%E2%80%99s%20deeply-entrenched%20prejudices%20against%20social%20change%20were%20worked%20on%20to%20bring%20them%20into%20open%20hostility%20to%20the%20government%3B%20numerous%20strikes%20were%20provoked%20through%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eunabashed%20manipulation%20of%20local%20discontent%20over%20something%20or%20the%20other%3B%20and%20the%20urban%20middle%20class%2C%20exposed%20to%20a%20torrent%20of%20virulent%20misinformation%20about%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20as%20well%20as%20its%20intent%2C%20began%20to%20clamour%20for%20change.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdl%3EHistory%20will%20not%20absolve%20the%20Nixon%20administration%20of%20its%20crime%20in%20Chile%2C%20just%20as%20it%20will%20not%20absolve%20al-Qaeda%20of%20its%20outrage%20on%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fdl%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20did%20not%20help%20that%2C%20world-wide%2C%20there%20was%20at%20this%20point%20a%20steep%20drop%20in%20copper%20prices%2C%20hitting%20export%20earnings%20badly.%20The%20US%20had%20already%20cut%20off%20its%20aid%20lines%20to%20Chile%20and%20had%20also%20prevailed%20upon%20the%20multilateral%20credit%20agencies%20like%20the%20IMF%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20The%20entire%20opposition%20ganged%20up%20against%20Allende%20demanding%20major%20policy%20reorientations%20and%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20top%20court%20played%20along%20helpfully.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHemmed%20in%20from%20all%20sides%2C%20Allende%20started%20making%20concessions%20to%20vested%20interests%2C%20notably%20the%20army.%20On%2029%20June%2C%201973%2C%20Lt%20Col.%20Roberto%20Souper%20led%20a%20coup%20and%20encircled%20the%20presidential%20palace%20with%20his%20tanks.%20The%20coup%20was%20beaten%20back%2C%20but%20General%20Carlos%20Prats%2C%20the%20Commander%20of%20the%20Chilean%20army%20and%20the%20Interior%20Minister%20who%20helped%20disarm%20the%20rebels%2C%20was%20soon%20embroiled%20in%20a%20controversy%20fomented%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eby%20the%20CIA%20and%20had%20to%20resign%20his%20position.%20On%2023%20August%2C%20General%20Augusto%20Pinochet%20who%2C%20unknown%20to%20the%20president%2C%20had%20already%20cut%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20CIA%2C%20managed%20to%20have%20himself%20installed%20as%20Prat%E2%80%99s%20successor.%20The%20last%20hurdle%20in%20the%20conspirators%E2%80%99%20path%20had%20now%20been%20removed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F06133933%2Ftrain2-1024x640.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F06133933%2Ftrain2-1024x640.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F06133933%2Ftrain2-300x188.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F06133933%2Ftrain2.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-287075%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22525%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20last%20known%20photograph%20of%20Allende%20alive%2C%20La%20Moneda%20Palace%2C%20September%2011%2C%201973.%20Credit%3A%20Wikipedia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPinochet%20moved%20swiftly%20and%2C%20on%2011%20September%2C%20the%20day%20Allende%20was%20scheduled%20to%20address%20the%20nation%20on%20the%20burgeoning%20crisis%2C%20he%20struck%20early%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20deploying%20army%20units%20to%20capture%20all%20vital%20installations%20and%20government%20buildings%20across%20Santiago%20at%20lightning%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20gunfire%20raged%20around%20the%20city%20centre%2C%20Pinochet%20called%20upon%20Allende%20to%20surrender.%20Allende%20refused.%20He%20declined%20an%20offer%20of%20safe%20passage%20also%2C%20vowing%20to%20die%20fighting%20at%20his%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20268px)%2085vw%2C%20268px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F10163727%2F1101730924_400-1-228x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22268%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F10163727%2F1101730924_400-1-228x300.jpg%20228w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F10163727%2F1101730924_400-1.jpg%20400w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-288609%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22353%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20September%2024%2C%201973%2C%20cover%20of%20TIME%20magazine.%20Credit%3A%20TIME%2FWikipedia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20presidential%20palace%20began%20to%20be%20heavily%20shelled%20by%20rebel%20artillery%2C%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20socialist%20president%20bade%20goodbye%20to%20his%20countrymen%20in%20a%20radio%20address%20broadcast%20live.%20His%20last%20message%20was%20one%20of%20hope%2C%20rather%20than%20of%20despair%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWorkers%20of%20my%20country!%20I%20have%20faith%20in%20Chile%20and%20its%20destiny.%20Other%20men%20will%20overcome%20this%20dark%20and%20bitter%20moment%20when%20treason%20seeks%20to%20prevail.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%2C%20much%20sooner%20than%20later%2C%20the%20great%20avenues%20will%20again%20be%20opened%20through%20which%20will%20pass%20free%20men%20to%20build%20a%20better%20society.%20Long%20live%20Chile!%20Long%20live%20the%20people!%20Long%20live%20the%20workers!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20president%20and%20his%20bodyguards%20fought%20a%20hopeless%20but%20brave%20battle%20for%20some%20hours%2C%20until%20Allende%20decided%20to%20take%20his%20own%20life%20sometime%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20using%20a%20gun%20gifted%20to%20him%20by%20his%20friend%20Castro.%20Augusto%20Pinochet%2C%20the%20CIA%E2%80%99s%20darling%2C%20soon%20assumed%20power%20and%20unleashed%20a%20reign%20of%20repression%20and%20terror%20that%20lasted%20for%2017%20years.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20were%20killed%20or%20%E2%80%98disappeared%E2%80%99%3B%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20were%20jailed%20and%20tortured%20while%20many%20chose%20exile%20instead%3B%20and%20Milton%20Friedman%E2%80%99s%20free-market%20zealots%20ran%20riot%20over%20Chile%E2%80%99s%20economic%20landscape%20to%20reduce%20the%20country%20to%20a%20shambles.%20Within%20years%2C%20Chile%20became%20one%20of%20the%20most%20unequal%20societies%20in%20the%20whole%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20must%20rank%20as%20one%20of%20history%E2%80%99s%20great%20ironies%20that%20the%20US%20suffered%20its%20most%20deadly%20enemy%20attack%20in%20six%20decades%20on%20a%20date%20it%20had%20chosen%20to%20unseat%20a%20democratically-elected%20government%20in%20a%20proud%20republic.%20The%20sins%20of%20a%20generation%2C%20it%20is%20said%2C%20are%20often%20visited%20on%20its%20own%20progeny.%20Salvador%20Allende%2C%20a%20Marxist%20and%20an%20atheist%2C%20had%20no%20use%20for%20sin%20or%20redemption.%20But%20history%20will%20not%20absolve%20the%20Nixon