0net.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20preconceptions%20about%20prenuptial%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20think%20they%20could%20mean%20you%20don't%20think%20you'll%20stay%20married%2C%20indicate%20suspicion%20or%20distrust%2C%20or%20that%20they're%20only%20useful%20if%20you%20have%20assets%20to%20protect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinancial%20experts%2C%20though%2C%20see%20a%20different%20side%20to%20the%20agreements%20and%20think%20all%20couples%20should%20consider%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheresa%20Viera%2C%20an%20attorney%20based%20in%20South%20Carolina%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F08%2F30%2F1196872794%2Fprenups-arent-just-for-the-rich-and-famous-heres-when-to-consider-one%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20NPR%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20prenups%20are%20financial%20safety%20nets%2C%20not%20harbingers%20of%20separation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20preconceiving%20that%20a%20divorce%20is%20going%20to%20occur%2C%26quot%3B%20Viera%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20discussing%20important%20financial%20issues%20that%20come%20up%20in%20every%20marriage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViera%20added%20prenup%20agreements%20can%20give%20a%20couple%20the%20opportunity%20to%20discuss%20long-term%20financial%20goals%2C%20like%20owning%20a%20business%2C%20retirement%20age%2C%20or%20shared%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Viera%20said%20prenup%20agreements%20are%20about%20taking%20care%20of%20your%20future%20spouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsidering%20a%20prenup%20is%20like%20telling%20your%20%3Cspan%3Efianc%C3%A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20you%20today.%20I%20don't%20know%20who%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%2010%20years%20from%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Viera%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20want%20you%20to%20know%20that%20no%20matter%20what%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20take%20care%20of%20you%2C%20even%20if%20our%20relationship%20ends%20in%20divorce.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinancial%20expert%20Suze%20Orman%20agrees%20%E2%80%94%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F03%2F11%2Fwhy-suze-orman-says-you-should-always-get-a-prenup.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20CNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20prenup%20might%20feel%20unromantic%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20an%20uncomfortable%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20get%20too%20many%20emails%20from%20older%20women%20and%20men%20telling%20me%20that%20they've%20just%20lost%20everything%20because%20of%20a%20divorce%2C%26quot%3B%20Orman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrman%20said%20despite%20the%20initial%20awkwardness%2C%20a%20prenup%20can%20actually%20make%20your%20relationship%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%20to%20Viera%2C%20she%20thought%20the%20agreement%20offered%20couples%20an%20opportunity%20to%20get%20to%20know%20all%20their%20partner's%20thoughts%20on%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20cannot%20talk%20money%20to%20the%20person%20that%20you%20are%20about%20to%20marry%2C%20you%20are%20doomed%20for%20failure%20because%20money%20is%20going%20to%20run%20through%20your%20relationship%20more%20than%20anything%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Orman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrenups%20can%20protect%20you%20from%20being%20responsible%20for%20your%20spouse's%20debt%2C%20Orman%20added%2C%20and%20protect%20your%20property%20both%20before%20and%20after%20the%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20pros%2C%20prenups%20only%20recently%20gained%20some%20popularity%20among%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheharrispoll.com%2Fbriefs%2Fpopularity-of-prenups-rising-2022%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Harris%20Poll%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20global%20consulting%20and%20market%20research%20firm%2C%20found%20that%20in%202022%2C%20about%2015%25%20of%20married%20or%20engaged%20Americans%20have%20signed%20a%20prenup.%20Historically%2C%20numbers%20have%20been%20much%20lower%20%E2%80%94%20in%202010%2C%20only%203%25%20of%20Americans%20had%20signed%20one%2C%20according%2