3E%3Cp%3EThis%20process%20also%20led%20me%20to%20explore%20the%20site's%20other%20features%3A%20outlining%20my%20funeral%20wishes%2C%20curating%20a%20funeral%20playlist%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wanted%20to%20strike%20an%20even%20balance%20between%20songs%20that%20were%20hopeful%20and%20songs%20that%20would%20leave%20no%20dry%20eyes%20in%20the%20room%20%E2%80%94%20and%20writing%20up%20and%20recording%20a%20goodbye%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaying%20goodbye%20was%20the%20hardest%20but%20most%20cathartic%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Epart%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222294%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20the%20goodbye%20message%20playing%20on%20my%20MyWishes%20profile%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f59941781926001910cd53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221147%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20goodbye%20message%20playing%20on%20my%20MyWishes%20profile.%3Cp%3EInsider%2FKai%20Xiang%20Teo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20goodbye%20messages%20you%20leave%20on%20MyWishes%20aren't%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20go%20up%20on%20your%20public%20profile%20%E2%80%94%20much%20like%20how%20a%20social%20network%20works.%20Anyone%20can%20access%20these%20after%20a%20trusted%20contact%20you%20nominate%20informs%20the%20company%20that%20you've%20died%20using%20a%20special%20code%20they%20receive%20via%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaring%20at%20a%20blank%20document%20titled%20%26quot%3BKai%20Final%20Goodbye.doc%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20at%20a%20loss%20for%20what%20to%20write.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%2027-year-old%20who%20constantly%20experiences%20the%20fear%20of%20missing%20out%20and%20has%20all%20the%20social%20anxiety%20of%20an%20overcaffeinated%20workaholic%2C%20so%20it's%20only%20natural%20that%20most%20of%20what%20came%20to%20my%20mind%20were%20regrets%20and%20all%20the%20things%20I'd%20yet%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20those%20didn't%20feel%20appropriate%20as%20my%20last%20parting%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20sure%20whether%20my%20age%20had%20something%20to%20do%20with%20my%20unease.%20But%20according%20to%20Norris%2C%20MyWishes%20isn't%20targeted%20at%20a%20specific%20age%20group%20%E2%80%94%20death%20visits%20everyone%20eventually%2C%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndy%20Ho%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20psychology%20and%20medicine%20at%20the%20Nanyang%20Technological%20University%20who%20specializes%20in%20deathcare%2C%20told%20me%20using%20such%20tools%20to%20exercise%20autonomy%20over%20death%20was%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20so%20common%20for%20us%20to%20keep%20it%20at%20the%20periphery%20of%20our%20lives%2C%20thinking%20that%20if%20we%20keep%20it%20at%20bay%2C%20it%20might%20not%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20can%20change%20that%20perspective.%20We're%20talking%20about%20death%20now%20because%20we%20want%20to%20live%20well%20and%20die%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20wound%20up%20recording%20a%20goodbye%20about%20my%20fears%20of%20never%20having%20enough%20time%2C%20my%20worry%20that%20I%20don't%20say%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20you%26quot%3B%20enough%2C%20and%20my%20enduring%20wish%20that%20my%20loved%20ones%20make%20peace%20with%20their%20friends%20and%20bring%20doom%20upon%20their%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22bold%5C%22%3EWhile%20MyWishes%20can't%20replace%20talking%20to%20your%20loved%20ones%20about%20your%20wishes%2C%20it's%20useful%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20shared%20my%20goodbye%20messages%20with%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20forewarned%20that%20this%20was%20merely%20a%20drill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20friends%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Btoo%20much%20of%20a%20romantic%20to%20use%20a%20website%20like%20this.%26quot%3B%20Another%20wasn't%20sure%20whether%20he%20could%20escape%20the%20worry%20of%20how%20secure%20it%20would%20