earing%20internship.%20That%20is%20equivalent%20to%20two%20or%20three%20course%20credits%2C%20which%20will%20not%20delay%20their%20graduation%2C%26quot%3B%20Phua%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Phua%2C%20of%20the%202%2C000%20students%20who%20completed%20internships%20in%20the%20last%20academic%20year%2C%2035%25%20were%20doing%20semester-long%20internships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChin%20told%20Insider%20that%20he's%20one%20such%20college%20student%20who's%20opted%20to%20substitute%20coursework%20with%20a%20longer%20internship.%20Chin%20says%20he%20thinks%20that%20having%20done%20a%20longer%20internship%20%E2%80%94%20as%20opposed%20to%20someone%20who's%20just%20tried%20a%20job%20out%20for%20%26quot%3Btwo%20or%20three%20months%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20will%20set%20him%20up%20for%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20internship%20battle%20royale%20is%20relentless%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Computer%20science%20major%20Xinrui%20Gao%20told%20Insider%20that%20some%20of%20his%20juniors%20were%20interning%20even%20before%20freshman%20year%20started.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f82c9e04e14000196c92e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EComputer%20science%20major%20Xinrui%20Gao%20told%20Insider%20that%20some%20of%20his%20juniors%20were%20interning%20even%20before%20freshman%20year%20started.%3Cp%3EXinrui%20Gao%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EXinrui%20Gao%2C%20a%20computer%20science%20major%20at%20the%20Nanyang%20Technological%20University%2C%20has%20completed%20six%20internships%20and%20is%20graduating%20in%20December.%20The%20aspiring%20software%20engineer%20believes%20that%20the%20competition%20for%20internships%20isn't%20easing%20up%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20getting%20fiercer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%20for%20some%20of%20my%20juniors%2C%20I%20see%20that%20before%20they%20come%20to%20university%2C%20they%20actually%20pursue%20one%20or%20even%20two%20internships%20even%20before%20school%20starts%2C%26quot%3B%20Gao%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdrian%20Teh%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20undergraduate%20degrees%20in%20law%20and%20business%20at%20the%20Singapore%20Management%20University%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20thinks%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20LinkedIn%20are%20fueling%20the%20arms%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20benchmarking%20themselves%20against%20one%20another%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20made%20a%20lot%20worse%20through%20LinkedIn%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Teh%2C%20who%20has%20done%20internships%20with%20private%20equity%20firms.%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20sort%20of%20has%20access%20to%20what%20everybody%20else%20is%20doing%2C%20and%20whenever%20people%20start%20new%20roles%2C%20they'll%20announce%20on%20LinkedIn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20guilty%20of%20the%20same%20crime.%20People%20do%20benchmark%20themselves%20against%20one%20another%2C%20and%20it%20does%20definitely%20create%20this%20culture%20of%2C%20'I%20need%20to%20do%20more%20because%20everybody%20else%20is%20doing%20more.'%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20young%20workers%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20believe%20it's%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20opt%20out%20of%20the%20internship%20rat%20race%20given%20the%20high%20stakes%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMegan%20Wong%2C%20a%20marketing%20professional%20who%20graduated%20in%202021%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20one%20could%20lose%20out%20in%20the%20job%20market%20if%20one%20did%20fewer%20internships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20that%20even%20with%20one%20or%20two%20internships%2C%20if%20you're%20a%20more%20laid-back%20person%2C%20yes%20you%20can%20get%20a%20job.%20But%20just%20be%20prepared%20that%20the%20job%20might%20not%20be%20as%20good%2C%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20it%20could%20be%20a%20smaller%20company%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20startup.%20It%20may%20not%20be%20as%20glamorous%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Wong%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20impacts%20your%20bargaining%20power%20moving%20forward%20when%20you%20move%20to%20your%20second%2C%20or%20third%20job%20and%20so%20on%20because%20you%20have%20already%20started%20a%20bit%20behind%20your%20peers%2C%26quot%3B%20Wong%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDoing%20varied%20internships%20is%20just%20a%20rite%20of%20passage%20for%20most%2C%20career%20counselors%20and%20professors%20say%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESim%20Cher%20Young%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20career%20services%20office%20at%20the%20Singapore%20Management%20University%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20students%20know%20that%20internships%20are%20critical%20to%20securing%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20become%20a%20rite%20of%20passage.%20It%20becomes%20something%20that%20they%20know%20it's%20a%20means%20to%20their%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Sim%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20means%20if%20they%20want%20to%20secure%20a%20good%20job%20in%20a%20big-name%20organization%2C%20they%20need%20to%20put%20that%20proof%20of%20experience%20in%20their%20resume.%20Hence%20their%20internships%2C%20they%20need%20to%20do%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20believe%20that%20completing%20multiple%20internships%20is%20a%20good%20way%20to%20experiment%20with%20different%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20Gen%20Z-ers%2C%20who%20are%20students%20now%2C%20they%20may%20not%20really%20know%20what%20they%20want.%20Many%20of%20them%20are%20using%20internships%20as%20a%20sampling%20to%20see%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20like%20the%20industry%20and%20to%20find%20out%20a%20bit%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Adrian%20Choo%2C%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcareeragility.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECareer%20Agility%20International%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20career%20strategy%20consultancy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20multiple%20internships%20could%20be%20necessary%20even%20if%20one%20already%20knows%20what%20industry%20they%20want%20to%20enter.%20This%20is%20especially%20so%20for%20complex%20industries%20like%20banking%2C%20Ted%20Teo%2C%20an%20adjunct%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20helpful%20to%20a%20student%20if%20he%20or%20she%20can%20have%20at%20least%20two%20internships%20in%20a%20bank%20to%20get%20a%20broader%20spectrum%20of%20what%20it's%20like%20working%20in%20the%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Teo%2C%20who%20teaches%20modules%20on%20banking%20at%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStacking%20internships%20is%20important%2C%20but%20there%20are%20also%20other%20ways%20to%20prove%20you're%20a%20good%20worker%2C%20career%20counselors%20say%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECollege%20students%20around%20the%20world%20have%20been%20just%20as%20obsessed%20with%20clocking%20in%20internships%2C%20particularly%20those%20with%20prestigious%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-internship-what-its-like-to-work-for-goldman-2023-8%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntense%20competition%20for%20a%20summer%20internship%20with%20the%20elite%20hedge%20fund%20Citadel%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-into-the-citadel-associate-program-an-11-week-internship%5C%22%3E1%25%20acceptance%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20applicants.%20That%20means%20it's%20harder%20to%20get%20an%20internship%20at%20Citadel%20than%20it%20is%20to%20make%20it%20into%20Harvard%2C%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecrimson.com%2Farticle%2F2023%2F3%2F31%2Fadmissions-decisions-2027%2F%5C%22%3Elatest%20acceptance%20rate%20was%203.41%25%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20about%20being%20hard%20to%20get%2C%20some%20companies%20pay%20these%20interns%20very%20well.%20For%20instance%2C%20summer%20internships%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fde-shaws-summer-internship-recruitment-interview-tips-2023-4%5C%22%3Ehedge%20fund%20D.E.%20Shaw%3C%2Fa%3E%20pay%20between%20%249%2C000%20to%20%2420%2C000%20a%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20internships%20are%20the%20be-all%20and%20end-all%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20securing%20jobs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingapore%20Management%20University's%20Sim%20told%20Insider%20that%20students%20with%20fewer%20internships%20on%20their%20record%20shouldn't%20be%20counted%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20students%20that%20are%20very%20bright%20and%20they%20only%20did%20one%20internship%2C%20but%20they%20have%20shown%20that%20during%20their%20free%20time%2C%20they%20make%20hay%20while%20the%20sun%20shines%2C%26quot%3B%20Sim%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20couldn't%20get%20an%20internship%2C%20they%20did%20some%20other%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we%20are%20able%20to%20help%20them%20to%20couch%20their%20answers%20during%20interviews%2C%20to%20convince%20the%20employers%20that%20just%20because%20they%20are%20short%20of%20internships%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20they%20can't%20find%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20internships%20aren't%20the%20only%20way%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20one's%20dream%20industry.%20Career%20Agility%20International's%20Choo%20told%20Insider%20that%20there%20are%20other%20ways%20to%20stand%20out%20amongst%20other%20job-seekers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20go%20into%20a%20technology%20firm%2C%20then%20maybe%20it%20pays%20for%20the%20student%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20coding%20projects%2C%20to%20be%20involved%20very%20heavily%20in%20coding%2C%20or%20to%20raise%20his%20coding%20skills%20to%20the%20point%20where%20he's%20really%20really%20good%20so%20that%20he%20can%20attract%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20Googles%20or%20Facebooks%20of%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Choo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20to%20get%20an%20advantage%20is%20in%20university%2C%20build%20your%20expertise%20so%20that%20you%20can%20hit%20the%20market%20running%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-students-wage-internship-arms-race-to-clinch-dream-jobs-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694389321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f991d98a7840001961dbdd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-students-wage-internship-arms-race-to-clinch-dream-jobs-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stacking%20all%20the%20internships%20one%20possibly%20can%20is%2C%20for%20some%2C%20a%20non-negotiable%20rite%20of%20passage%20to%20secure%20a%20dream%20job%2C%20one%20career%20counselor%20told%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40insider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A167%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-students-wage-internship-arms-race-to-clinch-dream-jobs-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sale%20Of%20False%20Version%20Of%202%20Drugs%20To%20Be%20Monitored%20In%20India%20After%20WHO%20Alert%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Drugs%20Controller%20General%20of%20India%20(DCGI)%20has%20directed%20the%20drugs%20controllers%20of%20all%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20to%20keep%20a%20strict%20vigil%20on%20the%20sale%20and%20distribution%20of%20falsified%20versions%20of%20two%20drugs%2C%20liver%20medication%20Defitelio%20and%20Takeda's%20cancer%20drug%20Adcetris%20(injection)%2C%20following%20alerts%20issued%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20advisory%20on%20September%205%2C%20the%20DCGI%20said%20the%20WHO%20has%20issued%20a%20safety%20alert%20identified%20with%20multiple%20falsified%20versions%20of%20Adcetris%20injection%2050%20mg%20manufactured%20by%20Takeda%20Pharmaceutical%20Company%20Limited%2C%20identified%20in%20four%20different%20countries%20including%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20products%20are%20most%20often%20available%20at%20the%20patient%20level%20and%20distributed%20in%20the%20unregulated%20supply%20chains%20(mainly%20online).%20The%20products%20have%20been%20identified%20in%20both%20regulated%20and%20illicit%20supply%20chains%2C%20sometimes%20at%20patient%20levels%20as%20well.%20WHO%20has%20reported%20that%20there%20are%20at%20least%20eight%20different%20batch%20numbers%20of%20falsified%20versions%20in%20circulation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DCGI%20said%20in%20a%20communication%20to%20the%20state%20drugs%20controllers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdcetris%20(Brentuximab%20Vedotin)%20is%20a%20CD30-directed%20antibody-drug%20conjugate%20indicated%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%20patients%20with%20Hodgkin's%20lymphoma%20after%20the%20failure%20of%20an%20autologous%20stem%20cell%20transplant%20and%20systemic%20anaplastic%20large%20cell%20lymphoma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%206%2C%20the%20DCGI%20issued%20another%20advisory%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20safety%20alert%20issued%20by%20the%20WHO%20on%20September%204%20for%20falsified%20product%20Defitelio%20(Defibrotide)%2080%20mg%2Fml%20concentrate%20for%20solution%20for%20infusion%2C%20manufactured%20by%20Gentium%20Srl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20falsified%20product%20has%20been%20detected%20in%20India%20(April%202023)%20and%20Turkiye%20(July%202023)%2C%20and%20was%20supplied%20outside%20of%20regulated%20and%20authorised%20channels%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20WHO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20genuine%20manufacturer%20of%20Defitelio%20has%20confirmed%20that%20the%20product%20referenced%20in%20the%20alert%20is%20falsified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20use%20of%20falsified%20Defitelio%20will%20result%20in%20the%20ineffective%20treatment%20of%20patients%20and%20may%20pose%20other%20serious%20risks%20to%20health%20because%20of%20its%20intravenous%20administration%20and%20could%20be%20life-threatening%20in%20some%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20health%20body%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20(UN)%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20safety%20alerts%20for%20both%20the%20products%2C%20the%20DCGI%20has%20advised%20doctors%20and%20healthcare%20professionals%20to%20carefully%20prescribe%20drugs%20and%20educate%20their%20patients%20for%20reporting%20any%20adverse%20drug%20reactions%20(ADRs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DCGI%20has%20also%20asked%20the%20state%20and%20regional%20regulatory%20offices%20to%20instruct%20their%20officers%20to%20keep%20a%20strict%20vigil%20on%20the%20movement%2C%20sale%2C%20distribution%20and%20stock%20of%20the%20mentioned%20drug%20products%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20should%20also%20draw%20samples%20and%20initiate%20necessary%20action%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Drugs%20and%20Cosmetics%20Act%20and%20the%20rules%20made%20thereunder%2C%20the%20DCGI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20consumers%20and%20patients%2C%20the%20apex%20drug%20regulator%20has%20asked%20them%20to%20be%20careful%20and%20only%20procure%20the%20medical%20products%20from%20authorised%20sources%20with%20a%20proper%20purchase%20invoice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2031%2C%20the%20DCGI%20had%20issued%20an%20advisory%20alert%20against%20Abbott's%20antacid%20Digene%20gel%2C%20citing%20safety%20concerns%20as%20the%20United%20States-based%20drugmaker%20voluntarily%20recalled%20several%20batches%20of%20its%20Digene%20gel%20in%20India%20after%20the%20drug%20regulator%20raised%20an%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DCGI%20had%20asked%20the%20consumers%20and%20patients%20to%20discontinue%20the%20use%20of%20Digene%20gel%2C%20which%20is%20manufactured%20at%20a%20Goa%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20wholesaler%20and%20distributors%2C%20the%20DCGI%20had%20said%20the%20impacted%20product%2C%20with%20all%20batch%20numbers%2C%20manufactured%20at%20the%20Goa%20facility%20within%20the%20active%20shelf%20life%20to%20be%20removed%20from%20distribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20development%2C%20Takeda%20Pharmaceutical%20Company%20Limited%20said%20Adcetris%20(injection)%20should%20be%20procured%20only%20from%20the%20authorised%20distribution%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20to%20clarify%20that%20the%20Central%20Drugs%20Standard%20Control%20Organisation%20has%20issued%20a%20general%20advisory%20cautioning%20against%20falsified%20versions%20of%20Adcetris%20Injection%20(Brentuximab%20vedotin)%20identified%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTakeda%20has%20been%20authorised%20by%20the%20Drug%20Controller%20General%20of%20India%20to%20import%2C%20sell%20and%20distribute%20Adcetris%20in%20India%2C%20and%20we%20make%20it%20available%20to%20our%20patients%20here%20through%20well-established%20supply%20chain%20networks.%20We%20strongly%20recommend%20that%20Adcetris%20should%20be%20procured%20from%20Takeda%20authorised%20distribution%20sources%20only%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20falsified%20medical%20products%20pose%20a%20significant%20threat%20to%20public%20health%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20firm%20is%20committed%20to%20safeguarding%20the%20integrity%20of%20its%20products%20and%20supporting%20the%20fight%20against%20falsified%20medicines%20in%20order%20to%20protect%20patient%20safety%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20is%20our%20highest%20priority%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694388780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2Ffl30hj7g_medicine-generic_625x300_17_December_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2