September%2010%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20called%20for%20a%20virtual%20meeting%20in%20November%20to%20look%20at%20%E2%80%9Chow%20progress%20can%20be%20accelerated%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20various%20proposals%20that%20were%20made%20during%20the%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20floral%20tributes%20paid%20by%20the%20leaders%20at%20Raj%20Ghat%20were%20the%20closest%20to%20a%20family%20photo%20for%20the%20New%20Delhi%20G-20%20presidency.%20It%20was%20for%20the%20second%20year%20in%20a%20row%20that%20there%20was%20no%20joint%20photo%20session%20at%20the%20G-20%20summit%20as%20the%20US%20and%20European%20leaders%20refused%20to%20be%20photographed%20together%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20G-20%20adopted%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Declaration%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20summit%20in%20a%20surprise%20move.%20In%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20summit%2C%20and%20even%20the%20final%20days%2C%20the%20prevailing%20notion%20had%20been%20that%20it%20would%20be%20extremely%20difficult%20to%20obtain%20a%20consensus%20over%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20to%20release%20the%20joint%20statement.%20The%20absence%20of%20joint%20statements%20at%20all%20the%20G-20%20ministerial%20meetings%20over%20the%20last%20eight%20months%20was%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20uphill%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20looking%20at%20the%20Declaration%2C%20I%20think%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20consensus%20around%20the%20document%20was%20far%20from%20clear%20until%20the%20very%20last%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20senior%20European%20Union%20official%20familiar%20with%20the%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20expressing%20surprise%20at%20the%20final%20shape%20and%20release%20of%20the%20declaration%2C%20the%20Russian%20foreign%20minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20told%20reporters%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfrankly%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20expect%20that%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20ready%20to%20defend%20our%20wording%20of%20the%20text.%20The%20Global%20South%20is%20no%20longer%20willing%20to%20be%20lectured%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20reporters%20at%20a%20news%20conference%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg20-modi-new-delhi-declaration-consensus%5C%22%3EG20%E2%80%99s%20New%20Delhi%20Declaration%C2%A0Released%3A%20Consensus%20Text%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Condemn%20Russia%20for%20Ukraine%20War%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20even%20described%20the%20corralling%20of%20all%20the%20G-20%20sherpas%20at%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20in%20Manesar%20as%20akin%20to%20the%20closed-door%20deliberations%20in%20Vatican%20City%20to%20select%20a%20new%20Pope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20closed%20it%20about%20100%20km%20away%20and%2C%20just%20like%20the%20Pope%20was%20being%20elected%2C%20there%20was%20no%20smoke%2C%20but%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20a%20very%20positive%20outcome.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9C99%25%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20work%20on%20the%20declaration%20was%20done%20before%20the%20summit%2C%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfinishing%20touches%E2%80%9D%20added%20by%20the%20principals%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%20The%20contentious%20issue%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20was%20pushed%20at%20the%20end%20after%20largely%20finalising%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%2083%20paragraphs%20of%20the%20leaders%E2%80%99%20edclaration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20in%20Bali%2C%20the%20G-20%20declaration%20had%20noted%20the%20UN%20resolutions%20criticising%20the%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.g20.org%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fgtwenty%2Fgtwenty_new%2Fabout_g20%2Fprevious-summit-documents%2F2022-bali%2FG20%2520Bali%2520Leaders%2527%2520Declaration%2C%252015-16%2520November%25202022.pdf%5C%22%3EIn%20Bali%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20most%20members%20had%20deplored%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20strongest%20terms%20the%20aggression%20by%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20against%20Ukraine%20and%20demands%20its%20complete%20and%20unconditional%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20territory%20of%20Ukraine%E2%80%9D.%20It%20had%20also%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20members%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09162344%2FScreenshot-2023-09-09-at-4.22.17.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09162344%2FScreenshot-2023-09-09-at-4.22.17.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09162344%2FScreenshot-2023-09-09-at-4.22.17-300x145.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F09162344%2FScreenshot-2023-09-09-at-4.22.17-1024x493.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672296%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22578%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESession%20one%20of%20the%20G20%20summit.%20Photo%3A%20X(Twitter)%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20Delhi%20declaration%20talks%20about%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20human%20suffering%20and%20negative%20added%20impacts%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20with%20regard%20to%20global%20food%20and%20energy%20security%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%E2%80%99s%20joint%20statement%20also%20called%20on%20states%20to%20%E2%80%9Crefrain%20from%20the%20threat%20or%20use%20of%20force%20to%20seek%20territorial%20acquisition%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20without%20taking%20any%20names.%20The%20only%20time%20that%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20taken%20in%20context%20of%20Ukraine%20was%20in%20the%20paragraph%20related%20to%20the%20Black%20Sea%20grain%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20paragraph%20also%20%E2%80%9Chighlighted%20human%20suffering%20and%20negative%20added%20impacts%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20directed%20at%20Russia%2C%20but%20also%20notes%20%E2%80%9Cdifferent%20views%20and%20assessments%20of%20the%20situation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20Saturday%20night%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20foreign%20ministry%20had%20noted%20that%20this%20declaration%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foleg.nikolenko.50%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0shhYbp4V4W6YJaKNBc1tMTD6qQjBptC4Xqpt5h7Ku1yBJ8yzAXinwXEtXJZf7mdUl%5C%22%3Enothing%20to%20be%20proud%20of%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20even%20as%20the%20entire%20Western%20leadership%20was%20hailing%20the%20document%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csuccess%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20National%20security%20adviser%20Jake%20Sullivan%20told%20reporters%3A%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20our%20perspective%2C%20it%20does%20a%20very%20good%20job%20of%20standing%20up%20for%20the%20principle%20that%20states%20cannot%20use%20force%20to%20seek%20territorial%20acquisition%20or%20to%20violate%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20sovereignty%20or%20political%20independence%20of%20other%20states.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20was%20a%20stunning%20climbdown%20for%20the%20Western%20countries%20and%20their%20leaders%20who%20had%20spent%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20sending%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20imposed%20wide-ranging%20sanctions%20on%20Russia%2C%20and%20also%20had%20invested%20considerable%20domestic%20political%2C%20with%20European%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bruegel.org%2Fanalysis%2Feuropean-public-opinion-remains-supportive-ukraine%5C%22%3Epublic%20opinion%20remaining%20highly%20sympathetic%3C%2Fa%3E%20towards%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20said%20that%20the%20G20%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20to%20solve%20the%20Asian%20economic%20crisis%2C%20is%20not%20the%20%E2%80%9Cforum%20for%20political%20discussions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20G-20%20declaration%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20a%20diplomatic%20victory%E2%80%9D%20for%20Russia.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20G20%20confirms%20once%20again%20the%20isolation%20of%20Russia.%20Today%2C%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20G20%20members%20condemn%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20its%20impact%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Macron%20in%20a%20packed%20media%20conference%20at%20the%20International%20Media%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20German%20chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20said%20the%20paragraphs%20relating%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deutschland.de%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fg20-scholz-praises-emphasis-on-territorial-integrity%5C%22%3Esuccess%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20statement%20which%20supports%20the%20territorial%20and%20sovereign%20integrity%20of%20Ukraine%2C%E2%80%9D%20Scholz%20said%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20Western%20leaders%20hailing%20the%20declaration%20as%20a%20success%2C%20Lavrov%20responded%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20read%20the%20text%20yourself%20and%20(can%20judge)%20the%20Western%20leaders%20if%20they%20believe%20that%20people%20are%20so%20na%C3%AFve%20and%20suggest%20that%20this%20declaration%20is%20a%20condemnation%20of%20Russia.%20It%20never%20even%20mentions%20Russia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20claimed%20that%20the%20paragraph%20that%20called%20for%20%E2%80%9Ccessation%20of%20military%20destruction%20or%20other%20attacks%20on%20relevant%20infrastructure%E2%80%9D%20was%20an%20indictment%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20West.%20%E2%80%9CEverybody%20understand%20that%20this%20is%20about%20the%20attacks%20on%20the%20Nordstream%20power%20pipeline%2C%20Zaporozhye%20nuclear%20power%20plant%2C%20Moscow%20power%20stations%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20%E2%80%9Cour%20Indian%20partners%20who%20prevented%20G20%20from%20being%20so%20politicised%20as%20to%20paint%20Russia%20one%20way%20or%20another%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20G-20%20Sherpa%20Amitabh%20Kant%20had%20pointed%20out%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20proposal%20for%20the%20text%20on%20Ukraine%20was%20led%20by%20the%20four%20emerging%20markets%20in%20G-20%2C%20India%2C%20Brazil%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20the%20Indian%20foreign%20minister%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20a%20day%20earlier%2C%20Indian%20government%20sources%20told%20reporters%20on%20Sunday%20that%20the%20paragraphs%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20declaration%20must%20not%20be%20looked%20at%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20Bali%20declaration.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20convergent%20consensus%20rather%20than%20a%20divisive%20consensus%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20could%20show%20a%20path%20towards%20actual%20negotiations%20to%20resolve%20the%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20an%20EU%20diplomatic%20official%20claimed%20that%20the%20New%20Delhi%20declaration%20is%20%E2%80%9Cperhaps%20more%20stable%E2%80%9D%20than%20that%20in%20Bali%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20direct%20condemnation%20by%20Russia.%20While%20Russia%20and%20China%20had%20agreed%20to%20the%20joint%20statement%20in%20Bali%20in%20November%202022%2C%20they%20had%20withdrawn%20their%20consent%20and%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20replication%20of%20the%20text%20in%20any%20other%20G-20%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20may%20remember%20in%20Bali%2C%20we%20had%20worked%20with%20a%20different%20concept%20to%20split%20language.%20We%20were%20essentially%20quoting%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20resolution%20that%20was%20only%20shared%20by%20some.%20So%20this%20time%20around%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20go%20for%20split%20text%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20admitted%20that%20if%20the%20West%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Cwriting%20the%20text%20(in%20the%20Delhi%20Declaration)%20ourselves%20it%20would%20be%20looking%20very%20different%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20point%20here%20is%20that%20you%20build%20consensus%20around%20an%20international%20and%20a%20global%20issue%20that%20has%20effects%20and%20spillover%20effects%20to%20countries%20far%20away%20from%20Europe%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20the%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694365566000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10222855%2FF5o4uL_WkAAv_10.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg-20-declaration-as-the-west-scrambles-to-justify-its-softening-stance-on-moscow-russia-exults%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Without%20directly%20naming%20Russia%2C%20the%20Delhi%20declaration%20only%20talks%20about%20'the%20human%20suffering%20and%20negative%20added%20impacts%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20with%20regard%20to%20global%20food%20and%20energy%20security'.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg-20-declaration-as-the-west-scrambles-to-justify-its-softening-stance-on-moscow-russia-exults%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20can%20see%20his%20body%20through%20the%20ruins'%3A%20Inside%20the%20Moroccan%20tourist%20town%20that's%20'expecting%202%2C000%20dead'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694364540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-morocco-earthquake_6280270.jpg%3F20230910181234%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmorocco-earthquake-inside-amizmiz-the-tourist-town-ripped-apart-and-expecting-2000-dead-12958634%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20my%20friend%20drove%20through%20Amizmiz%20on%20holiday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%