ed%20to%20exercise%20their%20right%20under%20the%201947%20temple%20entry%20law%20of%20the%20United%20Provinces%20on%20February%2017%2C%201954.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20sanatanists%20claimed%20that%20the%20Dalits%20had%20not%20been%20%E2%80%9Cstopped%20from%20entering%20through%20the%20main%20gate%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20state%20asserted%20that%20they%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Crefused%20entrance%20%E2%80%A6%20through%20the%20singhadwar%E2%80%9D.%20Weighing%20the%20conflicting%20versions%20that%20had%20been%20given%20under%20oath%2C%20the%20high%20court%20found%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Harijans%20could%20not%2C%20uninterrupted%2C%20have%20access%20%E2%80%A6%20through%20the%20main%20gate%20%E2%80%A6%20because%20the%20sanatanists%20%E2%80%A6%20were%20at%20the%20scene%20to%20obstruct%20their%20entry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmanoj-mitta%5C%22%3EManoj%20Mitta%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20author%20of%20the%20recently%20published%3C%2Fem%3E%20Caste%20Pride%3A%20Battles%20for%20Equality%20in%20Hindu%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694356209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F02113517%2F26329346436_6c1e289bf1_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fsanatan-dharma-an-ideology-or-the-entire-hindu-community%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20V.D.%20Savarkar%2C%20the%20most%20influential%20ideologue%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20hardly%20conflated%20%E2%80%98sanatan%20dharma%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20entire%20Hindu%20community%2C%20unlike%20the%20BJP's%20position%20on%20the%20current%20controversy%20over%20the%20term.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fsanatan-dharma-an-ideology-or-the-entire-hindu-community%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20is%20important%20partner%20of%20Canada%3A%20Trudeau%20after%20talks%20w