E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20very%20well%20represented%20at%20the%20Parliament.%20They%20covered%20a%20rich%20diversity%20of%20topics%20such%20as%20Vedanta%2C%20Bhagavad%20Gita%2C%20Ahimsa%2C%20Yoga%2C%20ethics%2C%20environment%2C%20animal%20welfare%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20These%20were%20interspersed%20with%20Indian%20classical%20music%20as%20well%20as%20examples%20of%20Hindu%20worship%20and%20chants.%20As%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Swamis%20as%20speakers%20exceeded%20the%20number%20of%20Reverends%20and%20Rabbis!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindusforhumanrights.org%2Fnew-page-5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHindus%20for%20Human%20Rights%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20organised%20four%20panel%20discussions%2C%20each%20of%20which%20directly%20touched%20on%20the%20theme%20of%20the%20Parliament%3A%20Challenging%20Christian%20and%20Hindu%20Nationalism%2C%20Confronting%20Caste%2C%20Freedom%20of%20Speech%2C%20and%20Advancing%20Human%20Rights%20in%20South%20Asia.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20also%20had%20a%20children%E2%80%99s%20booth%20where%20they%20could%20try%20yoga%20poses%20related%20to%20nature%20and%20reflect%20on%20the%20interconnectedness%20of%20all%20beings.%20Our%20sister%20organisation%20Sadhana%3A%20Coalition%20of%20Progressive%20Hindus%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20organised%20and%20participated%20in%20several%20conversations%20on%20Hindu%20themes%20as%20well%20as%20on%20climate%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20such%20a%20visibly%20large%20Hindu%20presence%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freligionnews.com%2F2023%2F08%2F18%2Fthe-india-problem-under-the-surface-at-the-parliament-of-worlds-religions%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20nationalist%20organisations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20insisted%20that%20Hindus%20were%20excluded%20by%20the%20Parliament%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Etying%20them%20unfairly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Ct%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eo%20India%E2%80%99s%20contentious%20religious%20politics%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Etheir%20implication%20being%20that%20Hindus%20in%20the%20US%20were%20being%20targeted%20for%20events%20happening%20far%20away%20in%20India%2C%20over%20which%20they%20had%20no%20control.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20may%20sound%20like%20a%20perfectly%20reasonable%20objection%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20far%20from%20the%20truth.%20As%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20HfHR%E2%80%99s%20Advisory%20Board%20member%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famericankahani.com%2Fperspectives%2Fdharma-and-identity-explaining-the-hindu-divide-at-the-parliament-of-the-worlds-religions%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EProf.%20Anantanand%20Rambachan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20observed%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0those%20who%20raised%20this%20objection%20didn%E2%80%99t%20address%20the%20fact%20that%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egrowing%20number%20of%20Hindu%20organisations%20in%20India%20and%20in%20the%20United%20States%20have%20tied%20themselves%20to%20%5BIndia%E2%80%99s%5D%20contentious%20and%20aggressive%20politics%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20In%20his%20view%2C%20it%20was%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20naive%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20Parliament%20should%20uncritically%20give%20a%20platform%20to%20those%20dangerous%20ideologies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20that%20some%20of%20the%20same%20people%20and%20organisations%20who%20pretend%20to%20be%20far%20removed%20from%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Etheir%20ancestral%20homeland%E2%80%99s%20woes%E2%80%9D%20are%20directly%20implicated%20in%20their%20uncritical%20support%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20its%20anti-minority%20policies%20%E2%80%93%20with%20some%20even%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.connectedtoindia.com%2Fnris-descend-upon-gujarat-to-campaign-for-bjp-prior-to-state-polls-3197.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eactively%20campaigning%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Efor%20his%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20elections.%20Many%20others%20are%20likely%20financially%20supporting%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20party%20through%20the%20completely%20opaque%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Ffeatures%2F2018%2F4%2F11%2Findia-parties-now-can-get-foreign-funding-activists-say-not-ok%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EElectoral%20Bonds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20scheme%2C%20which%20permits%20anonymous%20contributions%20from%20non-resident%20Indians%20as%20well%20as%20foreign%20businesses%2C%20as%20long%20as%20they%20have%20Indian%20subsidiaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECo-opting%20Swami%20Vivekananda%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20deeper%20significance%20to%20the%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20the%20Kendra%20and%20the%20RSS%20family%2C%20which%20may%20not%20be%20immediately%20evident.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kendra%E2%80%99s%20call%20to%20action%20is%20founded%20on%20the%20celebrated%20speech%20by%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20at%20the%20first%20World%20Parliament%20of%20Religions%20in%20Chicago%20in%201893%2C%20in%20which%20he%20declared%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20fervently%20hope%20that%20the%20bell%20that%20tolled%20this%20morning%20in%20honour%20of%20this%20convention%20may%20be%20the%20death-knell%20of%20all%20fanaticism%2C%20of%20all%20persecutions%20with%20the%20sword%20or%20with%20the%20pen%2C%20and%20of%20all%20uncharitable%20feelings%20between%20persons%20wending%20their%20way%20to%20the%20same%20goal.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20went%20on%20to%20decry%20the%20unhealthy%20competition%20among%20religions%3A%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6if%20anyone%20here%20hopes%20that%20this%20unity%20will%20come%20by%20the%20triumph%20of%20any%20one%20of%20the%20religions%20and%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20others%2C%20to%20him%20I%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Brother%2C%20yours%20is%20an%20impossible%20hope.%E2%80%99%20Do%20I%20wish%20that%20the%20Christian%20would%20become%20Hindu%3F%20God%20forbid.%20Do%20I%20wish%20that%20the%20Hindu%20or%20Buddhist%20would%20become%20Christian%3F%20God%20forbid.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20RSS%20family%2C%20which%20portray%20themselves%20as%20sole%20custodians%20of%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20legacy%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fswami-vivekananda-is-not-a-sangh-parivar-icon-liberal-progressives-allowed-his-appropriation%2F1667819%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eselectively%20deploy%20his%20words%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20that%20speech%2C%20as%20well%20as%20from%20his%20large%20body%20of%20writings%2C%20to%20make%20him%20seem%20like%20a%20supporter%20of%20their%20call%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20majoritarian%20Hindu%20Rashtra%2C%20where%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20would%20be%20relegated%20to%20second%20class%20citizenship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20engage%20with%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20the%20Kendra%20at%20its%20Chennai%20office%20several%20years%20ago.%20Taking%20me%20to%20be%20a%20sympathetic%20supporter%2C%20he%20had%20railed%20on%20about%20the%20dangers%20posed%20to%20Hindus%20and%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20security%20by%20the%20growth%20of%20Christianity%20in%20South%20India%20and%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20states.%20The%20one-way%20conversation%20was%20mostly%20centered%20around%20the%20Kendra%E2%80%99s%20fierce%20rivalry%20with%20Christian%20fisherfolk%20in%20the%20Kanyakumari%20area%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%2016th-century%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0converts%20to%20Catholicism%20by%20Saint%20Francis%20Xavier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20interlocutor%20also%20spoke%20at%20length%20about%20the%20Vivekananda%20Rock%20Memorial%20that%20the%20RSS%20had%20built%20on%20an%20off-shore%20rock%20on%20which%20the%20Swami%20is%20said%20to%20have%20sat%20in%20meditation%20prior%20to%20his%20momentous%20journey%20to%20Chicago%20in%201893.%20And%20he%20made%20no%20secret%20of%20the%20primary%20motivation%20of%20the%20RSS%20in%20conceiving%20the%20memorial%3A%20The%20strong%20desire%20to%20push%20back%20on%20the%20dominance%20of%20Christians%20in%20the%20area.%20Vivekananda%20Kendra%20was%20established%20by%20the%20RSS%20in%201972%20as%20a%20by-product%20of%20the%20memorial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F07191646%2FSwami_Vivekananda_at_Parliament_of_Religions.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-222020%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221123%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESwami%20Vivekananda%20at%20the%20Parliament%20of%20Religions%20in%201893.%20Credit%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20words%20of%20Kendra%E2%80%99s%20founder%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1_s3HM62gKMrEAGRSptGvcpwuC_9oLLHW%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EEknath%20Ranade%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20functionary%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20long%20though%20many%20of%20them%20have%20become%20Christians%20even%20then%20the%20Hindu%20thought%20and%20behavior%20is%20prominently%20present%20in%20them.%20The%20work%20of%20bringing%20all%20those%20communities%20back%20to%20the%20large%20Hindu%20fold%20is%20not%20as%20difficult%20as%20it%20appears%20to%20be%E2%80%A6The%20Memorial%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20is%20only%20a%20forerunner%20of%20that%20grand%20plan.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1_s3HM62gKMrEAGRSptGvcpwuC_9oLLHW%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing%5C%22%3EParameswaran%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20Kendra%E2%80%99s%20president%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20was%20known%20for%20his%20wild%20conspiracy%20theories%20targeting%20the%20West%20and%20Christians.%20He%20posited%20that%20America%20knows%20that%20the%20next%20war%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20have%20to%20be%20fought%20between%20Islam%20on%20one%20side%20and%20the%20USA%20and%20the%20Church%20on%20the%20other%20side%E2%80%A6The%20USA%20plans%2C%20therefore%2C%20to%20browbeat%2C%20subdue%2C%20cajole%2C%20coax%20and%20trick%20India%20to%20become%20an%20ally%E2%80%A6%5Band%5D%20to%20secure%20the%20loyalty%20of%20the%20Indians%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Hindus%20%E2%80%93%20they%20must%20first%20be%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kendra%20has%20also%20made%20a%20fetish%20out%20of%20peddling%20the%20conspiracy%20theory%20that%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.exoticindiaart.com%2Fbook%2Fdetails%2Fexpressions-of-christianity-with-focus-on-india-naf031%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elegend%20of%20apostle%20St.%20Thomas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20coming%20to%20India%20was%20a%20fraud%20perpetrated%20by%20missionaries%20merely%20to%20advance%20conversions%2C%20and%20that%20the%20iconic%20St.%20Thomas%20Basilica%20in%20Mylapore%20was%20built%20on%20top%20of%20a%20destroyed%20Shiva%20temple.%20Whatever%20the%20historical%20truth%2C%20for%20an%20avowed%20spiritual%20organization%20to%20actively%20scorn%20the%20beliefs%20of%20another%20faith%20defines%20the%20very%20character%20of%20the%20Kendra%20and%20the%20RSS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20my%20view%2C%20the%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20bold%20action%20in%20disinviting%20the%20Kendra%20was%20in%20effect%20a%20repudiation%20of%20such%20gross%20misappropriation%20of%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20by%20Hindu%20nationalists%20and%20their%20claim%20to%20be%20speaking%20for%20all%20Hindus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHinduism%20without%20Hindutva%20at%20the%20Parliament%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20Hindu%20nationalists%20around%20the%20world%20have%20been%20attempting%20to%20conflate%20their%20caustic%20Hindutva%20ideology%20with%20Hinduism%20at%20large.%20They%20have%20insinuated%20themselves%20into%20inter-faith%20spaces%2C%20claiming%20to%20speak%20for%20all%20Hindus.%20Their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emodus%20operandi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20been%20to%20play%20the%20victim%20card%20by%20exaggerating%20claims%20of%20Hinduphobia%20as%20a%20cover%20for%20their%20own%20antipathy%20towards%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20as%20well%20as%20to%20divert%20attention%20away%20from%20their%20staunch%20support%20for%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20disastrous%20anti-minority%20policies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20just%20seen%20them%20use%20the%20same%20playbook%20in%20their%20response%20to%20the%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20disinvite%20Bhide.%20To%20its%20credit%2C%20the%20Parliament%20did%20not%20yield.%20Thankfully%2C%20most%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20groups%20were%20kept%20off%20the%20stage%20and%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20attendee%20status%2C%20and%20no%20one%20seems%20to%20have%20missed%20their%20voices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20we%20witnessed%20in%20Chicago%20in%20mid-August%20was%20a%20refreshing%20reminder%20of%20what%20Hinduism%20looks%20like%20without%20Hindutva%20%E2%80%93%20memories%20that%20are%20fading%20in%20much%20of%20India%20since%20the%20Modi%20government%20came%20to%20power.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERaju%20Rajagopal%20is%20with%20Hindus%20for%20Human%20Rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694354428000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fparliament-of-worlds-religions-rss-linked-nivedi