%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Renu%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20credits%20failure%20as%20the%20biggest%20teacher.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20there%20should%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F248533%2Flockdown-coronavirus-mumbai-friends-cycle-trip-highway-plan-stop-how-to-kanyakumari-work-from-home-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estructured%20way%20of%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20an%20event.%20Earlier%20I%20would%20squeeze%20in%20gyming%2C%20cycling%20and%20strength%20training%20but%20this%20time%20I%20decided%20to%20dedicate%20five%20days%20to%20cycling%20and%20two%20days%20to%20strength%20training.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month%2C%20when%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20caught%20up%20with%20Gareema%20again%2C%20the%20change%20in%20her%20attitude%20towards%20life%20was%20unmissable.%20After%20the%20LEL%20challenge%2C%20she%20seemed%20beat.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20all%20she%20spoke%20of%20were%20the%20positives.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20learnt%20my%20biggest%20life%20lessons%20through%20cycling%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20ride%20cannot%20define%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20personifying%20this%20line%20in%20everything%20she%20does.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694182861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D329462%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gareema%20Shankar%20and%20Renu%20Singhi%20are%20well%20over%20the%20'conventional%20age'%20for%20cycling.%20But%20ask%20them%20to%20slow%20down%20and%20they%20will%20only%20pedal%20past.%20Let%20alone%20the%20naysayers%2C%20they%20are%20not%20stopping%20for%20anyone%20on%20their%20journey%20of%20self-discovery.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98It%20Was%20All%20Cacti%E2%80%99%3A%20Ex-Army%20Officer%20%26amp%3B%20His%20Wife%20Turn%20Barren%20Udaipur%20Land%20Into%20Flourishing%20Homestay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EConsidered%20among%20the%20oldest%20fold%20mountain%20ranges%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20and%20possibly%20the%20Earth%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Aravallis%20form%20the%20backdrop%20against%20which%20the%20glorious%20city%20of%20Udaipur%20stands.%20On%20any%20given%20day%2C%20a%20drive%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Udaipur%20treats%20the%20traveller%20to%20a%20spectacular%20view%20of%20the%20mountains%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322666%2Fretired-couple-turns-ancestral-land-into-eco-friendly-konkan-homestay-sindhudurg-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20interspersed%20valleys%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20honey-coloured%20villages%20amidst%20the%20desert%20sands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20a%20shame%20not%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20this%20scene.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20one%20such%20road%20trip%20in%201994%2C%20Major%20Durga%20Das%20and%20his%20wife%20Jyoti%20Jasol%2C%20succumbed%20to%20the%20same%20fate.%20Fondly%20called%20%E2%80%98Major%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20once%20served%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20in%20Udaipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Jyoti%20(57)%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20royal%20ancestral%20line%20of%20the%20Rathores%20of%20Marwar-Jodhpur.%20Major%20(66)%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20a%20descendant%20of%20the%20royal%20ancestral%20lines%20of%20The%20House%20of%20Bassi-Udaipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20look%20at%20the%20scenery%2C%20the%20couple%20recalls%2C%20was%20all%20it%20took%20to%20convince%20them%20to%20buy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284474%2Fhow-couple-quit-city-life-to-build-sustainable-homestay-in-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%202.5%20acre%20land%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Jyoti%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20was%20still%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20and%20I%20was%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20Textile%20Gallery%20at%20the%20City%20Palace.%20But%20we%20both%20had%20a%20nagging%20thought%20that%20our%20lives%20were%20not%20being%20used%20creatively.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20after%2013%20years%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20my%20husband%20left%20the%20service%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20start%20developing%20this%20land%20we%20had%20bought%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Devra%E2%80%99%2C%20by%20which%20they%20christened%20this%20plot%2C%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20local%20name%20given%20to%20tribal%20temples.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20Army%2C%20Major%20says%20his%20guiding%20belief%20has%20always%20centred%20around%20serving%20both%20the%20nation%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F300372%2F8-pocket-friendly-cosy-homestays-in-the-mountains-for-that-scenic-winter-break%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20this%20(Devra)%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20cultivate%20a%20generation%20that%20is%20acutely%20aware%20of%20their%20surroundings.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98What%20is%20stopping%20you%20from%20making%20the%20dream%20come%20true%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202229px)%20100vw%2C%202229px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222229%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20Devra%20the%20local%20women%20of%20Udaipur%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20showcase%20their%20skills%20while%20earning%20a%20livelihood%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749.jpg%202229w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FIMG_7362-1_11zon-1694171749-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329449%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221486%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20Devra%20the%20local%20women%20of%20Udaipur%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20showcase%20their%20skills%20while%20earning%20a%20livelihood%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Jyoti%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20first%20began%20working%20out%20of%20this%20land%2C%20they%20started%20floriculture%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20supplying%20flowers%20to%20the%20Taj%20Palace%2C%20Udaipur.%20However%2C%20what%20they%20estimated%20to%20be%20a%20booming%20business%20did%20not%20work%20out.%20They%20had%20hit%20a%20dead%20end.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20couple%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20in%201997%2C%20where%20their%20baby%20girl%20was%20born%2C%20and%20Jyoti%20spent%20the%20next%20two%20years%20being%20a%20doting%20mother.%20But%20the%20dream%20she%20harboured%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F258991%2Fcouple-quits-city-life-eco-friendly-homestay-banyan-bliss-ethnic-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20a%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Udaipur%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20being%20silenced.%20%E2%80%9CIn%201999%2C%20I%20decided%20there%20was%20no%20better%20time%20than%20the%20present%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20land%20and%20this%20time%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20plan.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20leading%20up%20to%202004%2C%20when%20Devra%20officially%20started%20welcoming%20guests%2C%20Jyoti%20would%20make%20frequent%20trips%20between%20Delhi%2C%20where%20her%20husband%20and%20child%20were%2C%20and%20Udaipur%2C%20where%20her%20dream%20was.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20years%20were%20beautiful%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20journey%20of%20inking%20relationships%20with%20the%20craftsmen%20of%20the%20city%2C%20since%20architects%20and%20civil%20engineers%20were%20tough%20to%20find%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20got%20a%20local%20person%2C%20Shivji%2C%20on%20board%2C%20and%20he%20helped%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280532%2Fchildhood-friends-convert-grandmothers-house-into-eco-friendly-homestay-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20the%20structure%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20what%20it%20is%20today.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20Shivji%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Rupa%20%3Cem%3EBai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(an%20honorific%20to%20describe%20a%20woman)%2C%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20staff%20at%20Devra.%20She%20has%20witnessed%20the%20evolution%20of%20both%20the%20homestay%2C%20and%20the%20city%2C%20through%20these%20years%20and%20calls%20it%20a%20privilege.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20progress%20of%20our%20family%2C%20and%20of%20Devra%2C%20is%20inseparable.%20We%20have%20watched%20our%20children%20grow%20al