tics%20because%20of%20these%20degraded%20cans.%20Our%20primary%20goal%20is%20to%20democratise%20safe%20water%20for%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bala.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20doing%20that%2C%20we%20also%20take%20pride%20in%20being%20a%20completely%20environmentally%20responsible%20and%20sustainable%20company.%20The%20most%20satisfying%20part%20is%20understanding%20that%20we%20are%20doing%20our%20bit%20towards%20the%20health%20of%20people%20as%20well%20as%20the%20environment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20BookWater.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694180691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D329441%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20way%20to%20track%20the%20quality%20of%20dirty%20and%20clouded%20water%20cans%2C%20siblings%20Bharath%20Govindaraghavan%20and%20Balachander%20G%20launched%20BookWater%20that%20ensures%20access%20to%20safe%20drinking%20water.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329441%2Fchennai-startup-bookwater-tracks-water-cans-quality-with-qr-codes-helps-access-safe-drinking-water%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Improve%20Our%20Climate%20Literacy%20%3F%20Conference%20for%20Sustainability%20Education%20Seeks%20Answers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20the%20Mobius%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand%20is%20facing%20a%20severe%20crisis%20with%20heavy%20rains%20and%20flooding.%20Reports%20indicate%20that%20this%20natural%20disaster%20has%20claimed%2085%20lives%20and%20caused%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20in%20the%20state.%20Other%20parts%20of%20India%20are%20also%20grappling%20with%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%2C%20which%20are