le%20solutions%20through%20success%20stories%20and%20case%20examples.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CYouth%20play%20a%20critical%20role%2C%20both%20today%20and%20tomorrow%2C%20in%20many%20of%20the%20sustainable%20development%20goals.%20Whether%20it%20is%20the%20SDG%20related%20to%20hunger%2C%20quality%20education%2C%20gender%20equality%2C%20decent%20work%20and%20economic%20growth%2C%20or%20reduced%20inequalities%2C%20all%20these%20changes%20start%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9CYOUTH%E2%80%9D.%20We%20tend%20to%20follow%20what%20the%20Youth%C2%A0%20does%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%20%3Cstrong%3EPradip%20Burman%2C%20Chairman%2C%20Mobius%20Foundation.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20ICSE%202023%20chief%20guest%20is%20%3Cstrong%3EEducation%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20who%20will%20be%20inaugurating%C2%A0%20the%20conference.%20Other%20notable%20attendees%20include%20Dr%20Anil%20Prakash%20Joshi%20%E2%80%94%20environmentalist%2C%20green%20activist%20and%20founder%20of%20Himalayan%20Environmental%20Studies%20and%20Conservation%20Organization%20(HESCO)%3B%20and%20Jadav%20%E2%80%9CMolai%E2%80%9D%20Payeng%20%E2%80%94%20environmental%20activist%2C%20forestry%20worker%2C%20renowned%20as%20the%20Forest%20Man%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIncluding%20sustainability%20in%20national%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius1-1694094245.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ICSE%202023%20will%20focus%20on%20educating%20for%20climate%20change%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius1-1694094245.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius1-1694094245-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2