iolarvicide-dengue-chikungunya%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evector-borne%20diseases%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficially%20incorporated%20in%20July%202019%20under%20the%20EcoBio%20Group%2C%20the%20venture%20is%20based%20out%20of%20Ahmedabad%20but%20has%20operations%20in%20cities%20including%20Pune%2C%20where%20they%20manufacture%20the%20EBT%2C%20and%20Mumbai%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap--1694091926.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Eco%20BioTrap%20Team.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap--1694091926.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap--1694091926-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap--1694091926-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap--1694091926-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap--1694091926-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329345%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Eco%20BioTrap%20Team.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20it%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFemale%20mosquitoes%20who%20bite%20humans%20(males%20do%20not)%20have%20an%20average%20life%20span%20of%2015%20to%2030%20days.%20They%20only%20breed%20in%20water%20and%20lay%20approximately%20500%E2%80%931%2C000%20eggs%20in%20their%20lifetime.%20The%20fundamental%20question%20here%20is%20how%20do%20we%20break%20the%20chain%20of%20mosquito%20breeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20EBT%20does%20is%20mimic%20the%20breeding%20ground%20for%20female%20mosquitoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20going%20further%20into%20how%20this%20device%20works%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20understand%20its%20three%20core%20components%20%E2%80%94%20a%20biodegradable%20container%2Fvase%20made%20from%20recycled%20corrugated%20boxes%20used%20extensively%20in%20the%20packaging%20industry%3B%20a%20natural%20attractant%20(plant-based%20animal%20food)%20and%20insect%20growth%20regulators%20(IGRs)%3B%20and%20an%20industry-standard%20household%20insecticide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20EBT%20works%20is%20that%20you%20add%20water%20to%20the%20device.%20The%20attractant%20then%20lures%20the%20female%20mosquito%20to%20breed%20in%20this%20container%2C%20and%20then%2C%20the%20killing%20ingredient%20(IGR)%20ensures%20that%20no%20adult%20emerges%2C%20thereby%20breaking%20the%20chain%20of%20reproduction.%20EBT%20is%20made%20from%20waste%20and%20saves%20lives%2C%20and%20is%20one%20that%20is%20built%20on%20science%20and%20validated%20by%20scientists%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Prasad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBioTraps%20essentially%20target%20female%20mosquitoes%20by%20mimicking%20the%20ideal%20mosquito%20breeding%20ground%20to%20lay%20their%20eggs.%20Our%20patented%20waterproofing%20technology%20along%20with%20a%20quick%20and%20efficient%20delivery%20of%20the%20IGR%20solution%20then%20eliminates%20the%20female%20mosquito%20and%20100%25%20of%20her%20larvae.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20not%20a%20single%20adult%20mosquito%20emerges%20from%20the%20BioTraps%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20pressed%20further%20on%20the%20specific%20ingredients%20of%20the%20natural%20attractant%20and%20IGR%2C%20Prasad%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20natural%20attractant%20is%20animal%20food%20and%20for%20proprietary%20reasons%2C%20its%20details%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20revealed.%20IGR%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20a%20household%20insecticide%20approved%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263520%2Fviral-malaria-vaccine-mosquirix-africa-india-children-who-rules%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20World%20Health%20Organization%3C%2Fa%3E%20(WHO)%2C%20and%20is%20widely%20used%20in%20India%20and%20worldwide%20by%20public%20health%20departments.%20Specifically%2C%20however%2C%20EBT%20uses%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fnpic.orst.edu%2Ffactsheets%2Fpyriprogen.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPyriproxyfen%2520mimics%2520a%2520natural%2520hormone%2C%252C%2520carpet%2520beetles%252C%2520and%2520mosquitoes.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epyriproxyfen%3C%2Fa%3E%20granules.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntirely%20made%20in%20India%20and%20manufactured%20in%20their%20Pune-based%20factory%2C%20a%20unit%20of%20EBT%20covers%20an%20area%20of%20around%20400%20square%20feet%20and%20costs%20approximately%20INR%20500%20(on%20Amazon).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20positive%20element%20of%20the%20EBT%20is%20its%20cost-effectiveness.%20Electric%20vapourisers%20are%2044%25%20more%20expensive%20than%20EBT.%20When%20you%20compare%20it%20with%20repellents%20like%20coils%20or%20essence%20sticks%2C%20a%20unit%20of%20EBT%20is%20about%20five%20times%20cheaper%20over%20a%20four%20to%20six-week%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Prasad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap-Device-1694092266.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eco%20BioTrap%20eliminates%20mosquitoes%20from%20your%20home%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap-Device-1694092266.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap-Device-1694092266-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap-Device-1694092266-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap-Device-1694092266-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap-Device-1694092266-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329350%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20question%20remains%20of%20how%20you%20should%20deploy%20the%20EBT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20requirement%20is%20that%20it%20should%20be%20positioned%20in%20an%20area%20with%20no%20direct%20sunlight.%20%E2%80%9CIdeally%2C%20the%20BioTrap%20should%20be%20placed%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20in%20the%20corners%2C%20with%20minimal%20movement%20around%2C%20and%20away%20from%20direct%20sunlight.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20also%20effective%20in%20attracting%20gravid%20female%20mosquitoes%20to%20lay%20eggs%20when%20positioned%20at%20a%20height%20of%20five%20to%20seven%20feet%20when%20hung%2C%20and%20up%20to%20nine%20feet%20if%20placed%20on%20a%20surface%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20can%20you%20expect%20to%20see%20results%3F%20After%20deploying%20it%20for%20around%20a%20week%2C%20Prasad%20claims%20that%20you%20will%20see%20a%20noticeable%20reduction%20in%20the%20number%20of%20mosquitoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20their%20website%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20significant%20reduction%20occurs%20when%20the%20Eco%20BioTraps%20are%20continually%20used%20over%20an%20extended%20period.%E2%80%9D%20It%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20effectiveness%20of%20mosquito%20population%20reduction%20is%20further%20evidenced%20by%20the%20presence%20of%20Aedes%20eggs%20found%20on%20the%20inner%20walls%20of%20Eco%20BioTraps.%20By%20eliminating%20these%20eggs%2C%20Eco%20BioTraps%20effectively%20%E2%80%98Break-The-Chain%E2%80%99%20of%20mosquito%20breeding%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20overall%20control%20of%20the%20mosquito%20population.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20its%20shelf%20life%20comes%20to%20an%20end%20after%20four%20to%20six%20weeks%20(marked%20by%20water%20leakage)%2C%20the%20used%20unit%20of%20EBT%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311633%2Fruhani-verma-built-indias-first-carbon-negative-recyclable-public-toilet-amritsar-airport%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edry%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20recycled%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fg4PtV6GZGFo%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChallenges%20in%20developing%20EBT%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20challenge%20in%20developing%20the%20EBT%20was%20finding%20the%20right%20biodegradable%20material%20that%20would%20hold%20water%20for%20four%20to%20six%20weeks%20and%20not%20turn%20itself%20into%20a%20breeding%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20the%20example%20of%20an%20egg%20tray.%20It%20uses%20the%20same%20material%20used%20in%20EBT.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20pour%20water%20in%20an%20egg%20tray%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20hold%20water%20for%20seconds%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Prasad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20challenge%20was%20how%20to%20ensure%20that%20similar%20material%20holds%20water%20for%20a%20month%20or%20more.%20A%20lot%20of%20permutations%20and%20combinations%20were%20done.%20The%20product%20now%20has%20patents%20in%20over%2050%20countries%20for%20its%20unique%20ability%20to%20hold%20water.%20We%20cannot%20delve%20into%20more%20detail%20about%20the%20technology%20employed%20because%20of%20its%20proprietary%20nature.%20Overall%2C%20it%20has%20taken%20more%20than%20seven%20years%20of%20development%20and%20around%20five%20iterations%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20final%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETesting%20EBT%20in%20Dharavi%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%20used%20EBT%20in%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20largest%20slum%2C%20Dharavi%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20pilot%20project.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20trap%20yielded%20good%20results%20as%20it%20was%20user-friendly%20and%20safe%20for%20the%20environment.%20Another%20plus%20point%20of%20EBT%20is%20that%20unlike%20other%20devices%20used%20for%20the%20prevention%20of%20mosquito%20breeding%2C%20this%20trap%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20require%20electricity%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Dr%20Susanta%20Kumar%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20scientist%20formerly%20with%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Malaria%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20support%20of%20the%20ICICI%20Foundation%20and%20BMC%E2%80%99s%20Insecticide%20Department%2C%20the%20EBT%20team%20embarked%20on%20an%20eight-month-long%20scientific%20evidence-generation%20exercise%20in%20Dharavi%20last%20year.%20They%20covered%20three%20pockets%20of%20the%20slum%20%E2%80%94%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Nagar%2C%20Mahim%20Phatak%2C%20and%20Kumbharwada.%20A%20total%20of%203%2C000%20EBTs%20were%20deployed%20every%20month%20in%20these%20three%20areas%2C%20covering%20approximately%2010%2C000%20households%20and%20a%20population%20of%2080%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Prasad%20and%20I%20first%20went%20into%20Dharavi%20to%20pilot%20test%20the%20EBT%2C%20we%20were%20stunned%20by%20the%20density%20and%20complexity%20of%20Dharavi%E2%80%99s%20topography.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20dense%20forest%20where%20the%20shanties%20are%20so%20tightly%20built%20together%20that%20barely%20any%20light%20can%20penetrate%20through.%20In%20the%20lanes%20of%20Dharavi%2C%20you%20cannot%20even%20open%20an%20umbrella%20and%20walk%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Dr%20Ghosh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20the%20EBT%20without%20a%20hanging%20mechanism%20was%20impossible%20to%20deploy%2C%20and%20I%20recall%20Prasad%20telling%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EDada%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20failed%20even%20before%20we%20start%E2%80%99.%20Deepak%2C%20the%20manufacturing%20head%20at%20the%20EcoBio%20Group%2C%20and%20his%20team%20took%20up%20the%20challenge%20and%20developed%20a%20mechanism%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20with%20the%20hanging%20net%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20biodegradable%2C%20hold%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20pot%20(two%20litres%20with%20water)%2C%20and%20not%20get%20squashed%20under%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20torrential%20rain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Traps-Dharavi--1694092334.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eco%20BioTraps%20in%20Dharavi%20helped%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20mosquitoes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Traps-Dharavi--1694092334.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Traps-Dharavi--1694092334-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Traps-Dharavi--1694092334-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Traps-Dharavi--1694092334-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Traps-Dharavi--1694092334-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329352%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETesting%20the%20device%20in%20Dharavi%2C%20Mumbai.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20marked%20success%20of%20this%20pilot%20project%20garnered%20Prasad%20and%20his%20team%20a%20lot%20of%20acclaim%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dufi7boKw2MI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%20News18%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20featuring%20their%20work%20in%20a%2010-minute%20documentary%20%E2%80%94%20as%20part%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98Changemakers%E2%80%99%20series%20which%20was%20aired%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20an%20event%20commemorating%20World%20Dengue%20Day%202022%2C%20Rajan%20Naringrekar%2C%20the%20insecticide%20officer%20at%20the%20BMC%2C%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dengue%20mosquito%20is%20a%20domestic%2C%20peri-domestic%20and%20container%20breeder%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20challenges%20we%E2%80%99re%20facing%20was%20the%20access%20to%20houses%20and%20workplaces.%20Eco%20Biotraps%20is%20an%20apt%20solution%20to%20solve%20this%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELooking%20Ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20ahead%2C%20Prasad%20claims%20that%20the%20EBT%20team%20%E2%80%9Care%20in%20the%20final%20stages%E2%80%9D%20of%20striking%20partnerships%20with%20various%20municipal%20corporations%20and%20government%20organisations%20in%20India%20and%20other%20South%20Asian%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRentokil%20PCI%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20pest%20control%20provider%2C%20recently%20signed%20an%20agreement%20that%20makes%20EBT%20available%20in%201000%2B%20RPCI%20branches%20across%2021%20states%20in%20India.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20our%20venture%20recently%20raised%20an%20undisclosed%20amount%20of%20seed%20funding%20from%20institutional%20investors%20and%20is%20valued%20at%20Rs%2050%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20the%20EBT%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20eliminating%20vector%20diseases%20like%20malaria%20and%20dengue%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20elimination%20of%20vector-borne%20diseases%20has%20four%20key%20pillars%20%E2%80%94%20integrated%20vector%20control%20management%2C%20disease%20management%20(including%20surveillance)%2C%20civic%20participation%2C%20and%20IEC%20(information%2C%20education%20and%20communication).%20For%20any%20elimination%20to%20be%20successful%2C%20all%20four%20pillars%20need%20to%20work%20in%20tandem.%20I%20believe%20Eco%20BioTraps%20help%20facilitate%20integrated%20vector%20control%20management.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20they%20are%20biodegradable%20and%20do%20not%20emit%20any%20toxic%20chemicals%20like%20mosquito%20coils%20that%20are%20known%20to%20induce%20respiratory%20distress%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prasad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(You%20can%20read%20more%20about%20EBT%20and%20the%20team%20behind%20it%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ecobiotraps.com%2Fabout-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%3A%20EcoBio%20Group.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694093705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEco-Bio-Trap--1694091926.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D329333%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Developed%20by%20Prasad%20Phadke%20and%20his%20team%20based%20out%20of%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20Eco%20BioTrap%20is%20a%20'Made%20in%20India'%20device%2C%20which%20is%20more%20affordable%20than%20electric%20vapourisers%2C%20mosquito%20repellents%2C%20and%20coils.%20It%20effectively%20disrupts%20the%20mosquito%20breeding%20cycle%2C%20helping%20prevent%20diseases%20like%20dengue%2C%20malaria%2C%20chikungunya%2C%20zika%20etc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329333%2Fbiodegradable-eco-biotraps-prasad-phadke-reduce-mosquito-population-dengue-malaria-zika%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Vision%20Nanny%E2%80%99%20by%203%20Friends%20Uses%20Tech%20To%20Make%20Therapy%20Affordable%20for%20Kids%20With%20Visual%20Impairment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrathyusha%20Potharaju%20had%20a%20really%20hard%20time%20writing%20the%20alphabet%20as%20a%20child.%20She%20recalls%20that%20she%20would%20often%20end%20up%20writing%20mirror%20images%20of%20the%20letters%20and%20struggled%20to%20form%20words.%20The%20school%20she%20was%20enrolled%20in%20didn%E2%80%99t%20recognise%20that%20children%20have%20different%20developmental%20milestones%20and%20grow%20differently.%20Instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20helping%20this%20child%2C%20who%20was%20hardly%20four%2C%20they%20made%20life%20miserable%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20saw%20me%20crying%20after%20school%20many%20times%20and%20realised%20that%20something%20was%20not%20right.%20When%20I%20was%20five%2C%20she%20put%20me%20in%20another%20school%20that%20followed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302712%2Fpuducherry-social-worker-helps-tribal-children-study-become-engineers-teachers-udhavi-karangal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMontessori%20principles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20changed%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prathyusha%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20principal%20of%20this%20new%20school%2C%20which%20has%20since%20shut%20down%2C%20was%20unlike%20the%20other%20educators%20the%20young%20girl%20had%20met%20%E2%80%94%20he%20took%20a%20personal%20interest%20and%20helped%20diagnose%20her%20with%20mild%20dyslexia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20principal%20then%20held%20sessions%20regularly%20to%20help%20me%20out%20using%20Montessori%20methods%2C%20which%20focus%20on%20self-learning%20and%20use%20play%20to%20help%20children%20learn.%20The%20school%20was%20play-oriented%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20focus%20just%20on%20studies.%20Slowly%2C%20I%20started%20writing%20and%20learning%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2026-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20six-month%20journey%20to%20find%20their%20purpose%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20Prathyusha%E2%80%99s%20introduction%20to%20how%20important%20timely%20intervention%20is%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20learning%20disabilities.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20what%20she%20understood%20with%20much%20more%20detail%20after%20she%20began%20volunteering%20years%20later%20at%20L%20V%20Prasad%20Eye%20Institute%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolunteering%20at%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20Institute%20for%20Visual%20Rehabilitation%2C%20she%20would%20record%20audiobooks%20for%20children%20living%20with%20visual%20impairments%2C%20and%20witnessed%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpositive%20effects%20of%20early%20intervention%20in%20many%20young%20children%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20here%20that%20she%20found%20like-minded%20people%20in%20Vivian%20Manohar%20(32)%2C%20a%20mechanical%20engineer%2C%20and%20Nivedha%20Christabel%2C%20an%20optometrist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgrailmaker2-1694006197.jpg%5C%22%20widt