velled%20to%20rural%20areas%20across%20the%20country%20like%20Jharkhand%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20for%20six%20months%20and%20gained%20exposure%20at%20three%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20primary%2C%20secondary%20and%20tertiary%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrathyusha%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20travel%20around%20the%20country%20and%20observe%20the%20medical%20setup.%20As%20we%20were%20keen%20on%20helping%20children%20with%20disabilities%2C%20we%20focused%20on%20how%20they%20were%20accessing%20healthcare.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20L%20V%20Prasad%2C%20we%20had%20a%20glimpse%20of%20how%20early%20intervention%20works.%20However%2C%20in%20rural%20facilities%2C%20even%20in%20government%20hospitals%2C%20not%20many%20facilities%20were%20available%20for%20developmental%20disabilities.%20This%20was%20true%20for%20most%20small%20towns%20and%20villages.%20We%20knew%20that%20this%20was%20the%20area%20we%20needed%20to%20focus%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20in%202021%2C%20Prathyusha%2C%20Vivian%20and%20Nivedha%20co-founded%20Grailmaker%20Innovations%2C%20an%20assistive%20technology%20company.%20With%20the%20monthly%20stipend%20and%20kickstart%20grant%20they%20received%20from%20their%20fellowship%2C%20they%20developed%20their%20first%20product%20%E2%80%94%20Vision%20Nanny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAffordable%20treatment%20for%20thousands%20of%20children%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201372px)%20100vw%2C%201372px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgrailmaker5-1694006202.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221372%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vision%20Nanny%20provides%20intervention%20for%20children%20with%20cortical%20visual%20impairment%20(CVI).%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgrailmaker5-1694006202.jpeg%201372w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgrailmaker5-1694006202-300x208.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgrailmaker5-1694006202-500x347.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgrailmaker5-1694006202-768x532.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgrailmaker5-1694006202-150x104.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329222%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22951%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVivian%20teaches%20children%20using%20the%20Vision%20Nanny%20app.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVision%20Nanny%20is%20a%20SaaS%20platform%20(software%20application)%20that%20provides%20therapy%20for%20cerebral%20visual%20impairment%20(CVI)%20at%20the%20click%20of%20a%20button.%20Why%20CVI%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20fellowship%2C%20the%20duo%20observed%20that%20several%20young%20children%20had%20visual%20impairments%20that%20were%20not%20ocular%20(eye-related)%20but%20caused%20by%20damage%20to%20parts%20of%20the%20brain%20that%20process%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Vivian%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CCVI%20is%20a%20major%20problem%20that%20is%20going%20unaddressed.%20It%20is%20a%20growing%20cause%20of%20childhood%20blindness.%20This%20occurs%20in%20children%20because%20of%20complicated%20birth%2C%20preterm%20birth%2C%20or%20accidents.%20Their%20eyes%20are%20fine%2C%20but%20due%20to%20neurological%20damage%2C%20they%20are%20not%20able%20to%20understand%20what%20they%20see.%20The%20whole%20world%20looks%20like%20a%20confused%20maze%20for%20them.%20The%20only%20solution%20for%20this%20is%20vision%20therapy%2C%20but%20the%20awareness%20and%20expertise%20at%20rural%20centres%20is%20appalling%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vivian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVision%20Nanny%20caters%20to%20children%20with%20this%20problem.%20It%20is%20a%20set%20of%20digital%20activities%20that%20can%20be%20accessed%20through%20a%20mobile%20device%2C%20tablet%2C%20laptop%2C%20or%20even%20Smart%20TV.%20Every%20activity%20that%20is%20provided%20for%20developing%20the%20visual%20skills%20of%20a%20child%20in%20a%20hospital%20is%20available%20on%20this%20platform%20and%20has%20the%20advantage%20of%20being%20customisable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F293875%2Fworlds-first-braille-literacy-award-winning-device-annie-innovation-for-blind-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVision%20Nanny%3C%2Fa%3E%20provides%20personalised%20intervention%20for%20every%20child%20with%20CVI%20through%20customisable%2C%20interactive%2C%20vision%20stimulation%20activities.%20It%20is%20designed%20for%20parents%20and%20special%20educators.%20You%20can%20access%20different%20colours%20and%20pictures%2C%20move%20objects%2C%20show%20charts%2C%20conduct%20simple%20activities%20like%20moving%20a%20torchlight%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vivian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20has%20three%20phases%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20age%20and%20condition%20of%20the%20child.%20The%20different%20activities%20are%20used%20to%20improve%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20vision%2C%20and%20the%20platform%20is%20also%20equipped%20with%20interactive%20tools%20that%20make%20this%20process%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20starts%20with%20simple%20shapes%20like%20circles%20and%20triangles%2C%20which%20you%20can%20show%20in%20different%20colours.%20You%20can%20also%20change%20the%20background%20colour%20and%20size%20of%20the%20object%2C%20highlight%20features%2C%20add%20text%2C%20and%20bubble%20wrap%20it.%20This%20helps%20children%20identify%20the%20word%20as%20a%20shape.%20You%20can%20also%20move%20objects%20and%20add%20complexity%20as%20the%20child%20grows%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Vivian%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20interventions%20change%20how%20children%20interact%20with%20the%20environment%20and%20do%20activities%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20recognising%20different%20objects%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20view%20things%20better%20in%20person%20too%2C%20starting%20with%20simple%20things%20like%20recognising%20their%20toothbrush%20and%20toothpaste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVision%20Nanny%20also%20aims%20to%20help%20therapists%20with%20an%20easy-to-use%20assessment%20tool%20and%20dashboard%20to%20monitor%20the%20overall%20progress%20of%20the%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Beula%20Christy%2C%20head%2C%20Institute%20for%20Vision%20Rehabilitation%2C%20L%20V%20Prasad%20Eye%20Institute%2C%20says%20that%20this%20platform%20is%20a%20big%20boon.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20application%20gives%20educators%20and%20parents%20the%20ability%20to%20control%20everything%20with%20customisation%2C%20which%20other%20apps%20don%E2%80%99t%20offer.%20You%20can%20change%20colour%2C%20change%20activities%2C%20and%20even%20show%20your%20photo.%20It%20helps%20continuous%20therapy%2C%20which%20is%20the%20need%20in%20CVI%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Beula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20better%20life%20for%20children%20with%20CVI%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgrailmaker7-1694006205.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vision%20Nanny%20provides%20intervention%20for%20children%20with%20cortical%20visual%20impairment%20(CVI).%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgrailmaker7-1694006205.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgrailmaker7-1694006205-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgrailmaker7-1694006205-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb