9071%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKanika%20learnt%20to%20make%20vermiwash%20and%20enriched%20vermicompost%20manure%2C%20boosting%20her%20business.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanika%20was%20the%20first%20in%20her%20village%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20business.%20Looking%20back%20at%20her%20life%20nine%20years%20ago%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20attended%20the%20workshop%2C%20I%20had%20to%20travel%203%20km%20to%20get%20there.%20It%20would%20cost%20me%20Rs%2015-20%20for%20one-way%20travel.%20There%20were%20days%20when%20I%20would%20not%20even%20have%20money%20for%20the%20journey%20home.%20I%20would%20have%20to%20walk.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20buy%20water%20if%20I%20got%20thirsty%20en%20route.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20teach%20my%20daughter%20in%20a%20good%20school.%20I%20wish%20she%20either%20becomes%20a%20doctor%20or%20gets%20into%20an%20agriculture%20university.%20Previously%2C%20I%20did%20not%20feel%20comfortable%20asking%20my%20parents%20for%20money.%20Thankfully%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20ask%20for%20money%20from%20anyone%20today.%20With%20my%20earnings%2C%20I%20also%20got%20my%20home%20renovated%20and%20constructed%20an%20office%20for%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Kanika%20was%20conferred%20the%20national-level%20Padma%20awards%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20(ICAR)%2C%20New%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20a%20few%20years%20back%2C%20I%20could%20not%20have%20even%20imagined%20that%20I%20would%20get%20recognition%20from%20the%20government.%20The%20happiness%20cannot%20be%20expressed%20in%20words%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Kanika%20Talukdar%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A16939206