FBallari-4-1-1693911163.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221033%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mission%20ICU%20has%20been%20implemented%20in%2020%20hospitals%20across%20India%20including%20in%20districts%20of%20Karnataka%20such%20as%20Bellari%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-4-1-1693911163.jpg%201033w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-4-1-1693911163-300x251.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-4-1-1693911163-500x418.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-4-1-1693911163-768x642.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FBallari-4-1-1693911163-150x125.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329082%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMission%20ICU%20has%20been%20implemented%20in%2020%20hospitals%20across%20India%20including%20in%20districts%20of%20Karnataka%20such%20as%20Bellari%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Maanoj%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Maanoj%20points%20out%2C%20the%20idea%20for%20Mission%20ICU%20was%20in%20no%20way%20a%20happy%20accident%2C%20but%20rather%2C%20very%20intentional.%20Maanoj%20has%20a%20number%20of%20social%20impact%20projects%20to%20his%20name%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20of%20which%20is%20%E2%80%98Corona%20Champions%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20its%20purpose%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20COVID%20started%20reaching%20rural%20areas%2C%20the%20people%20who%20contracted%20the%20virus%20in%20these%20places%20were%20treated%20like%20untouchables.%20Through%20this%20initiative%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20tell%20stories%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327807%2Fgautam-yadav-person-living-with-hiv-shares-myths-and-things-to-know%2F%5C%22%20target%